如何在照片中使用水平线（打造令人惊叹的构图） https://digital-photography-school.com/using-horizo​​ntal-lines-in-photography/Darren Rowse Thu, 20 Jun 2024 10:00:00 +0000 Photography Tips and TutorialsCompositionintermediate https://digital-photography-school.com/blog/?p=52 <p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://digital-photography-school.com/using-horizontal-lines-in-photography/">如何在照片中使用水平线（用于令人惊叹的构图）</a>一文首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://digital-photography-school.com">数码摄影学校</a>上。它的作者是<a rel="nofollow" href="https://digital-photography-school.com/author/darren/">达伦·罗斯</a>。</p><p>本文于 2024 年 6 月更新，由 Darren Rowse 和 Jaymes Dempsey 贡献。想象一下您正在穿过一家画廊，欣赏一系列令人惊叹的照片。当您从一张图像移动到下一张图像时，一些有趣的东西引起了您的注意：许多图像中存在水平线，这些水平线引导您的眼睛[...]</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://digital-photography-school.com/using-horizontal-lines-in-photography/">如何在照片中使用水平线（用于令人惊叹的构图）</a>一文首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://digital-photography-school.com">数码摄影学校</a>上。它的作者是<a rel="nofollow" href="https://digital-photography-school.com/author/darren/">达伦·罗斯</a>。</p> ; <p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://digital-photography-school.com/using-horizontal-lines-in-photography/">如何在照片中使用水平线（用于令人惊叹的构图）</a>一文首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://digital-photography-school.com">数码摄影学校</a>上。它的作者是<a rel="nofollow" href="https://digital-photography-school.com/author/darren/">达伦·罗斯</a>。</p><div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-full"> <span class="responsive-image wp-image-261535" style="width:1200px"><span class="space" style="width:1200px; padding-top:103.67%"></span><img decoding="async" fetchpriority="high" width="1200" height="1244" src="https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/horizontal-lines-photography-1005.jpg?resize=1200%2C1244&#038;ssl=1" alt="用水平线改善你的构图" class="wp-image-261535" srcset="https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/horizontal-lines-photography-1005.jpg?w=1200&amp;ssl=1 1200w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/horizontal-lines-photography-1005.jpg?resize=289%2C300&amp;ssl=1 289w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/horizontal-lines-photography-1005.jpg?resize=579%2C600&amp;ssl=1 579w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/horizontal-lines-photography-1005.jpg?resize=768%2C796&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/horizontal-lines-photography-1005.jpg?resize=717%2C743&amp;ssl=1 717w" sizes="(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px" data-recalc-dims="1" /></span></figure></div><p><em>本文于 2024 年 6 月更新，由 Darren Rowse 和 Jaymes Dempsey 贡献。</em></p><p>想象一下您正在穿过一家画廊，欣赏一系列令人惊叹的照片。当您从一幅图像移至另一幅图像时，一些有趣的东西引起了您的注意：许多图像中都存在水平线，这些水平线将您的视线从画面的一侧引导到另一侧，并赋予每个<a href="https://digital-photography-school.com/composition-in-photography/" target="_blank" aria-label="composition (opens in a new tab)" rel="noreferrer noopener" class="ek-link">构图</a>一种拉伸甚至<em>慵懒的</em>感觉。</p><p>这些线条，无论是地平线、伸出的手臂、道路还是人行道，都是摄影师手中的强大工具 - 虽然您不需要在<em>每次</em>拍摄中都使用它们，但包含水平线可以在很长一段时间内发挥作用增强图像的方法。但你不应该随意添加水平线。相反，有意识地决定您使用的水平线的类型及其位置非常重要。在这篇文章中，我旨在与您分享一些富有洞察力的提示和技巧 - 这样您就可以掌握水平线在摄影中的使用并改变您的构图！</p><p>让我们开始吧。 </p><h2 class="wp-block-heading" class="wp-block-heading" data-section id="why-are-horizontal-lines-so-important-in-photography">为什么水平线在摄影中如此重要？</h2><div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-full"> <span class="responsive-image wp-image-206612" style="width:1500px"><span class="space" style="width:1500px; padding-top:56.13%"></span><img decoding="async" width="1500" height="842" src="https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/horizontal-lines-photography-3.jpg?resize=1500%2C842&#038;ssl=1" alt="摄影中的水平线" class="wp-image-206612" srcset="https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/horizontal-lines-photography-3.jpg?w=1500&amp;ssl=1 1500w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/horizontal-lines-photography-3.jpg?resize=300%2C168&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/horizontal-lines-photography-3.jpg?resize=600%2C337&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/horizontal-lines-photography-3.jpg?resize=768%2C431&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/horizontal-lines-photography-3.jpg?resize=717%2C402&amp;ssl=1 717w" sizes="(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px" data-recalc-dims="1" /></span></figure></div><p>水平线具有独特的属性。首先，它们经常唤起一种稳定和休息的感觉。想象一下宁静的地平线、倒下的树或平静的海洋的形象。这些场景中的每一个都具有突出的水平线，散发出一种永恒、永恒或宁静的感觉。换句话说，线条不仅仅存在于画面中，还存在于画面中。他们与观众交流，传达信息和情感。</p><p>然而，水平线不仅仅是为了创造一种稳定的情绪。他们还引导观众。当你的目光落在图像中的一条水平线上时，你几乎会本能地沿着它穿过画面。 （不相信我？看看本文中显示的图像，并注意您的眼睛如何在它们上移动！）</p><p>这一特性使得水平线对于强调重点和引导视觉流动非常有价值。它们可以引导观众的注意力集中在关键元素上，并让他们专注于镜头。</p><p>正如我上面强调的，仔细使用水平线至关重要。如果使用不当，它们可能会导致不必要的干扰、缺乏活力，甚至在你的作品中出现无意的紧张感。这就是为什么了解如何有效地使用水平线至关重要。通过掌握构图的这方面，您可以提升您的摄影水平 - 无论您是喜欢捕捉风景的壮丽还是日常生活的微妙差别。 </p><h2 class="wp-block-heading" class="wp-block-heading" data-section id="tips-and-techniques-for-using-horizontal-lines">使用水平线的技巧和技巧</h2><p>掌握水平线的使用可以对你的摄影产生巨大的影响——在下面的部分中，我将深入研究几种实用的技巧。无论您是初学者还是寻求提高技能的经验丰富的摄影师，这些技巧都将帮助您利用水平线的力量！ </p><h3 class="wp-block-heading" class="wp-block-heading" data-section id="start-with-the-rule-of-thirds"> 1.从三分法开始</h3><p><a href="https://digital-photography-school.com/rule-of-thirds/" target="_blank" aria-label="The rule of thirds (opens in a new tab)" rel="noreferrer noopener" class="ek-link">三分法则</a>是一种构图指南，旨在创建视觉平衡和动态的图像。想象一下你的框架被两条垂直线和两条水平线分成九个相等的部分。根据三分法，通过沿着这些线或它们的交叉点放置关键元素，可以显着增强照片的吸引力。</p><p>三分法则相当广泛，但您可以轻松地使用它来指导框架内水平线的放置。假设您正在拍摄具有引人注目的前景或天空的风景。您可以使用三分法将地平线沿着上或下水平三分之一定位，而不是将地平线定位在画面的正中心，从而为图像添加深度感和趣味性，如下所示：</p><div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-full"> <span class="responsive-image wp-image-206611" style="width:1500px"><span class="space" style="width:1500px; padding-top:66.67%"></span><img decoding="async" width="1500" height="1000" src="https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/horizontal-lines-photography-4-1.jpg?resize=1500%2C1000&#038;ssl=1" alt="摄影中的水平线" class="wp-image-206611" srcset="https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/horizontal-lines-photography-4-1.jpg?w=1500&amp;ssl=1 1500w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/horizontal-lines-photography-4-1.jpg?resize=300%2C200&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/horizontal-lines-photography-4-1.jpg?resize=600%2C400&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/horizontal-lines-photography-4-1.jpg?resize=768%2C512&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/horizontal-lines-photography-4-1.jpg?resize=90%2C60&amp;ssl=1 90w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/horizontal-lines-photography-4-1.jpg?resize=717%2C478&amp;ssl=1 717w" sizes="(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px" data-recalc-dims="1" /></span></figure></div><p> （当然，这种技术不仅仅适用于风景；它的用途广泛，几乎可以在任何摄影类型中定位水平线时使用！）</p><p>对于初学者来说，三分法则是一个很好的起点。它提供了一个简单而有效的框架来在框架内排列元素。但请记住，规则是用来打破的。一旦您熟悉了三分法则，就可以随意尝试。打破这些指导方针可以带来独特的、引人注目的和创造性的结果！ </p><h3 class="wp-block-heading" class="wp-block-heading" data-section id="use-a-horizontal-line-to-divide-the-frame"> 2.用水平线划分框架</h3><p>水平线可以将视线引导到画面周围，但它们<em>也</em>可以充当图像中的视觉障碍，有效地阻止观看者的视线。可以创造性地利用它来划分框架，分离构图中的各种元素或图层。例如，合影中伸出的手臂可以作为分界线，从而区分前景和背景互动。</p><p>即使您的图像不包含多个图层，您仍然可以使用水平线来划分框架，创造一种简单的感觉。想象一个<a href="https://digital-photography-school.com/photographic-minimalism/" target="_blank" aria-label="minimalist scene (opens in a new tab)" rel="noreferrer noopener" class="ek-link">极简主义场景</a>，一条孤独的地平线横跨镜头。这种简单可以唤起一种广阔和孤独的感觉。此外，根据它的位置——沿着三分之一，或者在中心——这条线可以创造出微妙不同的情绪。</p><p>这种利用水平线划分画面的技术提供了无限的创作可能性。如果您认真对待它，它将鼓励您从新的角度看待日常场景，并使用强大的水平线来有效地划分和平衡您的图像！ </p><h3 class="wp-block-heading" class="wp-block-heading" data-section id="use-landscape-orientation-for-a-calmer-shot"> 3. 使用横向拍摄更平静的照片</h3><div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-full"><span class="responsive-image wp-image-206608" style="width:1500px"><span class="space" style="width:1500px; padding-top:75%"></span><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="1500" height="1125" src="https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/horizontal-lines-photography-1.jpg?resize=1500%2C1125&#038;ssl=1" alt="摄影中的水平线" class="wp-image-206608" srcset="https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/horizontal-lines-photography-1.jpg?w=1500&amp;ssl=1 1500w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/horizontal-lines-photography-1.jpg?resize=300%2C225&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/horizontal-lines-photography-1.jpg?resize=600%2C450&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/horizontal-lines-photography-1.jpg?resize=768%2C576&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/horizontal-lines-photography-1.jpg?resize=717%2C538&amp;ssl=1 717w" sizes="(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px" data-recalc-dims="1" /></span></figure></div><p> <a href="https://digital-photography-school.com/portrait-or-landscape-orientation/" target="_blank" aria-label="orientation of your camera (opens in a new tab)" rel="noreferrer noopener" class="ek-link">相机的方向</a>会显着影响摄影中水平线的效果！当您想要增强水平线（例如地平线）的平静和稳定效果时，请考虑横向拍摄。</p><p>换句话说，调整相机的位置，使画面宽度大于高度，并让水平线横跨画面。顾名思义，风景摄影师经常采用风景方向，尤其是在拍摄极简主义场景时，但它也适用于许多其他类型和主题！</p><p>在横向方向上，观看者的眼睛自然地跟随延长线，带来视觉上舒缓的体验。连绵不断的地平线或任何其他水平元素给人一种平静和广阔的感觉。这是突出场景或主题的简单之美的绝佳方式。 </p><h3 class="wp-block-heading" class="wp-block-heading" data-section id="use-portrait-orientation-for-more-tension"> 4. 使用纵向来增加张力</h3><p>相反，如果您的目标是为照片注入紧张感或活力感，请尝试将相机翻转为纵向。这种垂直框架切断了水平线条，创造出更加强烈和充满活力的构图。这是捕捉熙熙攘攘的街景或任何以混乱和运动为关键元素的环境的有效策略。</p><p>在纵向方向上，截断的水平线通常会形成视觉障碍，增加惊喜或期待的元素。当您想要关注垂直元素（例如摩天大楼或树木），同时仍结合水平运动的能量时，此技术特别有用。</p><p>快速提示：如果您不确定是使用横向还是纵向，请同时尝试！尝试看看哪种最能传达您想要用图像讲述的故事总是值得的。</p><div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"> <span class="responsive-image wp-image-206610" style="width:400px"><span class="space" style="width:400px; padding-top:150%"></span><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="400" height="600" src="https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/horizontal-lines-photography-2.jpg?resize=400%2C600&#038;ssl=1" alt="摄影中的水平线" class="wp-image-206610" srcset="https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/horizontal-lines-photography-2.jpg?resize=400%2C600&amp;ssl=1 400w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/horizontal-lines-photography-2.jpg?resize=200%2C300&amp;ssl=1 200w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/horizontal-lines-photography-2.jpg?resize=768%2C1152&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/horizontal-lines-photography-2.jpg?resize=717%2C1076&amp;ssl=1 717w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/horizontal-lines-photography-2.jpg?w=1000&amp;ssl=1 1000w" sizes="(max-width: 400px) 100vw, 400px" data-recalc-dims="1" /></span> </figure></div><h3 class="wp-block-heading" class="wp-block-heading" data-section id="use-horizontal-lines-to-lead-the-eye"> 5.利用水平线引导视线</h3><p>我在整篇文章中都提到了水平线的引导力，但这是非常重要的一点，值得单独用一节来阐述。</p><p>您会看到，水平线可以<a href="https://digital-photography-school.com/how-to-use-leading-lines-for-better-compositions/" target="_blank" aria-label="direct the viewer's gaze through your photograph (opens in a new tab)" rel="noreferrer noopener" class="ek-link">引导观看者的视线穿过您的照片</a>- 通过战略性地放置这些线，您可以强调特定主题或在画面中创建叙事流程。这是一种微妙而强大的方式来控制图像的查看和解释方式。</p><div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-full"> <span class="responsive-image wp-image-206613" style="width:1500px"><span class="space" style="width:1500px; padding-top:70.33%"></span><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="1500" height="1055" src="https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/horizontal-lines-photography-5.jpg?resize=1500%2C1055&#038;ssl=1" alt="摄影中的水平线" class="wp-image-206613" srcset="https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/horizontal-lines-photography-5.jpg?w=1500&amp;ssl=1 1500w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/horizontal-lines-photography-5.jpg?resize=300%2C211&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/horizontal-lines-photography-5.jpg?resize=600%2C422&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/horizontal-lines-photography-5.jpg?resize=768%2C540&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/horizontal-lines-photography-5.jpg?resize=717%2C504&amp;ssl=1 717w" sizes="(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px" data-recalc-dims="1" /></span></figure></div><p>例如，如果您想突出显示某个特定主题（例如人或地标），请对齐镜头中的水平线以指向该主题。这种技术可用于各种场景，从城市景观到自然场景，引导观看者的眼睛到照片的焦点。 （请记住，我们的目标是不仅将这些线条用作风景的一部分，而且将其用作有助于图像整体影响的活跃元素！） </p><h3 class="wp-block-heading" class="wp-block-heading" data-section id="keep-your-horizontal-lines-straight"> 6.保持水平线笔直</h3><p>在摄影中有效使用水平线的一个基本方面是<a href="https://digital-photography-school.com/keeping-your-horizon-line-level/" target="_blank" aria-label="ensuring they are perfectly straight (opens in a new tab)" rel="noreferrer noopener" class="ek-link">确保它们完全笔直</a>。这似乎是一个简单的技巧，但其重要性怎么强调也不为过。稍微倾斜的地平线会破坏图像的视觉和谐！</p><p>要保持直线，尤其是地平线，首先要注意如何握住相机，并尽力保持水平。 （许多相机的取景器或液晶屏上都有内置网格线。这些网格可以作为您的指南，精确对齐画面中的水平元素。）对于那些想要更高精确度的人，可以使用热靴泡水平仪是一个方便的配件。无论您在什么地形上拍摄，它都能确保您的相机保持完美水平。</p><p>如果您的相机配备了电子水准仪，请充分利用它！此功能在具有挑战性的拍摄条件下特别有用 - 例如当您在山上或移动的车辆上拍摄时 - 在这些条件下保持相机水平可能很困难。</p><p>最后，如果你最终得到一条稍微倾斜的线，那也不是世界末日。后处理程序提供了<a href="https://digital-photography-school.com/how-to-straighten-a-crooked-image-in-photoshop/" target="_blank" aria-label="plenty of effective leveling tools (opens in a new tab)" rel="noreferrer noopener" class="ek-link">大量有效的调平工具</a>，而且它们非常易于使用。但首先要努力在相机内使其正确，因为在编辑时拉直图像会导致帧边缘周围丢失一些像素。</p><p>底线：水平直线会给您的图像带来专业、精美的外观，确保观众的注意力集中在您讲述的故事上！ </p><h2 class="wp-block-heading" class="wp-block-heading" data-section id="horizontal-lines-in-photography-final-words">摄影中的水平线：最后的话</h2><div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-full"><span class="responsive-image wp-image-206614" style="width:1500px"><span class="space" style="width:1500px; padding-top:66.67%"></span><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="1500" height="1000" src="https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/horizontal-lines-photography-6.jpg?resize=1500%2C1000&#038;ssl=1" alt="摄影中的水平线" class="wp-image-206614" srcset="https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/horizontal-lines-photography-6.jpg?w=1500&amp;ssl=1 1500w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/horizontal-lines-photography-6.jpg?resize=300%2C200&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/horizontal-lines-photography-6.jpg?resize=600%2C400&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/horizontal-lines-photography-6.jpg?resize=768%2C512&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/horizontal-lines-photography-6.jpg?resize=90%2C60&amp;ssl=1 90w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/horizontal-lines-photography-6.jpg?resize=717%2C478&amp;ssl=1 717w" sizes="(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px" data-recalc-dims="1" /></span></figure></div><p>如果你能有效地使用水平线，你可以显着增强图像的影响力和吸引力！只需记住我分享的技巧 - 例如应用三分法则、使用线条划分画面以及切换方向以创造不同的情绪 - 并获得一些在现场使用它们的实践经验。</p><p>也就是说，摄影是一种艺术形式，规则的作用是指导而不是限制。因此，在牢记这些提示的同时，不要忘记进行实验。尝试放置水平线，并始终注意这些线如何影响图像的平衡和情绪。</p><p>通过练习和实验，您会发现有效地使用水平线成为第二天性，让您能够创作出更具活力、更具吸引力和视觉吸引力的照片！</p><p>现在交给你：</p><p><em>你觉得水平线怎么样？您打算如何在照片中使用它们？在下面的评论中分享您的想法！</em></p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://digital-photography-school.com/using-horizontal-lines-in-photography/">如何在照片中使用水平线（用于令人惊叹的构图）</a>一文首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://digital-photography-school.com">数码摄影学校</a>上。它的作者是<a rel="nofollow" href="https://digital-photography-school.com/author/darren/">达伦·罗斯</a>。</p> ;
如何在 Photoshop 中进行无损编辑https://digital-photography-school.com/non-destroy-editing-photoshop/ https://digital-photography-school.com/non-destroy-editing-photoshop/#commentsMegan Kennedy Wed, 19 Jun 2024 10:00:00 +0000 Post Production TipsbeginnerPhotoshop https://digital-photography-school.com/?p=110143 <p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://digital-photography-school.com/non-destructive-editing-photoshop/">如何在 Photoshop 中进行非破坏性编辑</a>一文首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://digital-photography-school.com">Digital Photography School</a>上。它的作者是<a rel="nofollow" href="https://digital-photography-school.com/author/megan-kennedy/">梅根·肯尼迪</a>。</p><p>想象一下：您正在 Photoshop 中对美丽的城市景观进行后处理大约一半。当您突然发现图像的一小部分区域不符合要求时，您已经投入了数小时进行编辑。您正在处理的一面墙被意外克隆，看起来好像以不自然的角度悬挂着。结果就是感觉不对劲。后 […]</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://digital-photography-school.com/non-destructive-editing-photoshop/">如何在 Photoshop 中进行非破坏性编辑</a>一文首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://digital-photography-school.com">Digital Photography School</a>上。它的作者是<a rel="nofollow" href="https://digital-photography-school.com/author/megan-kennedy/">梅根·肯尼迪</a>。</p> ; <p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://digital-photography-school.com/non-destructive-editing-photoshop/">如何在 Photoshop 中进行非破坏性编辑</a>一文首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://digital-photography-school.com">Digital Photography School</a>上。它的作者是<a rel="nofollow" href="https://digital-photography-school.com/author/megan-kennedy/">梅根·肯尼迪</a>。</p><div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-full"> <span class="responsive-image wp-image-261524" style="width:1200px"><span class="space" style="width:1200px; padding-top:103.67%"></span><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="1200" height="1244" src="https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/non-destructive-editing-photoshop-1005.jpg?resize=1200%2C1244&#038;ssl=1" alt="Photoshop 无损编辑指南" class="wp-image-261524" srcset="https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/non-destructive-editing-photoshop-1005.jpg?w=1200&amp;ssl=1 1200w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/non-destructive-editing-photoshop-1005.jpg?resize=289%2C300&amp;ssl=1 289w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/non-destructive-editing-photoshop-1005.jpg?resize=579%2C600&amp;ssl=1 579w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/non-destructive-editing-photoshop-1005.jpg?resize=768%2C796&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/non-destructive-editing-photoshop-1005.jpg?resize=717%2C743&amp;ssl=1 717w" sizes="(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px" data-recalc-dims="1" /></span></figure></div><p>想象一下：您正在<a aria-label="Photoshop (opens in a new tab)" href="https://digital-photography-school.com/5-easy-photoshop-tips-beginners/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" class="ek-link">Photoshop</a>中对美丽的城市景观进行后处理大约一半。当您突然发现图像的一小部分区域不符合要求时，您已经投入了<em>数小时</em>进行编辑。您正在处理的一面墙被意外<a href="https://digital-photography-school.com/12-tips-for-mastering-the-clone-stamp-tool-in-photoshop/" target="_blank" aria-label="cloned (opens in a new tab)" rel="noreferrer noopener" class="ek-link">克隆</a>，看起来好像以不自然的角度悬挂着。结果就是感觉<em>不对劲</em>。</p><p>反复点击<strong>“撤消”</strong>按钮后，您发现 Photoshop 只能记住这么多，而您却陷入了这个看起来灾难性的编辑过程中。您现在所能做的就是浪费更多时间尝试解决问题或关闭程序并从头开始。如果有某种方法可以在 Photoshop 中编辑文件，以便每次新的调整都是完全可逆的……</p><p>在 Photoshop 中进行无损编辑！下面，我将解释如何非破坏性地使用 Photoshop，以便根据需要轻松恢复到早期的编辑阶段，并让您免于头痛和强烈的挫败感。 </p><h2 class="wp-block-heading" class="wp-block-heading" data-section id="what-is-non-destructive-editing">什么是无损编辑？ </h2><div class="wp-block-image wp-image-110479 size-full is-style-with-caption"><figure class="aligncenter"> <span class="responsive-image wp-image-110479" style="width:750px"><span class="space" style="width:750px; padding-top:60.67%"></span><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="750" height="455" src="https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/NDE00.jpg?resize=750%2C455&#038;ssl=1" alt="Photoshop 中的无损编辑" class="wp-image-110479" srcset="https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/NDE00.jpg?w=750&amp;ssl=1 750w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/NDE00.jpg?resize=300%2C182&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/NDE00.jpg?resize=600%2C364&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/NDE00.jpg?resize=717%2C435&amp;ssl=1 717w" sizes="(max-width: 750px) 100vw, 750px" data-recalc-dims="1" /></span><figcaption class="wp-element-caption">现在你看到我了……现在你看不到了！使用非破坏性工作流程进行编辑意味着您可以编辑照片，而不会在原始文件上留下痕迹。</figcaption></figure></div><p>非破坏性编辑（也称为“NDE”）是 Photoshop 中处理文件的一种方法，允许您<em>在不</em>覆盖原始图像数据的情况下进行更改。使用非破坏性方法，您始终能够回溯对图像所做的调整，保持灵活性并保持原始图像的分辨率不变。</p><p>事实上，您在学习在线 Photoshop 教程时可能已经遇到过非破坏性编辑，这些教程指导您使用特定的调整图层进行修改，而不是直接应用调整。</p><p>请注意，非破坏性编辑不是一种单一技术。您可以在 Photoshop 中以多种方式执行此操作，具体取决于所需的图像结果。在本文中，我将向您介绍摄影师在 Photoshop 中进行濒死体验时使用的一些最基本的方法。 </p><h2 class="wp-block-heading" class="wp-block-heading" data-section id="duplicate-the-background-layer"> 1.复制背景图层</h2><p>无论您在 Photoshop 中打开什么图像，都应该从复制背景<a href="https://digital-photography-school.com/beginners-introduction-using-layers/" target="_blank" aria-label="layer (opens in a new tab)" rel="noreferrer noopener" class="ek-link">图层</a>开始。如果您碰巧直接对图像进行调整，背景图层将保持不变。然后您就可以在所有调整图层完好无损的情况下重新开始！</p><p>如何复制背景图层？首先，在 Photoshop 中打开图像。将光标移至“图层”面板中的缩略图，然后单击显示<strong>“背景”</strong>的阴影区域：</p><div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter"> <span class="responsive-image wp-image-111306" style="width:750px"><span class="space" style="width:750px; padding-top:62.53%"></span><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="750" height="469" src="https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/nondestructive-editing-duplicate-layer.jpg?resize=750%2C469&#038;ssl=1" alt="非破坏性编辑重复图层" class="wp-image-111306" srcset="https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/nondestructive-editing-duplicate-layer.jpg?w=750&amp;ssl=1 750w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/nondestructive-editing-duplicate-layer.jpg?resize=300%2C188&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/nondestructive-editing-duplicate-layer.jpg?resize=600%2C375&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/nondestructive-editing-duplicate-layer.jpg?resize=717%2C448&amp;ssl=1 717w" sizes="(max-width: 750px) 100vw, 750px" data-recalc-dims="1" /></span></figure></div><p>选择<strong>“复制图层”</strong>选项，然后在出现提示时选择<strong>“确定”</strong> ：</p><div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter"> <span class="responsive-image wp-image-111307" style="width:750px"><span class="space" style="width:750px; padding-top:62.53%"></span><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="750" height="469" src="https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/nondestructive-editing-name-layer.jpg?resize=750%2C469&#038;ssl=1" alt="无损编辑 Photoshop" class="wp-image-111307" srcset="https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/nondestructive-editing-name-layer.jpg?w=750&amp;ssl=1 750w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/nondestructive-editing-name-layer.jpg?resize=300%2C188&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/nondestructive-editing-name-layer.jpg?resize=600%2C375&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/nondestructive-editing-name-layer.jpg?resize=717%2C448&amp;ssl=1 717w" sizes="(max-width: 750px) 100vw, 750px" data-recalc-dims="1" /></span></figure></div><p>一个新图层将出现在“图层”面板中的“背景”图层上方，标记为“背景副本”：</p><div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter"> <span class="responsive-image wp-image-111308" style="width:750px"><span class="space" style="width:750px; padding-top:62.53%"></span><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="750" height="469" src="https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/nondestructive-editing-layer-copy.jpg?resize=750%2C469&#038;ssl=1" alt="非破坏性编辑" class="wp-image-111308" srcset="https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/nondestructive-editing-layer-copy.jpg?w=750&amp;ssl=1 750w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/nondestructive-editing-layer-copy.jpg?resize=300%2C188&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/nondestructive-editing-layer-copy.jpg?resize=600%2C375&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/nondestructive-editing-layer-copy.jpg?resize=717%2C448&amp;ssl=1 717w" sizes="(max-width: 750px) 100vw, 750px" data-recalc-dims="1" /></span> </figure></div><h2 class="wp-block-heading" class="wp-block-heading" data-section id="work-with-adjustment-layers">2. 使用调整图层</h2><p>简而言之， <a href="https://digital-photography-school.com/photoshop-adjustment-layers-explained-part-1/" target="_blank" aria-label="adjustment layers (opens in a new tab)" rel="noreferrer noopener" class="ek-link">调整图层</a>将颜色和色调调整应用于图像，而不会永久更改任何像素值 - 而标准<strong>图像>;调整</strong>工具会将每个新调整烘焙到文件中。</p><p>要开始使用图层，您需要确保“调整图层”面板处于活动状态。只需选择<strong>“窗口”>;“调整”</strong> ：</p><div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter"> <span class="responsive-image wp-image-110455" style="width:750px"><span class="space" style="width:750px; padding-top:67.33%"></span><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="750" height="505" src="https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/NDE04.jpg?resize=750%2C505&#038;ssl=1" alt="Non-Destructive Editing in Photoshop" class="wp-image-110455" title="Photoshop 中的无损编辑" srcset="https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/NDE04.jpg?w=750&amp;ssl=1 750w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/NDE04.jpg?resize=300%2C202&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/NDE04.jpg?resize=600%2C403&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/NDE04.jpg?resize=90%2C60&amp;ssl=1 90w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/NDE04.jpg?resize=717%2C483&amp;ssl=1 717w" sizes="(max-width: 750px) 100vw, 750px" data-recalc-dims="1" /></span></figure></div><p>这将打开一个带有许多调整图层选项的面板，例如色相/饱和度、曲线、色阶、色彩平衡和黑白。这应该是您进行数字编辑的首选面板，在大多数情况下，它将提供您需要的所有编辑工具。</p><p>通过单击选项之一来选择调整图层之一：</p><div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter"> <span class="responsive-image wp-image-111310" style="width:750px"><span class="space" style="width:750px; padding-top:62.4%"></span><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="750" height="468" src="https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/nondestructive-editing-curves-adjustment.jpg?resize=750%2C468&#038;ssl=1" alt="非破坏性编辑曲线" class="wp-image-111310" srcset="https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/nondestructive-editing-curves-adjustment.jpg?w=750&amp;ssl=1 750w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/nondestructive-editing-curves-adjustment.jpg?resize=300%2C187&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/nondestructive-editing-curves-adjustment.jpg?resize=600%2C374&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/nondestructive-editing-curves-adjustment.jpg?resize=717%2C447&amp;ssl=1 717w" sizes="(max-width: 750px) 100vw, 750px" data-recalc-dims="1" /></span></figure></div><p>在此示例中，我选择了曲线来调整照片的对比度。当我单击该图标时，会弹出“曲线”面板并显示可用的设置：</p><div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter"> <span class="responsive-image wp-image-110457" style="width:750px"><span class="space" style="width:750px; padding-top:66.13%"></span><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="750" height="496" src="https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/NDE06.jpg?resize=750%2C496&#038;ssl=1" alt="Non-Destructive Editing in Photoshop" class="wp-image-110457" title="Photoshop 中的无损编辑" srcset="https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/NDE06.jpg?w=750&amp;ssl=1 750w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/NDE06.jpg?resize=300%2C198&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/NDE06.jpg?resize=600%2C397&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/NDE06.jpg?resize=90%2C60&amp;ssl=1 90w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/NDE06.jpg?resize=115%2C75&amp;ssl=1 115w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/NDE06.jpg?resize=717%2C474&amp;ssl=1 717w" sizes="(max-width: 750px) 100vw, 750px" data-recalc-dims="1" /></span></figure></div><p class="has-text-align-left">请注意，“图层”面板中现在有一个新图层；这是您的调整图层，它应该位于名为<strong>“背景”</strong>的图层以及<strong>“背景副本”</strong>图层之上。这意味着曲线图层下方的任何图层都将受到此调整的影响。</p><p class="has-text-align-left">要将调整效果限制为单个图层，请右键单击调整图层并选择<strong>“创建剪贴蒙版”</strong> 。将会出现一个向下的小箭头，表示调整图层只会影响位于其正下方的图层：</p><div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter"> <span class="responsive-image wp-image-110459" style="width:750px"><span class="space" style="width:750px; padding-top:57.33%"></span><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="750" height="430" src="https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/NDE7.jpg?resize=750%2C430&#038;ssl=1" alt="Non-Destructive Editing in Photoshop" class="wp-image-110459" title="Photoshop 中的无损编辑" srcset="https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/NDE7.jpg?w=750&amp;ssl=1 750w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/NDE7.jpg?resize=300%2C172&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/NDE7.jpg?resize=600%2C344&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/NDE7.jpg?resize=339%2C194&amp;ssl=1 339w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/NDE7.jpg?resize=717%2C411&amp;ssl=1 717w" sizes="(max-width: 750px) 100vw, 750px" data-recalc-dims="1" /></span> </figure></div><h2 class="wp-block-heading" class="wp-block-heading" data-section id="use-smart-filters"> 3.使用智能过滤器</h2><p>如果您想锐化照片、应用畸变校正等，Photoshop 滤镜会派上用场。然而，默认情况下，它们会被破坏性地应用，并且它们也不能作为图层使用。</p><p>幸运的是，向图像添加滤镜<em>可以</em>非破坏性地完成，这样您就可以在以后改变主意时撤消其效果。</p><p>单击要应用过滤器的图层，然后单击主工具栏中的<strong>“过滤器”</strong>下拉菜单。选择<strong>转换为智能过滤器</strong>：</p><div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter"> <span class="responsive-image wp-image-111311" style="width:750px"><span class="space" style="width:750px; padding-top:62.53%"></span><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="750" height="469" src="https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/nondestructive-editing-convert-smart-filters.jpg?resize=750%2C469&#038;ssl=1" alt="无损编辑转换智能滤镜" class="wp-image-111311" srcset="https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/nondestructive-editing-convert-smart-filters.jpg?w=750&amp;ssl=1 750w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/nondestructive-editing-convert-smart-filters.jpg?resize=300%2C188&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/nondestructive-editing-convert-smart-filters.jpg?resize=600%2C375&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/nondestructive-editing-convert-smart-filters.jpg?resize=717%2C448&amp;ssl=1 717w" sizes="(max-width: 750px) 100vw, 750px" data-recalc-dims="1" /></span></figure></div><p>应该会出现一个弹出窗口，提示您必须将所选图层转换为<a href="https://digital-photography-school.com/photoshop-smart-objects-beginners/" target="_blank" aria-label="Smart Object (opens in a new tab)" rel="noreferrer noopener" class="ek-link">智能对象</a>。点击<strong>“确定”</strong> ，所选图层缩略图的左下角将出现一个文档形状的小图标：</p><div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter"> <span class="responsive-image wp-image-111312" style="width:750px"><span class="space" style="width:750px; padding-top:61.6%"></span><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="750" height="462" src="https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/nondestructive-editing-smart-object.jpg?resize=750%2C462&#038;ssl=1" alt="非破坏性编辑智能对象" class="wp-image-111312" srcset="https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/nondestructive-editing-smart-object.jpg?w=750&amp;ssl=1 750w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/nondestructive-editing-smart-object.jpg?resize=300%2C185&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/nondestructive-editing-smart-object.jpg?resize=600%2C370&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/nondestructive-editing-smart-object.jpg?resize=717%2C442&amp;ssl=1 717w" sizes="(max-width: 750px) 100vw, 750px" data-recalc-dims="1" /></span></figure></div><p>选择滤镜并将其应用到图像后，您将在所选图层下方看到两个新项目。单击“图层”面板中图层旁边的“眼睛”图标将打开和关闭滤镜，双击“滤镜库”文本附近将打开“滤镜库”调整。右键单击过滤器库图层将弹出一个菜单。如果您想完全删除某个滤镜，请选择<strong>“删除”</strong> ，该滤镜将会消失，而不会降低您的图像质量。</p><div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter"> <span class="responsive-image wp-image-111313" style="width:750px"><span class="space" style="width:750px; padding-top:62.8%"></span><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="750" height="471" src="https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/non-destructive-editing-smart-filters.jpg?resize=750%2C471&#038;ssl=1" alt="非破坏性编辑" class="wp-image-111313" srcset="https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/non-destructive-editing-smart-filters.jpg?w=750&amp;ssl=1 750w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/non-destructive-editing-smart-filters.jpg?resize=300%2C188&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/non-destructive-editing-smart-filters.jpg?resize=600%2C377&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/non-destructive-editing-smart-filters.jpg?resize=717%2C450&amp;ssl=1 717w" sizes="(max-width: 750px) 100vw, 750px" data-recalc-dims="1" /></span> </figure></div><h2 class="wp-block-heading" class="wp-block-heading" data-section id="use-layer-masks-instead-of-the-eraser-tool"> 4.使用图层蒙版代替橡皮擦工具</h2><p>如果您想删除或隐藏图像的一部分，一种选择是使用<a href="https://digital-photography-school.com/photoshop-eraser-tool/" target="_blank" aria-label="Eraser tool (opens in a new tab)" rel="noreferrer noopener" class="ek-link">橡皮擦工具</a>。不幸的是，与 Photoshop 的标准调整一样，橡皮擦工具具有完全破坏性。</p><p>因此，我建议不要使用橡皮擦工具，而是<em>使用 mask</em> 。</p><p>遮罩是 Photoshop 大师工具包中较常用的工具之一。 <a href="https://digital-photography-school.com/layer-masks-in-photoshop-beginners/" target="_blank" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)" rel="noreferrer noopener" class="ek-link">使用图层蒙版</a>可以隐藏或<em>遮盖</em>图像的某些部分，而无需实际删除像素。</p><p>要应用图层蒙版，请选择要编辑的图层，然后单击“图层”面板底部的圆形框架图标：</p><div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter"> <span class="responsive-image wp-image-111314" style="width:750px"><span class="space" style="width:750px; padding-top:62.4%"></span><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="750" height="468" src="https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/non-destructive-editing-mask.jpg?resize=750%2C468&#038;ssl=1" alt="非破坏性编辑蒙版" class="wp-image-111314" srcset="https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/non-destructive-editing-mask.jpg?w=750&amp;ssl=1 750w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/non-destructive-editing-mask.jpg?resize=300%2C187&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/non-destructive-editing-mask.jpg?resize=600%2C374&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/non-destructive-editing-mask.jpg?resize=717%2C447&amp;ssl=1 717w" sizes="(max-width: 750px) 100vw, 750px" data-recalc-dims="1" /></span></figure></div><p>所选图层旁边将出现一个蒙版，您将在缩略图和蒙版之间看到一个小链图标。只要您选择图像缩略图，您的编辑效果就会正常应用。但是，如果您选择蒙版缩略图，您会发现用黑色画笔在其上绘画会隐藏该图层的部分内容。 </p><div class="wp-block-image size-full wp-image-110466 is-style-with-caption"><figure class="aligncenter is-resized"> <span class="responsive-image wp-image-110466" style="width:432px"><span class="space" style="width:432px; padding-top:60.65%"></span><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/NDE13.jpg?resize=432%2C262&#038;ssl=1" alt="所选蒙版层的特写 - 请注意该层角周围的白线。" class="wp-image-110466" style="width:432px;height:262px" width="432" height="262" data-recalc-dims="1" /></span><figcaption class="wp-element-caption">所选图层蒙版的特写。请注意，角落周围的白线指示“图层”面板的哪一部分处于活动状态。 </figcaption></figure></div><div class="wp-block-image wp-image-110465 size-full is-style-with-caption"><figure class="aligncenter"> <span class="responsive-image wp-image-110465" style="width:750px"><span class="space" style="width:750px; padding-top:68.4%"></span><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="750" height="513" src="https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/NDE12.jpg?resize=750%2C513&#038;ssl=1" alt="Photoshop 中的无损编辑" class="wp-image-110465" srcset="https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/NDE12.jpg?w=750&amp;ssl=1 750w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/NDE12.jpg?resize=300%2C205&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/NDE12.jpg?resize=600%2C410&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/NDE12.jpg?resize=717%2C490&amp;ssl=1 717w" sizes="(max-width: 750px) 100vw, 750px" data-recalc-dims="1" /></span><figcaption class="wp-element-caption">背景图层关闭（即不可见）后，您可以看到该图层的一部分丢失或被黑色图层蒙版隐藏。</figcaption></figure></div><p>此外，如果蒙版的任何黑色部分被涂上白色，则图像的相应部分将再次可见。 （如果您随后删除蒙版，所有隐藏区域都会重新出现。） </p><h2 class="wp-block-heading" class="wp-block-heading" data-section id="dodge-and-burn-non-destructively"> 5. 非破坏性的闪避和燃烧</h2><p><a href="https://digital-photography-school.com/what-are-burning-and-dodging-and-how-they-can-help-your-photos/" target="_blank" aria-label="Dodge and Burn (opens in a new tab)" rel="noreferrer noopener" class="ek-link">减淡和加深</a>工具用于使图像的区域变亮和变暗，但将这些效果直接应用于图像具有破坏性，并且会阻止您稍后编辑更改。</p><p>要非破坏性地躲避和燃烧，请首先打开您的照片。复制背景图层，然后从顶部菜单栏中选择<strong>图层>;新建>;图层</strong>： </p><div class="wp-block-image wp-image-110468 size-full is-style-with-caption"><figure class="aligncenter"> <span class="responsive-image wp-image-110468" style="width:750px"><span class="space" style="width:750px; padding-top:61.2%"></span><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="750" height="459" src="https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/NDE14.jpg?resize=750%2C459&#038;ssl=1" alt="Photoshop 中的无损编辑" class="wp-image-110468" srcset="https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/NDE14.jpg?w=750&amp;ssl=1 750w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/NDE14.jpg?resize=300%2C184&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/NDE14.jpg?resize=600%2C367&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/NDE14.jpg?resize=717%2C439&amp;ssl=1 717w" sizes="(max-width: 750px) 100vw, 750px" data-recalc-dims="1" /></span><figcaption class="wp-element-caption">创建一个新层！</figcaption></figure></div><p>会弹出一个对话框；确保您的设置与下面所示的相同，然后点击<strong>“确定”</strong> ： </p><div class="wp-block-image wp-image-111315 size-full is-style-with-caption"><figure class="aligncenter"> <span class="responsive-image wp-image-111315" style="width:750px"><span class="space" style="width:750px; padding-top:62.4%"></span><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="750" height="468" src="https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/non-destructive-editing-Dodge-burn-layer.jpg?resize=750%2C468&#038;ssl=1" alt="非破坏性编辑" class="wp-image-111315" srcset="https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/non-destructive-editing-Dodge-burn-layer.jpg?w=750&amp;ssl=1 750w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/non-destructive-editing-Dodge-burn-layer.jpg?resize=300%2C187&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/non-destructive-editing-Dodge-burn-layer.jpg?resize=600%2C374&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/non-destructive-editing-Dodge-burn-layer.jpg?resize=717%2C447&amp;ssl=1 717w" sizes="(max-width: 750px) 100vw, 750px" data-recalc-dims="1" /></span><figcaption class="wp-element-caption">将这些设置用于减淡和加深图层。</figcaption></figure></div><p>将创建一个新图层，其中填充灰色并使用柔光混合模式，以使其有效地进行闪避和燃烧。</p><p>您可以给该层起一个昵称，以帮助您记住它正在做什么。 （如果您忘记了，您可以随时添加它 - 只需双击图层名称，然后输入“dodge/burn”。</p><div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter"> <span class="responsive-image wp-image-110470" style="width:570px"><span class="space" style="width:570px; padding-top:63.33%"></span><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="570" height="361" src="https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/NDE16.jpg?resize=570%2C361&#038;ssl=1" alt="如何在 Photoshop 中进行无损编辑" class="wp-image-110470" srcset="https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/NDE16.jpg?w=570&amp;ssl=1 570w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/NDE16.jpg?resize=300%2C190&amp;ssl=1 300w" sizes="(max-width: 570px) 100vw, 570px" data-recalc-dims="1" /></span></figure></div><p>现在只需选择减淡或加深工具并将任何调整应用到这个新图层。虽然您现在正在编辑实际图像上方的一层，但您已经调整了混合模式，以便灰色减淡/加深图层完全透明，并且您对此图层所做的任何更改现在似乎只是调整图像，而不会影响图像的质量。原始像素。</p><div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter"> <span class="responsive-image wp-image-111316" style="width:750px"><span class="space" style="width:750px; padding-top:62.4%"></span><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="750" height="468" src="https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/non-destructive-editing-dodge-burn.jpg?resize=750%2C468&#038;ssl=1" alt="无损编辑减淡烧伤图层" class="wp-image-111316" srcset="https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/non-destructive-editing-dodge-burn.jpg?w=750&amp;ssl=1 750w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/non-destructive-editing-dodge-burn.jpg?resize=300%2C187&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/non-destructive-editing-dodge-burn.jpg?resize=600%2C374&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/non-destructive-editing-dodge-burn.jpg?resize=717%2C447&amp;ssl=1 717w" sizes="(max-width: 750px) 100vw, 750px" data-recalc-dims="1" /></span> </figure></div><div class="wp-block-image size-full wp-image-111317 is-style-with-caption"><figure class="aligncenter"> <span class="responsive-image wp-image-111317" style="width:750px"><span class="space" style="width:750px; padding-top:66.67%"></span><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="750" height="500" src="https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/non-destructive-editing-dodge-burn-result.jpg?resize=750%2C500&#038;ssl=1" alt="闪避和燃烧层的结果" class="wp-image-111317" srcset="https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/non-destructive-editing-dodge-burn-result.jpg?w=750&amp;ssl=1 750w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/non-destructive-editing-dodge-burn-result.jpg?resize=300%2C200&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/non-destructive-editing-dodge-burn-result.jpg?resize=600%2C400&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/non-destructive-editing-dodge-burn-result.jpg?resize=90%2C60&amp;ssl=1 90w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/non-destructive-editing-dodge-burn-result.jpg?resize=717%2C478&amp;ssl=1 717w" sizes="(max-width: 750px) 100vw, 750px" data-recalc-dims="1" /></span><figcaption class="wp-element-caption">闪避和燃烧层的结果！ </figcaption></figure></div><h2 class="wp-block-heading" class="wp-block-heading" data-section id="use-the-clone-stamp-tool-non-destructively"> 6. 非破坏性地使用仿制图章工具</h2><p>克隆图章是另一个很棒的工具，用于删除图像中您可能不想要的碎片。通常它的工作原理是移动原始图像中的像素，但是 - 你猜对了！ ——这是一种极具破坏性的技术。</p><p>要非破坏性地使用仿制图章工具，只需像以前一样创建一个新图层即可。接下来，选择<strong>克隆图章</strong>工具，然后在<strong>示例</strong>下拉菜单中选择<strong>当前和以下</strong>选项：</p><div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter"> <span class="responsive-image wp-image-110477" style="width:750px"><span class="space" style="width:750px; padding-top:68.27%"></span><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="750" height="512" src="https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/NDE21-1.jpg?resize=750%2C512&#038;ssl=1" alt="克隆工具" class="wp-image-110477" srcset="https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/NDE21-1.jpg?w=750&amp;ssl=1 750w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/NDE21-1.jpg?resize=300%2C205&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/NDE21-1.jpg?resize=600%2C410&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/NDE21-1.jpg?resize=90%2C60&amp;ssl=1 90w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/NDE21-1.jpg?resize=717%2C489&amp;ssl=1 717w" sizes="(max-width: 750px) 100vw, 750px" data-recalc-dims="1" /></span></figure></div><p>现在，克隆图章工具将对图像中的所有内容进行采样，但仅将任何更改应用于最顶层。 </p><div class="wp-block-image wp-image-111318 size-full is-style-with-caption"><figure class="aligncenter"> <span class="responsive-image wp-image-111318" style="width:750px"><span class="space" style="width:750px; padding-top:62.27%"></span><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="750" height="467" src="https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/non-destructive-editing-masked.jpg?resize=750%2C467&#038;ssl=1" alt="非破坏性编辑" class="wp-image-111318" srcset="https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/non-destructive-editing-masked.jpg?w=750&amp;ssl=1 750w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/non-destructive-editing-masked.jpg?resize=300%2C187&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/non-destructive-editing-masked.jpg?resize=600%2C374&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/non-destructive-editing-masked.jpg?resize=717%2C446&amp;ssl=1 717w" sizes="(max-width: 750px) 100vw, 750px" data-recalc-dims="1" /></span><figcaption class="wp-element-caption">克隆层看起来像这样！ </figcaption></figure></div><div class="wp-block-image wp-image-110476 size-full is-style-with-caption"><figure class="aligncenter"> <span class="responsive-image wp-image-110476" style="width:750px"><span class="space" style="width:750px; padding-top:61.2%"></span><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="750" height="459" src="https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/NDE22.jpg?resize=750%2C459&#038;ssl=1" alt="克隆工具无损" class="wp-image-110476" srcset="https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/NDE22.jpg?w=750&amp;ssl=1 750w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/NDE22.jpg?resize=300%2C184&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/NDE22.jpg?resize=600%2C367&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/NDE22.jpg?resize=717%2C439&amp;ssl=1 717w" sizes="(max-width: 750px) 100vw, 750px" data-recalc-dims="1" /></span><figcaption class="wp-element-caption">应用克隆层的结果如下所示。 </figcaption></figure></div><h2 class="wp-block-heading" class="wp-block-heading" data-section id="edit-without-ruining-your-images">编辑而不破坏您的图像！</h2><p>在 Photoshop 中还有很多其他非破坏性编辑方法 - 但正如本文所希望展示的，非破坏性编辑主要是使用放置在原始图像上方的新图层，而不是调整原始图像本身。</p><p>一开始它可能看起来很笨重，但它很快就会成为您工作流程的自动部分。下次当您发现自己遇到尴尬的编辑时，您会很高兴您可以简单地关闭图层而不用重新开始！</p><p>现在交给你：</p><p><em>您在 Photoshop 中进行非破坏性编辑吗？你打算这么做吗？在下面的评论中分享您的想法！</em></p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://digital-photography-school.com/non-destructive-editing-photoshop/">如何在 Photoshop 中进行非破坏性编辑</a>一文首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://digital-photography-school.com">Digital Photography School</a>上。它的作者是<a rel="nofollow" href="https://digital-photography-school.com/author/megan-kennedy/">梅根·肯尼迪</a>。</p> ; https://digital-photography-school.com/non-destroy-editing-photoshop/feed/ 10
最适合摄影的圆偏光镜 (2024) https://digital-photography-school.com/best-circular-polizing-filter/ https://digital-photography-school.com/best-circular-polizing-filter/#commentsSimon Ringsmuth Tue, 18 Jun 2024 10:00:00 +0000 Cameras and Equipmentintermediatephotography accessories https://digital-photography-school.com/?p=259215 <p><a rel="nofollow" href="https://digital-photography-school.com/best-circular-polarizing-filter/">最佳摄影圆偏光镜 (2024) 的</a>帖子首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://digital-photography-school.com">数码摄影学校</a>上。它的作者是<a rel="nofollow" href="https://digital-photography-school.com/author/simonringsmuth/">西蒙·林斯穆斯 (Simon Ringsmuth)</a> 。</p><p>圆偏光镜，也称为圆偏光滤镜，是拍摄风景、自然和野生动物图像的摄影师的必备工具，尤其是在湖泊、溪流或其他水体附近。它是一个简单的玻璃圈，几乎可以安装在任何相机镜头的前面，它可以增强色彩，同时减少不需要的[...]</p><p><a rel="nofollow" href="https://digital-photography-school.com/best-circular-polarizing-filter/">最佳摄影圆偏光镜 (2024) 的</a>帖子首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://digital-photography-school.com">数码摄影学校</a>上。它的作者是<a rel="nofollow" href="https://digital-photography-school.com/author/simonringsmuth/">西蒙·林斯穆斯 (Simon Ringsmuth)</a> 。</p> ; <p><a rel="nofollow" href="https://digital-photography-school.com/best-circular-polarizing-filter/">最佳摄影圆偏光镜 (2024) 的</a>帖子首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://digital-photography-school.com">数码摄影学校</a>上。它的作者是<a rel="nofollow" href="https://digital-photography-school.com/author/simonringsmuth/">西蒙·林斯穆斯 (Simon Ringsmuth)</a> 。</p><div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-full"> <span class="responsive-image wp-image-261507" style="width:1200px"><span class="space" style="width:1200px; padding-top:103.67%"></span><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="1200" height="1244" src="https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/best-circular-polarizing-filter-1005.jpg?resize=1200%2C1244&#038;ssl=1" alt="选择最好的圆偏光镜" class="wp-image-261507" srcset="https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/best-circular-polarizing-filter-1005.jpg?w=1200&amp;ssl=1 1200w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/best-circular-polarizing-filter-1005.jpg?resize=289%2C300&amp;ssl=1 289w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/best-circular-polarizing-filter-1005.jpg?resize=579%2C600&amp;ssl=1 579w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/best-circular-polarizing-filter-1005.jpg?resize=768%2C796&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/best-circular-polarizing-filter-1005.jpg?resize=717%2C743&amp;ssl=1 717w" sizes="(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px" data-recalc-dims="1" /></span></figure></div><p>圆偏光镜，也称为圆<a aria-label="polarizing filters (opens in a new tab)" href="https://digital-photography-school.com/how-to-use-and-buy-polarizing-filters/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" class="ek-link">偏光滤镜</a>，是拍摄风景、自然和野生动物图像的摄影师的必备工具，尤其是在湖泊、溪流或其他水体附近。它是一个简单的玻璃圈，几乎可以安装在任何相机镜头的前面，它可以增强色彩，同时减少不必要的眩光和反射。 （偏光滤镜还可以保护镜头免受灰尘、污垢和碎屑的影响。）</p><p>在最基本的层面上，圆偏光镜的工作原理是防止光线进入相机镜头，就像太阳镜阻止光线进入您的眼睛一样。然而，圆偏光镜的神奇之处（或更准确地说，是物理学）在于遮光过程。当您旋转圆偏振器的边框时，会阻止特定波长的光穿过并到达相机传感器。这意味着您可以<em>最大限度地减少</em>某些类型的光（例如反射和眩光），这使得圆偏光镜非常适合受水面反射困扰的场景。</p><p>圆形偏光镜易于使用，强烈推荐给任何喜欢拍摄户外照片的人，但它们也适用于其他类型的摄影，包括肖像和微距摄影。您可以找到各种价位的圆偏光镜，以下型号是目前可用的最佳选择！</p><div class="wp-block-image is-style-with-caption"><figure class="aligncenter size-full"> <span class="responsive-image wp-image-260571" style="width:1500px"><span class="space" style="width:1500px; padding-top:66.73%"></span><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="1500" height="1001" src="https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/best-circular-polarizers-gloss-mountains.jpg?resize=1500%2C1001&#038;ssl=1" alt="最佳圆偏光镜日落" class="wp-image-260571" srcset="https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/best-circular-polarizers-gloss-mountains.jpg?w=1500&amp;ssl=1 1500w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/best-circular-polarizers-gloss-mountains.jpg?resize=300%2C200&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/best-circular-polarizers-gloss-mountains.jpg?resize=600%2C400&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/best-circular-polarizers-gloss-mountains.jpg?resize=768%2C513&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/best-circular-polarizers-gloss-mountains.jpg?resize=90%2C60&amp;ssl=1 90w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/best-circular-polarizers-gloss-mountains.jpg?resize=717%2C478&amp;ssl=1 717w" sizes="(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px" data-recalc-dims="1" /></span><figcaption class="wp-element-caption">圆形偏光镜可最大限度地减少反射、减少眩光并增强色彩。它们很容易安装到相机镜头上，几乎可以改善任何拍摄效果。 </figcaption></figure></div><h2 class="wp-block-heading" class="wp-block-heading" data-section id="best-circular-polarizer-for-landscape-photographers-the-polarpro-quartzline"> 1.最适合风光摄影师的圆偏光镜：PolarPro QuartzLine</h2><div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-full"> <span class="responsive-image wp-image-260388" style="width:1000px"><span class="space" style="width:1000px; padding-top:42.4%"></span><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="1000" height="424" src="https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/best-circular-polarizers-polarpro-quartzline.jpg?resize=1000%2C424&#038;ssl=1" alt="最佳圆偏光镜 PolarPro QuartzLine 圆偏光镜滤光片" class="wp-image-260388" srcset="https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/best-circular-polarizers-polarpro-quartzline.jpg?w=1000&amp;ssl=1 1000w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/best-circular-polarizers-polarpro-quartzline.jpg?resize=300%2C127&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/