要优势是厚实的红色框架，在极端天气条件下易于抓握和精确转动。红色也不是为了好看，而是为了好看。它旨在帮助您轻松从装备包中的所有其他过滤器中识别过滤器。</p><p>最后，该滤镜仅牺牲一档光， <a aria-label="shooting in low light (opens in a new tab)" href="https://digital-photography-school.com/low-light-wildlife-photography/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" class="ek-link">在弱光</a>和/或使用<a href="https://digital-photography-school.com/aperture/" target="_blank" aria-label="maximum apertures (opens in a new tab)" rel="noreferrer noopener" class="ek-link">最大光圈</a>通常较小的长焦和超长焦镜头拍摄时为您提供更大的灵活性。 X4 CPL 并不便宜，但它能完成工作，是野生动物工作的绝佳选择。 </p><div class="wp-block-group is-vertical is-layout-flex wp-container-3 wp-block-group-is-layout-flex"><p><strong>优点：</strong></p><ul class="is-style-default"><li>厚实的外表盘使戴手套和在极端天气条件下也能轻松操作</li><li>红色环使该过滤器在装备包中易于区分</li></ul></div><div class="wp-block-group is-vertical is-layout-flex wp-container-4 wp-block-group-is-layout-flex"><p><strong>缺点：</strong></p><ul class="is-style-default"><li>非常高的价格限制了它对于新射手的实用性</li></ul></div><h2 class="wp-block-heading" class="wp-block-heading" data-section id="best-circular-polarizer-for-portrait-photographers-the-hoya-nxt-plus"> 3.最适合人像摄影师的圆偏光镜：Hoya NXT Plus</h2><div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-full"> <span class="responsive-image wp-image-260390" style="width:1500px"><span class="space" style="width:1500px; padding-top:46.93%"></span><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="1500" height="704" src="https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/best-circular-polarizers-hoya-nxt-plus.jpg?resize=1500%2C704&#038;ssl=1" alt="最佳圆偏光镜 Hoya NXT Plus 圆偏光镜" class="wp-image-260390" srcset="https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/best-circular-polarizers-hoya-nxt-plus.jpg?w=1500&amp;ssl=1 1500w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/best-circular-polarizers-hoya-nxt-plus.jpg?resize=300%2C141&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/b