igital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/photo-contest-pros-cons-1005.jpg?resize=289%2C300&amp;ssl=1 289w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/photo-contest-pros-cons-1005.jpg?resize=579%2C600&amp;ssl=1 579w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/photo-contest-pros-cons-1005.jpg?resize=768%2C796&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/photo-contest-pros-cons-1005.jpg?resize=717%2C743&amp;ssl=1 717w" sizes="(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px" data-recalc-dims="1" /></span></figure></div><p><em>本文于 2024 年 6 月更新，由 Simon Bond、Dale Wilson、 <a aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)" href="https://digital-photography-school.com/author/charlie-moss/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" class="ek-link">Charlie Moss</a>和<a aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)" href="https://digital-photography-school.com/author/pwc/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" class="ek-link">Peter West Carey</a>贡献。</em></p><p>如今，摄影比赛似乎无处不在，它们往往伴随着荣耀和受欢迎的承诺，更不用说大量引人注目的奖品了。但它们值得你花时间吗？作为初学者、业余爱好者，甚至是专业摄影师，你应该投入时间和精力参加摄影比赛吗？</p><p>在本文中，我们讨论摄影比赛对您、您的摄影和您的摄影职业有价值的原因。我们还探讨了比赛的阴暗面，并分享了一些（或全部！）摄影比赛不值得参加的一些原因。</p><p>当您读完后，您就会知道摄影比赛是否适合您！ </p><h2 class="wp-block-heading" class="wp-block-heading" data-section id="should-you-enter-a-photo-contest-the-benefits">你应该参加摄影比赛吗？好处</h2><div class="wp-block-image size-full wp-image-163564 is-style-with-caption"><figure class="aligncenter"> <span class="responsive-image wp-image-163564" style="width:1500px"><span class="space" style="width:1500px; padding-top:66.67%"></span><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="1500" height="1000" src="https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/Photo-contest-01.jpg?resize=1500%2C1000&#038;ssl=1" alt="你应该参加摄影比赛吗？" class="wp-image-163564" srcset="https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/Photo-contest-01.jpg?w=1500&amp;ssl=1 1500w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/Photo-contest-01.jpg?resize=300%2C200&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/Photo-contest-01.jpg?resize=768%2C512&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/Photo-contest-01.jpg?resize=600%2C400&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/Photo-contest-01.jpg?resize=90%2C60&amp;ssl=1 90w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/Photo-contest-01.jpg?resize=717%2C478&amp;ssl=1 717w" sizes="(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px" data-recalc-dims="1" /></span><figcaption class="wp-element-caption">良好的创造力和精美的照片是赢得比赛所需的两件事。</figcaption></figure></div><p>作为参加过相当多比赛的人，我可以自信地说，它们确实带来了真正的好处。以下是其中几个最大的： </p><h3 class="wp-block-heading" class="wp-block-heading" data-section id="photo-contests-give-you-direction"> 1.摄影比赛给你指明方向</h3><p>作为一名摄影师，有时你会有点漂移。这是否意味着你拍照的次数减少了<em>，或者</em>当你拍照时没有太多的凝聚力，这取决于你作为一名摄影师。</p><p>即使是那些对自己的摄影有清晰想法的人也会受益于明确的前进方向，而摄影比赛是实现这一目标的一个好方法。许多摄影比赛都有主题，当您希望构图最佳照片时，您会考虑这个主题。 </p><h3 class="wp-block-heading" class="wp-block-heading" data-section id="photo-contests-push-you-out-of-your-comfort-zone"> 2.摄影比赛让你走出舒适区</h3><p>就像主题竞赛可以给你指明方向一样，它<em>也</em>可以让你走出舒适区。</p><p>当然，如果比赛太超出你的舒适区，你可能会决定不参加，那也没关系。然而，在最终报名日期之前有足够的时间，并且主题不太吓人，比赛提供了磨练您在另一个<a href="https://digital-photography-school.com/types-of-photography/" target="_blank" aria-label="area of photography (opens in a new tab)" rel="noreferrer noopener" class="ek-link">摄影领域的</a>技能的绝佳机会。</p><p>比赛还允许您调整照片的方式以适应比赛的主题。你喜欢<a href="https://digital-photography-school.com/11-surefire-tips-for-improving-your-landscape-photography/" target="_blank" aria-label="landscape photography (opens in a new tab)" rel="noreferrer noopener" class="ek-link">风景摄影</a>吗？以<a href="https://digital-photography-school.com/7-steps-refraction-photography/" target="_blank" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)" rel="noreferrer noopener" class="ek-link">水晶球摄影</a>为主题的竞赛可能是学习这种新摄影技术同时应用您已经了解的风景摄影知识的绝佳机会。 </p><div class="wp-block-image size-full wp-image-163566 is-style-with-caption"><figure class="aligncenter"> <span class="responsive-image wp-image-163566" style="width:1500px"><span class="space" style="width:1500px; padding-top:66.67%"></span><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="1500" height="1000" src="https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/Photo-contest-03.jpg?resize=1500%2C1000&#038;ssl=1" alt="你应该参加摄影比赛吗？" class="wp-image-163566" srcset="https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/Photo-contest-03.jpg?w=1500&amp;ssl=1 1500w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/Photo-contest-03.jpg?resize=300%2C200&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/Photo-contest-03.jpg?resize=768%2C512&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/Photo-contest-03.jpg?resize=600%2C400&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/Photo-contest-03.jpg?resize=90%2C60&amp;ssl=1 90w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/Photo-contest-03.jpg?resize=717%2C478&amp;ssl=1 717w" sizes="(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px" data-recalc-dims="1" /></span><figcaption class="wp-element-caption">这张照片在 Flickr 每日竞赛中排名第一。 </figcaption></figure></div><h3 class="wp-block-heading" class="wp-block-heading" data-section id="photo-contests-help-you-focus-on-the-technical-details"> 3.摄影比赛帮助你专注于技术细节</h3><p>您总是以正确的<a aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)" href="https://digital-photography-school.com/aperture/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" class="ek-link">光圈</a>拍摄吗？你有没有把<a aria-label="ISO (opens in a new tab)" href="https://digital-photography-school.com/iso-settings/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" class="ek-link">ISO</a>调得太高过？ <a href="https://digital-photography-school.com/shutter-speed/" target="_blank" aria-label="shutter speed (opens in a new tab)" rel="noreferrer noopener" class="ek-link">快门速度</a>是否太慢？</p><p>当您为自己拍照时，很容易拍一张快速照片而忘记考虑技术细节。但是，当您为比赛拍照时，您肯定会获得正确的技术设置 - 只是因为您将专注于拍摄尽可能最好的图像！</p><p> （在比赛中，最小的优势都可以叠加起来，你需要利用一切优势来<a href="https://digital-photography-school.com/how-to-win-a-photography-competition/" target="_blank" aria-label="win a contest (opens in a new tab)" rel="noreferrer noopener" class="ek-link">赢得比赛</a>！） </p><h3 class="wp-block-heading" class="wp-block-heading" data-section id="photo-contests-are-a-great-way-to-gain-exposure"> 4.摄影比赛是获得曝光度的好方法</h3><p>您可以通过多种方式通过摄影比赛获得曝光度。那些持续几个月的比赛很可能每周都会产生前十名。这些精选照片最终可能不会赢得奖项，但如果您进入每周精选集，您的参赛作品将会吸引眼球。</p><p>除此之外，摄影比赛通常会产生获胜者以及大量获奖照片。再说一遍，如果您的照片受到赞扬，您可以期待获得不错的曝光度！ </p><div class="wp-block-image size-full wp-image-163565 is-style-with-caption"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"> <span class="responsive-image wp-image-163565" style="width:400px"><span class="space" style="width:400px; padding-top:150%"></span><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="400" height="600" src="https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/Photo-contest-02.jpg?resize=400%2C600&#038;ssl=1" alt="你应该参加摄影比赛吗？" class="wp-image-163565" srcset="https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/Photo-contest-02.jpg?resize=400%2C600&amp;ssl=1 400w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/Photo-contest-02.jpg?resize=200%2C300&amp;ssl=1 200w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/Photo-contest-02.jpg?resize=768%2C1151&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/Photo-contest-02.jpg?resize=717%2C1075&amp;ssl=1 717w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/Photo-contest-02.jpg?w=1500&amp;ssl=1 1500w" sizes="(max-width: 400px) 100vw, 400px" data-recalc-dims="1" /></span><figcaption class="wp-element-caption">这张照片几年前在韩国赢得了一场比赛。 </figcaption></figure></div><h3 class="wp-block-heading" class="wp-block-heading" data-section id="theres-the-potential-to-win-a-great-prize"> 5. 有机会赢取大奖！</h3><p>比赛规模越大，奖品就越大！当然，赢得任何比赛的大奖都是非常困难的，摄影更是如此。获胜者往往会获得千载难逢的摄影机会。</p><p>例如，国家地理竞赛通常设有前往异国他乡旅行的奖品，以及向知名摄影师学习的机会。 </p><h3 class="wp-block-heading" class="wp-block-heading" data-section id="you-can-be-inspired-by-other-entries"> 6.您可以从其他条目中获得灵感</h3><p>您可以在很多地方看到其他摄影师的作品。或多或少，任何形式的社交媒体都允许这样做。但摄影比赛是人们提交<em>最好的</em>照片的地方。</p><p>看看其他人如何解读比赛主题也可以给你自己的作品带来<a href="https://digital-photography-school.com/7-steps-find-inspiration-create-phenomenal-photographs/">灵感</a>。当然，抄袭并不是一个好主意，但审视风格、技术和执行可能会导致你自己拍照的方式发生改变。采纳别人的想法并将其融入到你的工作中是一个很好的改进方法！ </p><div class="wp-block-image size-full wp-image-163568 is-style-with-caption"><figure class="aligncenter"> <span class="responsive-image wp-image-163568" style="width:1197px"><span class="space" style="width:1197px; padding-top:51.29%"></span><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="1197" height="614" src="https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/Photo-contest-05.jpg?resize=1197%2C614&#038;ssl=1" alt="你应该参加摄影比赛吗？" class="wp-image-163568" srcset="https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/Photo-contest-05.jpg?w=1197&amp;ssl=1 1197w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/Photo-contest-05.jpg?resize=300%2C154&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/Photo-contest-05.jpg?resize=768%2C394&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/Photo-contest-05.jpg?resize=600%2C308&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/Photo-contest-05.jpg?resize=717%2C368&amp;ssl=1 717w" sizes="(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px" data-recalc-dims="1" /></span><figcaption class="wp-element-caption">像 Pixoto 这样的摄影比赛网站是了解您的摄影进展情况的好方法。 </figcaption></figure></div><h3 class="wp-block-heading" class="wp-block-heading" data-section id="doing-well-validates-you"> 7. 表现出色会验证你的价值</h3><p>所有的曝光度和潜在的奖项并不是您从摄影比赛中获得的唯一好处。拥有一张获奖作品——无论是总冠军还是受到赞扬的图片——都会给你的摄影带来验证。</p><p>另外，如果您想发展摄影业务，它也可以验证这一点！称自己为获奖摄影师的能力可以大有帮助。</p><p> （比赛的规模重要吗？老实说，参加规模较小的比赛，你获胜的机会更大！） </p><h3 class="wp-block-heading" class="wp-block-heading" data-section id="you-can-gain-feedback-on-your-images"> 8.您可以获得有关图像的反馈</h3><p>如果幸运的话，您可能会从比赛评委那里得到直接反馈。那些允许发表评论的竞赛也可能会导致其他参赛者对您的作品发表评论。</p><p>获得有关您所做工作的反馈是作为一名摄影师成长的好方法，而比赛是您可以获得一些重要信息的平台。 </p><div class="wp-block-image size-full wp-image-163567 is-style-with-caption"><figure class="aligncenter"> <span class="responsive-image wp-image-163567" style="width:1273px"><span class="space" style="width:1273px; padding-top:48.23%"></span><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="1273" height="614" src="https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/Photo-contest-04.jpg?resize=1273%2C614&#038;ssl=1" alt="你应该参加摄影比赛吗？" class="wp-image-163567" srcset="https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/Photo-contest-04.jpg?w=1273&amp;ssl=1 1273w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/Photo-contest-04.jpg?resize=300%2C145&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/Photo-contest-04.jpg?resize=768%2C370&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/Photo-contest-04.jpg?resize=600%2C289&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/Photo-contest-04.jpg?resize=717%2C346&amp;ssl=1 717w" sizes="(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px" data-recalc-dims="1" /></span><figcaption class="wp-element-caption">真正的大型比赛是非常难以获胜的！ </figcaption></figure></div><h2 class="wp-block-heading" class="wp-block-heading" data-section id="should-you-enter-a-photo-contest-the-drawbacks">你应该参加摄影比赛吗？缺点</h2><p>虽然参加摄影比赛有很多充分的理由，但也存在一些严重的缺点： </p><h3 class="wp-block-heading" class="wp-block-heading" data-section id="repeated-losses-can-be-hard">1. 反复亏损可能会很艰难</h3><p>我们并不总是赢得比赛。当然，每个人不可能赢得他们参加的每场比赛，但一次又一次地不进入候选名单可能会对我们的心理健康造成影响。</p><div class="wp-block-image is-style-with-caption"><figure class="aligncenter"> <span class="responsive-image wp-image-180691" style="width:1500px"><span class="space" style="width:1500px; padding-top:56.27%"></span><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="1500" height="844" src="https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/goals-for-photography-comps.jpg?resize=1500%2C844&#038;ssl=1" alt="你应该参加摄影比赛吗？" class="wp-image-180691" srcset="https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/goals-for-photography-comps.jpg?w=1500&amp;ssl=1 1500w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/goals-for-photography-comps.jpg?resize=300%2C169&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/goals-for-photography-comps.jpg?resize=768%2C432&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/goals-for-photography-comps.jpg?resize=600%2C338&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/goals-for-photography-comps.jpg?resize=717%2C403&amp;ssl=1 717w" sizes="(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px" data-recalc-dims="1" /></span><figcaption class="wp-element-caption">图片来源：查理·莫斯</figcaption></figure></div><p>你必须确保你参加比赛是有充分理由的，而不是那些在你面临拒绝时最终导致你情绪低落的比赛。即使对于经验丰富的摄影师来说，找到这些原因也可能很困难。</p><h3 class="wp-block-heading" class="wp-block-heading" data-section id="fees-can-be-hefty"> 2. 费用可能很高</h3><p>大多数摄影比赛都是免费的或象征性的报名费。不过，有些比赛会收取高额报名费。这取决于你，但有时最好避免这些竞争。没有理由收取高额入场费。一场好的比赛有很多参赛者，所以他们只需要收取每人象征性的参赛费即可支付费用。 </p><h3 class="wp-block-heading" class="wp-block-heading" data-section id="you-can-lose-the-rights-to-your-photos"> 3.您可能会失去照片的权利</h3><p>仔细阅读摄影比赛的条款和条件总是值得的。这是因为，当您参加比赛时，某些比赛会声称对您的照片拥有权利 - 即使您的照片不是获奖作品之一。</p><p>像这样的竞赛本质上是希望将您的作品用于商业广告。他们不会花钱购买库存图片，而是会举办摄影比赛来以这种方式获取广告材料。 </p><h3 class="wp-block-heading" class="wp-block-heading" data-section id="the-winning-images-arent-always-the-best"> 4. 获奖图像并不总是最好的</h3><div class="wp-block-image size-full wp-image-163569 is-style-default"><figure class="aligncenter"> <span class="responsive-image wp-image-163569" style="width:1168px"><span class="space" style="width:1168px; padding-top:48.12%"></span><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="1168" height="562" src="https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/Photo-contest-06.jpg?resize=1168%2C562&#038;ssl=1" alt="你应该参加摄影比赛吗？" class="wp-image-163569" srcset="https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/Photo-contest-06.jpg?w=1168&amp;ssl=1 1168w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/Photo-contest-06.jpg?resize=300%2C144&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/Photo-contest-06.jpg?resize=768%2C370&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/Photo-contest-06.jpg?resize=600%2C289&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/Photo-contest-06.jpg?resize=717%2C345&amp;ssl=1 717w" sizes="(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px" data-recalc-dims="1" /></span></figure></div><p>对我来说，这是一个大问题。获胜者是由一位法官还是由陪审团选出？还是通过点赞和分享投票的公开人气竞赛？</p><p>我更喜欢评审和评判的比赛，尤其是当我可以研究那些进行挑选的人时。我选择这些比赛是因为评委通常是摄影师或具有高级艺术教育和经验的人。我觉得这些比赛的竞争环境更加公平。</p><p>另一方面，小猫、日落、彩虹和过度饱和的山脉的图片整体上在投票互联网上表现得很好。我回避人气竞赛，因为a）我不是超级受欢迎，b）它们可能被操纵，并且经常为了漂亮的作品而埋葬伟大的作品。网站举办摄影比赛的主要原因是为了让自己更受欢迎和访问量更大，这就是这些类型的比赛存在的原因。 </p><h2 class="wp-block-heading" class="wp-block-heading" data-section id="should-you-enter-photo-competitions-final-words">你应该参加摄影比赛吗？最后的话</h2><p>摄影比赛当然对你来说很棒，而且绝对值得参加。我觉得它们帮助我发展了作为一名摄影师的实践，让我自由地进行实验，并让我在同行中得到评价。这三件事对我来说非常重要。</p><p>比赛也是结识新摄影师和发现新作品的绝佳机会。去当地的摄影俱乐部，甚至参加大型比赛的展览都可以既富有成效又令人兴奋！</p><p>但您必须采取措施了解为什么您想参加摄影比赛以及您参加比赛的理由是否充分。当踏入竞争激烈的摄影舞台时，您首先需要采取措施保护您的心理健康，并确保您不会让自己、您的财务或您的图像面临风险。</p><p>现在交给你：</p><p><em>您对摄影比赛有何感想？您之前输入过吗？您未来打算进入吗？在下面的评论中分享您的想法！</em></p><p>帖子<a rel="nofollow" href="https://digital-photography-school.com/reasons-to-enter-photo-contest/">你应该参加摄影比赛吗？优点和缺点</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://digital-photography-school.com">数码摄影学校</a>。它的作者是<a rel="nofollow" href="https://digital-photography-school.com/author/simon-bond/">西蒙·邦德</a>。</p> ; https://digital-photography-school.com/reasons-to-enter-photo-contest/feed/ 4
 15 个乡村风景摄影技巧（+ 示例） https://digital-photography-school.com/rural-landscape-photography/ https://digital-photography-school.com/rural-landscape-photography/#commentsJeremy Flint Sun, 16 Jun 2024 10:00:00 +0000 Photography Tips and TutorialsintermediateLandscape Photography https://digital-photography-school.com/?p=210691 <p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://digital-photography-school.com/rural-landscape-photography/">15个乡村风景摄影技巧（+示例）</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://digital-photography-school.com">数码摄影学校</a>。它的作者是<a rel="nofollow" href="https://digital-photography-school.com/author/jeremy-flint/">杰里米·弗林特</a>。</p><p>捕捉乡村风景的宁静和简单是有一些迷人的。当您远离城市的喧嚣时，迎接您的是一个完全不同的世界——这个世界提供了独特的机会来展示未受破坏的远景、风化的建筑以及在其他地方很难找到的宁静的隔离感。但是虽然[…]</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://digital-photography-school.com/rural-landscape-photography/">15个乡村风景摄影技巧（+示例）</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://digital-photography-school.com">数码摄影学校</a>。它的作者是<a rel="nofollow" href="https://digital-photography-school.com/author/jeremy-flint/">杰里米·弗林特</a>。</p> ; <p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://digital-photography-school.com/rural-landscape-photography/">15个乡村风景摄影技巧（+示例）</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://digital-photography-school.com">数码摄影学校</a>。它的作者是<a rel="nofollow" href="https://digital-photography-school.com/author/jeremy-flint/">杰里米·弗林特</a>。</p><div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-full"> <span class="responsive-image wp-image-261445" style="width:1200px"><span class="space" style="width:1200px; padding-top:103.67%"></span><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="1200" height="1244" src="https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/rural-landscape-photography-1006.jpg?resize=1200%2C1244&#038;ssl=1" alt="如何拍摄乡村风景" class="wp-image-261445" srcset="https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/rural-landscape-photography-1006.jpg?w=1200&amp;ssl=1 1200w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/rural-landscape-photography-1006.jpg?resize=289%2C300&amp;ssl=1 289w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/rural-landscape-photography-1006.jpg?resize=579%2C600&amp;ssl=1 579w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/rural-landscape-photography-1006.jpg?resize=768%2C796&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/rural-landscape-photography-1006.jpg?resize=717%2C743&amp;ssl=1 717w" sizes="(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px" data-recalc-dims="1" /></span></figure></div><p>捕捉乡村<a href="https://digital-photography-school.com/11-surefire-tips-for-improving-your-landscape-photography/" target="_blank" aria-label="landscapes (opens in a new tab)" rel="noreferrer noopener" class="ek-link">风景</a>的宁静和简单是有一些迷人的。当您远离城市的喧嚣时，迎接您的是一个完全不同的世界——这个世界提供了独特的机会来展示未受破坏的远景、风化的建筑以及在其他地方很难找到的宁静的隔离感。</p><p>然而，虽然乡村风景摄影可以令人心碎地美丽，但它也需要独特的方法。您不想像拍摄<a href="https://digital-photography-school.com/mountain-landscape-photography/" target="_blank" aria-label="mountain vistas (opens in a new tab)" rel="noreferrer noopener" class="ek-link">山景</a>或<a href="https://digital-photography-school.com/simple-tips-improve-travel-photography-photographing-deserts/" target="_blank" aria-label="sweeping deserts (opens in a new tab)" rel="noreferrer noopener" class="ek-link">广阔的沙漠</a>那样拍摄乡村场景，而这正是本文派上用场的地方。我花了很多时间捕捉乡村美景，在本指南中，我分享：</p><ul><li>乡村风景照片的最佳照明</li><li>让你的作文更上一层楼的关键技巧</li><li>利用天气取得显着效果的方法</li><li>多得多！</li></ul><p>让我们开始吧，从……开始</p><h2 class="wp-block-heading" class="wp-block-heading" data-section id="what-is-rural-landscape-photography">什么是乡村风光摄影？</h2><p> “乡村风景摄影”一词常常让人联想到田园诗般的农田、古朴的小屋和一望无际的开阔田野。但这不仅仅是一个漂亮的背景。这种摄影风格还可以提供叙事内容，讲述在我们快节奏的现代世界中经常被忽视的地方和生活方式的故事。</p><p>您可能会从废弃的农舍、生锈的拖拉机，甚至是穿过草地的羊群中找到灵感。与城市景观通常关注建筑的宏伟和人造结构的复杂性不同，乡村景观提供了更有机的东西。在这里，美丽在于简单。即使是开阔田野中的一棵树也可以成为照片的焦点。</p><p>捕捉乡村生活的本质非常重要。无论您是展示宁静湖泊的宁静还是古老谷仓的粗犷魅力，这些图像都会邀请观看者停下来思考。当谈到创建影响观看者的图像时，不仅仅要制作一张具有视觉吸引力的照片，还要与观众建立<em>情感</em>联系。</p><p>现在您已经了解了乡村风景摄影的真正<em>含义</em>，这里有一些技巧可以帮助您拍摄自己的乡村风景： </p><h2 class="wp-block-heading" class="wp-block-heading" data-section id="experiment-with-different-rural-subjects"> 1. 不同农村主体的实验</h2><div class="wp-block-image caption-align-center"><figure class="aligncenter size-full"><span class="responsive-image wp-image-211827" style="width:1500px"><span class="space" style="width:1500px; padding-top:66.67%"></span><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="1500" height="1000" src="https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/8G6A5133.jpg?resize=1500%2C1000&#038;ssl=1" alt="有水和牧场的乡村景观" class="wp-image-211827" srcset="https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/8G6A5133.jpg?w=1500&amp;ssl=1 1500w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/8G6A5133.jpg?resize=300%2C200&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/8G6A5133.jpg?resize=600%2C400&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/8G6A5133.jpg?resize=768%2C512&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/8G6A5133.jpg?resize=90%2C60&amp;ssl=1 90w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/8G6A5133.jpg?resize=717%2C478&amp;ssl=1 717w" sizes="(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px" data-recalc-dims="1" /></span></figure></div><p>乡村风景摄影为您提供捕捉各种有趣主题的机会，包括：</p><ul><li>旧谷仓</li><li>塔楼</li><li>教堂</li><li>机械</li><li>年久失修的建筑物</li></ul><p>您还可能包括现代乡村元素，例如房屋、农场等。</p><p>进行乡村摄影时，不要将自己局限于单一主题。相反，尝试所有这些不同的选项。如果您发现一个旧谷仓，请花时间拍摄它 - 如果您发现一个闪亮的新农舍，也请拍摄它！ </p><h2 class="wp-block-heading" class="wp-block-heading" data-section id="shoot-when-the-light-is-soft"> 2.光线柔和时拍摄</h2><div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-full"><span class="responsive-image wp-image-211829" style="width:1500px"><span class="space" style="width:1500px; padding-top:66.67%"></span><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="1500" height="1000" src="https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/IMG_8966.jpg?resize=1500%2C1000&#038;ssl=1" alt="雾中的岩石" class="wp-image-211829" srcset="https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/IMG_8966.jpg?w=1500&amp;ssl=1 1500w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/IMG_8966.jpg?resize=300%2C200&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/IMG_8966.jpg?resize=600%2C400&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/IMG_8966.jpg?resize=768%2C512&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/IMG_8966.jpg?resize=90%2C60&amp;ssl=1 90w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/IMG_8966.jpg?resize=717%2C478&amp;ssl=1 717w" sizes="(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px" data-recalc-dims="1" /></span></figure></div><p>您可以在一天中的任何时间拍摄乡村风景……</p><p> …但是<a href="https://digital-photography-school.com/tips-for-creating-landscape-photos-during-the-golden-hour/" target="_blank" aria-label="golden hour (opens in a new tab)" rel="noreferrer noopener" class="ek-link">黄金时段</a>、 <a href="https://digital-photography-school.com/new-photographers-guide-to-blue-hour/" target="_blank" aria-label="blue hour (opens in a new tab)" rel="noreferrer noopener" class="ek-link">蓝色时段</a>和<a href="https://digital-photography-school.com/the-night-sky-in-landscape-photography/" target="_blank" aria-label="nighttime (opens in a new tab)" rel="noreferrer noopener" class="ek-link">夜间</a>是携带相机外出的最佳时间。光线柔和且迷人，非常适合乡村主题。</p><p>黄金时段提供神奇的光芒，可以提升您的图像，而蓝色时段则添加冷色调，非常适合老房子和废弃建筑等主题。</p><p>如果您喜欢在夜间拍摄，则可能需要更具创意，因为建筑物的灯光可能会关闭。我建议使用手电筒并在拍摄对象上涂抹光线，以使其在最终照片中更加明显。</p><h2 class="wp-block-heading" class="wp-block-heading" data-section id="use-a-wide-angle-lens"> 3.使用广角镜头</h2><p>您可能听说过一张图片胜过一千个文字。但如果你可以扩展这个叙述呢？ <a href="https://digital-photography-school.com/7-ways-to-get-more-out-of-a-wide-angle-lens/" target="_blank" aria-label="wide-angle lens (opens in a new tab)" rel="noreferrer noopener" class="ek-link">广角镜头</a>可以帮助您做到这一点。它允许您拍摄场景的更大部分，从而将乡村环境变成史诗般的景色。</p><p>例如，如果您站在向日葵田中，使用<em>标准</em>镜头，您可能会捕捉到这些阳光明媚的花朵的可爱景象。但超广角镜头可以让您拍摄整个田野、地平线，甚至头顶戏剧性的天空。其结果是一张感觉非常<em>真实的</em>照片，如果做得好，可以将观众带入风景中。</p><p>现在，使用超广角镜头不仅仅是指点和拍摄。您应该考虑一些事项以最大限度地发挥其潜力。其一，要注意透视变形。镜头距离前景中的物体越近，它们相对于背景就会显得越大——虽然极端的透视畸变并不总是坏事，但在某些情况下，它可能会显得不自然。透视畸变还可能导致垂直线会聚，这可以在后处理中纠正<em>，但</em>会导致帧边缘周围的像素丢失。当你构图时请记住这一点！</p><p>另外，不要忘记选择一个焦点。由于您将捕捉如此多的场景，因此观看者的眼睛很容易走神。放置得当的谷仓、树木，甚至动物都可以作为视觉锚点，帮助观众欣赏你的广角镜头。 </p><h2 class="wp-block-heading" class="wp-block-heading" data-section id="think-about-the-sky-and-the-weather"> 4. 想想天空（和天气）</h2><p>想要拍摄<em>创意</em>田园风光照片吗？确保你花足够的时间思考<a aria-label="sky (opens in a new tab)" href="https://digital-photography-school.com/6-tips-for-capturing-dramatic-skies-in-your-landscape-photography/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" class="ek-link">天空</a>，它有能力提升——或毁掉——你的形象。</p><p>问问自己：我想要捕捉什么类型的氛围？要拍摄喜怒无常的照片，您可以在雨、雪或雾期间出发。要获得乐观、色彩丰富的图像，请在强烈的阳光下拍摄。</p><p>顺便说一句，您需要考虑天空是否应该包含在您的照片中。在阴天（没有太多的云彩情绪，但也没有任何漂亮的天空颜色），您可能想要完全忽略天空。但在暴风雨的日子，或在戏剧性的日出和日落期间，天空会给您的照片增添额外的维度。</p><div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-full"> <span class="responsive-image wp-image-211823" style="width:750px"><span class="space" style="width:750px; padding-top:66.67%"></span><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="750" height="500" src="https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/3F6A7592_.jpg?resize=750%2C500&#038;ssl=1" alt="高耸的乡村景观与远处的城市" class="wp-image-211823" srcset="https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/3F6A7592_.jpg?w=750&amp;ssl=1 750w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/3F6A7592_.jpg?resize=300%2C200&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/3F6A7592_.jpg?resize=600%2C400&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/3F6A7592_.jpg?resize=90%2C60&amp;ssl=1 90w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/3F6A7592_.jpg?resize=717%2C478&amp;ssl=1 717w" sizes="(max-width: 750px) 100vw, 750px" data-recalc-dims="1" /></span> </figure></div><h2 class="wp-block-heading" class="wp-block-heading" data-section id="use-architecture-to-anchor-the-viewer"> 5.利用建筑来锚定观众</h2><p>我发现建筑是乡村风景摄影的一个重要焦点；它常常与自然形成美丽的对比。</p><p>传统结构可以很好地发挥作用，尤其是具有崎岖、风化外墙的谷仓。它们会营造出质朴的外观和感觉，真正激发观众的想象力。例如，看一下这张旧谷仓的图像：</p><div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-full"> <span class="responsive-image wp-image-211832" style="width:1000px"><span class="space" style="width:1000px; padding-top:66.7%"></span><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="1000" height="667" src="https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/3F6A2659.jpg?resize=1000%2C667&#038;ssl=1" alt="有山和树的谷仓 如何拍摄乡村风景" class="wp-image-211832" srcset="https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/3F6A2659.jpg?w=1000&amp;ssl=1 1000w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/3F6A2659.jpg?resize=300%2C200&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/3F6A2659.jpg?resize=600%2C400&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/3F6A2659.jpg?resize=768%2C512&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/3F6A2659.jpg?resize=90%2C60&amp;ssl=1 90w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/3F6A2659.jpg?resize=717%2C478&amp;ssl=1 717w" sizes="(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px" data-recalc-dims="1" /></span></figure></div><p>其他构成有趣乡村景观图像的建筑包括废弃的房屋、旧农场和人们搬到城市时留下的建筑物。您可以在周围的乡村捕捉到它们老化、破败的特征。 </p><h2 class="wp-block-heading" class="wp-block-heading" data-section id="try-a-telephoto-focal-length"> 6.尝试长焦焦距</h2><p>如果您已阅读技巧#3，您可能会认为广角镜头是拍摄乡村风景的理想选择。你没有错；广角玻璃是捕捉广阔乡村的绝佳工具。但这不是唯一有效的方法！</p><p>您会看到， <a href="https://digital-photography-school.com/10-tips-for-great-telephoto-photography/" target="_blank" aria-label="telephoto lens (opens in a new tab)" rel="noreferrer noopener" class="ek-link">长焦镜头</a>（例如 70-200 毫米型号）可以打开通往亲密、细致的乡村风景世界的大门。广角镜头可以捕捉一览无余的远景，而长焦镜头可以让您放大细节。想象一下捕捉旧谷仓木材的纹理或栅栏柱之间蜘蛛网的复杂图案。</p><p>此外，长焦镜头的压缩效果可以使远处的物体显得更近，从而使您可以在单个帧中分层不同的元素以获得拼贴画般的效果。</p><p>放大时，您需要注意图像质量问题。长焦镜头更容易因相机抖动而变得模糊，因此请使用三脚架或相机内稳定等稳定技术来保持照片清晰。</p><p>底线：长焦镜头可以让您讲述不同的故事。您不是展示乡村场景的广阔开放，而是邀请观众靠过来，靠近观察，这可能<em>非常</em>有效！ </p><h2 class="wp-block-heading" class="wp-block-heading" data-section id="dont-be-afraid-to-include-people-in-your-photos"> 7. 不要害怕在照片中加入人物</h2><p>人们常常在乡村创作伟大的题材！毕竟，它们是乡村景观不可分割的一部分。</p><p>乡村环境的一大优点是始终有人类活动。在农场，可以看到人们照料他们的土地和农场动物。人们可能会外出骑马、锻炼身体或操作机器，所有这些都可以构成美丽的图像。</p><div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-full"> <span class="responsive-image wp-image-211826" style="width:1500px"><span class="space" style="width:1500px; padding-top:66.67%"></span><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="1500" height="1000" src="https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/8G6A4916.jpg?resize=1500%2C1000&#038;ssl=1" alt="牧羊人与羊" class="wp-image-211826" srcset="https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/8G6A4916.jpg?w=1500&amp;ssl=1 1500w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/8G6A4916.jpg?resize=300%2C200&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/8G6A4916.jpg?resize=600%2C400&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/8G6A4916.jpg?resize=768%2C512&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/8G6A4916.jpg?resize=90%2C60&amp;ssl=1 90w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/8G6A4916.jpg?resize=717%2C478&amp;ssl=1 717w" sizes="(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px" data-recalc-dims="1" /></span> </figure></div><h2 class="wp-block-heading" class="wp-block-heading" data-section id="incorporate-animals-into-your-shots"> 8. 将动物融入到你的镜头中</h2><p>当你到乡村去的时候，你<em>总会</em>遇到动物。这些可能是野生动物，它们通常隐藏得很好，很难拍摄。或者它们可能是圈养动物，例如马、牛和羊。</p><p>充分利用这些拍照机会。尝试不同形式的照明来创建独特的农场动物图像。当天气有雾时，不要害怕拍摄；它将提供大量令人惊叹的游戏氛围：</p><div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-full"> <span class="responsive-image wp-image-211822" style="width:1500px"><span class="space" style="width:1500px; padding-top:66.67%"></span><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="1500" height="1000" src="https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/3F6A1510.jpg?resize=1500%2C1000&#038;ssl=1" alt="迷雾中的马匹" class="wp-image-211822" srcset="https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/3F6A1510.jpg?w=1500&amp;ssl=1 1500w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/3F6A1510.jpg?resize=300%2C200&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/3F6A1510.jpg?resize=600%2C400&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/3F6A1510.jpg?resize=768%2C512&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/3F6A1510.jpg?resize=90%2C60&amp;ssl=1 90w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/3F6A1510.jpg?resize=717%2C478&amp;ssl=1 717w" sizes="(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px" data-recalc-dims="1" /></span> </figure></div><h2 class="wp-block-heading" class="wp-block-heading" data-section id="capture-some-rural-landscapes-at-night"> 9. 拍摄一些夜晚的乡村风景</h2><p>月亮和星星下的乡村风景有一种神奇的感觉。夜间提供了一种独特的氛围，<em>需要</em>您的镜头来捕捉。也就是说，虽然<a href="https://digital-photography-school.com/the-night-sky-in-landscape-photography/" target="_blank" aria-label="night is visually compelling (opens in a new tab)" rel="noreferrer noopener" class="ek-link">夜晚在视觉上引人注目</a>，但它也带来了一系列重大挑战。</p><p>首先，您需要考虑相机设置。由于您将在昏暗的光线下工作，因此您需要使用较长的快门速度，这意味着您的相机必须保持静止更长时间。对于这种类型的摄影， <a href="https://digital-photography-school.com/best-tripods-for-landscape-photography/" target="_blank" aria-label="sturdy tripod (opens in a new tab)" rel="noreferrer noopener" class="ek-link">坚固的三脚架</a>不是可选的；这是必备的。您还可以考虑使用远程快门释放来最大程度地减少相机抖动的可能性。如果你的快门速度太长，你可以提高 ISO，但要小心；高 ISO 会产生噪点，过多的噪点会导致细节明显丢失。</p><p>但设置只是等式的一部分。夜间也存在潜在风险，尤其是在农村地区。您距离城市很远，而且援助并不触手可及。规划至关重要。确保您清楚自己的位置，告诉别人您要去哪里，并始终携带可靠的光源。安全永远应该是您的第一要务。</p><p>在装备方面，除了三脚架之外，还要考虑镜头的选择。具有较宽最大光圈（如 f/1.8 或 f/2.8）的镜头可以让更多光线进入，帮助您保持较短的快门速度，同时保持较低的 ISO。当然，使用大光圈会导致景深变浅，因此您需要<em>非常</em>仔细地对焦，以最大限度地提高整个画面的清晰度。</p><p>最后，最好的装备和技术不能取代计划。因此，在出发之前，请花一些时间在白天侦察您的位置，以确定夜间拍摄的最佳地点！ </p><h2 class="wp-block-heading" class="wp-block-heading" data-section id="carefully-position-your-subject-for-better-compositions"> 10. 仔细定位拍摄对象以获得更好的构图</h2><p>与所有风景摄影一样， <a href="https://digital-photography-school.com/4-rules-of-composition-for-landscape-photography/" target="_blank" aria-label="composition (opens in a new tab)" rel="noreferrer noopener" class="ek-link">构图</a>是拍摄最佳乡村照片的重要组成部分，因此正确构图非常重要。</p><p>首先问自己：我的主要主题是什么？这个场景最让我感兴趣的是什么？然后确定要将主要拍摄对象放置在画面中的位置。</p><p>您可以将其放在镜头的正中央，也可以将其放在一侧。记住<a aria-label="rule of thirds (opens in a new tab)" href="https://digital-photography-school.com/rule-of-thirds/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" class="ek-link">三分法则</a>通常是有好处的，它建议您将主要拍摄对象放置在画面的三分之一处（垂直或水平）。</p><div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-full"> <span class="responsive-image wp-image-211828" style="width:750px"><span class="space" style="width:750px; padding-top:66.67%"></span><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="750" height="500" src="https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/IMG_0337-A_.jpg?resize=750%2C500&#038;ssl=1" alt="迷雾寺" class="wp-image-211828" srcset="https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/IMG_0337-A_.jpg?w=750&amp;ssl=1 750w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/IMG_0337-A_.jpg?resize=300%2C200&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/IMG_0337-A_.jpg?resize=600%2C400&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/IMG_0337-A_.jpg?resize=90%2C60&amp;ssl=1 90w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/IMG_0337-A_.jpg?resize=717%2C478&amp;ssl=1 717w" sizes="(max-width: 750px) 100vw, 750px" data-recalc-dims="1" /></span> </figure></div><h2 class="wp-block-heading" class="wp-block-heading" data-section id="try-minimalist-composition-techniques"> 11.尝试极简主义构图技巧</h2><p>您是否曾经看过一张照片，并因其简单而立即感到平静？这就是<a href="https://digital-photography-school.com/photographic-minimalism/" target="_blank" aria-label="minimalist composition (opens in a new tab)" rel="noreferrer noopener" class="ek-link">极简构图</a>的力量。乡村景观往往非常<em>宽敞</em>，这意味着它们为这种方法提供了很多机会。想象一下广阔的田野、一棵孤独的树，或者荒无人烟的地方一个孤独的谷仓。有时，少即是多。</p><p>为了获得最佳的简约图像，首先要确定您的主题。无论是远处的一匹孤独的马还是田野中央的一棵树，您都需要仔细地对其进行构图。使用三分法等技巧，以吸引眼球的方式放置拍摄对象，同时在其周围留下大量的负空间，以创造更加冥想、宁静的效果。</p><p>极简主义工具箱中的另一个工具是<a href="https://digital-photography-school.com/how-to-use-leading-lines-for-better-compositions/" target="_blank" aria-label="leading lines (opens in a new tab)" rel="noreferrer noopener" class="ek-link">引导线</a>。道路、栅栏或成排的农作物可以将观看者的视线直接引向您的主要主题。例如，一条通往一栋孤独房​​屋的蜿蜒道路可以构成引人注目的构图。</p><p>还有一点提示：极简主义构图通常受益于有限的调色板。太多的颜色会分散注意力，将注意力从主要拍摄对象上转移开。如果景观不提供自然的颜色限制，请考虑将图像转换为黑白。这是一个经典的选择，通常可以简化最复杂的主题。 </p><h2 class="wp-block-heading" class="wp-block-heading" data-section id="use-the-right-settings-for-sharp-photos"> 12.使用正确的设置拍摄清晰的照片</h2><p>对于乡村风景摄影，最佳相机设置取决于您要拍摄的照片以及天气。</p><p>一般来说，f/8 的中档<a aria-label="aperture (opens in a new tab)" href="https://digital-photography-school.com/aperture/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" class="ek-link">光圈</a>将为您提供足够的<a aria-label="depth of field (opens in a new tab)" href="https://digital-photography-school.com/understanding-depth-field-beginners/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" class="ek-link">景深</a>，让一切都清晰对焦，这通常效果很好。但如果您想让画面的某些部分失焦，请使用更大的光圈 - f/4 是一个很好的起点，f/2.8 会进一步减少对焦区域。</p><p>您需要将<a href="https://digital-photography-school.com/iso-settings/" target="_blank" aria-label="ISO (opens in a new tab)" rel="noreferrer noopener" class="ek-link">ISO</a>保持在相当低的水平，因此选择 100 到 400 之间的 ISO。任何更高的 ISO 值，您都会面临产生不必要的噪点的风险 - 但如果您在弱光下拍摄，ISO 为 800 或更高可能还是有必要的。</p><p>至于<a href="https://digital-photography-school.com/shutter-speed/" target="_blank" aria-label="shutter speeds (opens in a new tab)" rel="noreferrer noopener" class="ek-link">快门速度</a>：如果您的场景包含移动主体（例如摇摆的马），则您至少需要 1/100 秒甚至可能更多。对于没有明显运动的场景，我仍然建议将快门速度保持在 1/60 秒左右（尽管您也可以选择使用三脚架）。</p><p>当然，快门速度通常需要进行实验。因此，不要害怕测试不同的速度，看看哪种速度效果最好。 </p><h2 class="wp-block-heading" class="wp-block-heading" data-section id="head-out-when-the-weather-is-bad"> 13.天气不好时外出</h2><div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-full"><span class="responsive-image wp-image-211825" style="width:1500px"><span class="space" style="width:1500px; padding-top:66.67%"></span><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="1500" height="1000" src="https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/3F6A8317.jpg?resize=1500%2C1000&#038;ssl=1" alt="云雾缭绕的丘陵和树木" class="wp-image-211825" srcset="https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/3F6A8317.jpg?w=1500&amp;ssl=1 1500w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/3F6A8317.jpg?resize=300%2C200&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/3F6A8317.jpg?resize=600%2C400&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/3F6A8317.jpg?resize=768%2C512&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/3F6A8317.jpg?resize=90%2C60&amp;ssl=1 90w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/3F6A8317.jpg?resize=717%2C478&amp;ssl=1 717w" sizes="(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px" data-recalc-dims="1" /></span></figure></div><p>这是真的：</p><p>明亮、阳光明媚的日子，尤其是日出或日落前后，为拍摄乡村风景照片提供了绝佳的条件。</p><p>但在恶劣天气下拍摄可以给场景带来另一个层次的戏剧性。例如，雾可以增加大量的气氛，雨可以看起来非常沉闷，而<a href="https://digital-photography-school.com/5-tips-better-winter-landscape-photography/" target="_blank" aria-label="snow (opens in a new tab)" rel="noreferrer noopener" class="ek-link">雪</a>可以将您的照片提升到新的高度。</p><p>所以不要把自己限制在好天气里。相反，要准备好在乡村景观看起来引人注目时进行拍摄（这通常是在最不愉快的日子！）。 </p><h2 class="wp-block-heading" class="wp-block-heading" data-section id="use-a-drone-to-capture-aerial-images"> 14.使用无人机捕捉航拍图像</h2><p><a href="https://digital-photography-school.com/how-to-use-drones-to-do-stunning-aerial-photography/" target="_blank" aria-label="Drones (opens in a new tab)" rel="noreferrer noopener" class="ek-link">无人机</a>是相机世界中相对较新的技术，它们是以全新的视角拍摄乡村照片的绝佳方式。使用无人机，您可以从其他方式无法到达的角度捕捉图像，并彻底<em>改变</em>您观看乡村景观的方式。盘旋在农田上空，漂浮在乡村建筑上空，或者捕捉一览无余的空中景色……无人机确实可以为您的投资组合增添<em>惊喜</em>。</p><p>但在启动之前，让我们先谈谈合法性和安全性。驾驶无人机有其自己的一套规则。您可能需要注册您的无人机和/或参加认证测试，因此在将您的无人机发射到空中之前，请确保检查了所有复选框。此外，请务必检查当地法规并尊重私有财产。确保仅在指定区域飞行，并与人和动物保持安全距离。</p><p>一旦您的无人机升空，您需要记住一些事情。首先，即使是大功率无人机的电池寿命也往往<em>非常</em>有限。您可能只能在空中停留 20-30 分钟（或更短！）的时间，因此快速而准确的行动非常重要。 （我还建议购买一两块额外的电池，特别是如果您打算定期进行无人机摄影。这会让您的生活变得更加轻松！）</p><p>其次，改变无人机的高度会极大地影响构图。较低的海拔可能会为您提供农作物图案的详细图像，而较高的有利位置可以捕捉到广阔的乡村环境的壮丽景色。尝试不同的高度以获得不同的镜头。</p><p> （也就是说，请记住任何相关的高度限制；例如，在撰写本文时，美国以及许多其他国家/地区的休闲无人机操作员必须保持在 400 英尺以下。）</p><p>另外，要特别注意灯光！您可以在日出和日落时拍摄乡村地区的戏剧性照片，此时光线柔和且呈金色，但如果您在接近中午时外出，此时光线坚硬且对比度高，您<em>也</em>可以获得有趣的照片。始终考虑光线的方向，并选择适合您视觉的光线类型。</p><p>如果您还没有无人机，值得一提的是，您绝对<em>不需要</em>高端无人机来开始拍摄。有很多适合初学者的选项，可提供良好的图像质量和易用性，因此您不必急于购买价值 3000 美元的无人机！ </p><h2 class="wp-block-heading" class="wp-block-heading" data-section id="take-a-walk-in-the-landscape"> 15.在风景中散步</h2><p>这是您最后的乡村风景摄影技巧：</p><p>散步。带上相机出发吧。玩得开心。</p><p>毕竟，乡村是一个美丽的地方，你永远不知道会发现什么。您可能会遇到野生动物、盛开的花朵、干草堆等等——所有这些都是绝佳的摄影主题！</p><div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-full"> <span class="responsive-image wp-image-211830" style="width:1500px"><span class="space" style="width:1500px; padding-top:66.67%"></span><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="1500" height="1000" src="https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/Nature-photos-03.jpg?resize=1500%2C1000&#038;ssl=1" alt="森林里的风信子" class="wp-image-211830" srcset="https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/Nature-photos-03.jpg?w=1500&amp;ssl=1 1500w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/Nature-photos-03.jpg?resize=300%2C200&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/Nature-photos-03.jpg?resize=600%2C400&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/Nature-photos-03.jpg?resize=768%2C512&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/Nature-photos-03.jpg?resize=90%2C60&amp;ssl=1 90w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/Nature-photos-03.jpg?resize=717%2C478&amp;ssl=1 717w" sizes="(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px" data-recalc-dims="1" /></span> </figure></div><h2 class="wp-block-heading" class="wp-block-heading" data-section id="rural-landscape-photography-tips-final-words">乡村风光摄影技巧：最后的话</h2><p>我们探索了很多领域，从镜头选择到构图技术、夜间拍摄，甚至航空摄影。乡村风景摄影有着丰富的可能性，每一张都提供了我们通常认为理所当然的世界的独特视角！</p><p>那就出去看看乡村风景吧。随身携带相机，并尝试我上面分享的技巧。也许您会发现超广角镜头与您的艺术视野产生共鸣。或者也许长焦镜头的亲密感会吸引您。不要限制自己，很快您就会捕捉到一些令人惊叹的图像！</p><p>现在交给你：</p><p><em>您有最喜欢的乡村风景题材吗？您对于构图、灯光或主题选择有什么我们遗漏的建议吗？在下面的评论中分享您的想法（和图片！）。</em></p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://digital-photography-school.com/rural-landscape-photography/">15个乡村风景摄影技巧（+示例）</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://digital-photography-school.com">数码摄影学校</a>。它的作者是<a rel="nofollow" href="https://digital-photography-school.com/author/jeremy-flint/">杰里米·弗林特</a>。</p> ; https://digital-photography-school.com/rural-landscape-photography/feed/ 4
如何有效地使用纵向角度：视觉指南https://digital-photography-school.com/portrait-angles-for-beginners-a-visual-guide/ https://digital-photography-school.com/portrait-angles-for-beginners-a-visual-guide/#commentsMeredith Clark Sat, 15 Jun 2024 10:00:00 +0000 Photography Tips and TutorialsbeginnerPortrait Photography https://digital-photography-school.com/?p=105818 <p>文章《 <a rel="nofollow" href="https://digital-photography-school.com/portrait-angles-for-beginners-a-visual-guide/">如何有效地使用肖像角度：视觉指南》</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://digital-photography-school.com">《数码摄影学校》</a>上。它的作者是<a rel="nofollow" href="https://digital-photography-school.com/author/meredithclark/">梅雷迪思·克拉克</a>。</p><p>在创作一幅成功的肖像时，有很多变化的部分。我们经常谈论灯光、构图和相机装备，虽然这三件事对于创建最终图像都很重要，但它们并不是唯一起作用的变量。捕捉一流肖像的另一个重要部分是仔细[...]</p><p>文章<a rel="nofollow" href="https://digital-photography-school.com/portrait-angles-for-beginners-a-visual-guide/">如何有效地使用肖像角度：视觉指南</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://digital-photography-school.com">数码摄影学校</a>上。它的作者是<a rel="nofollow" href="https://digital-photography-school.com/author/meredithclark/">梅雷迪思·克拉克</a>。</p> ; <p>文章<a rel="nofollow" href="https://digital-photography-school.com/portrait-angles-for-beginners-a-visual-guide/">如何有效地使用肖像角度：视觉指南</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://digital-photography-school.com">数码摄影学校</a>上。它的作者是<a rel="nofollow" href="https://digital-photography-school.com/author/meredithclark/">梅雷迪思·克拉克</a>。</p><div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-full"> <span class="responsive-image wp-image-261439" style="width:1200px"><span class="space" style="width:1200px; padding-top:103.67%"></span><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="1200" height="1244" src="https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/portrait-angle-photography-1006.jpg?resize=1200%2C1244&#038;ssl=1" alt="探索纵向角度的力量" class="wp-image-261439" srcset="https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/portrait-angle-photography-1006.jpg?w=1200&amp;ssl=1 1200w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/portrait-angle-photography-1006.jpg?resize=289%2C300&amp;ssl=1 289w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/portrait-angle-photography-1006.jpg?resize=579%2C600&amp;ssl=1 579w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/portrait-angle-photography-1006.jpg?resize=768%2C796&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/portrait-angle-photography-1006.jpg?resize=717%2C743&amp;ssl=1 717w" sizes="(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px" data-recalc-dims="1" /></span></figure></div><p>当谈到<a href="https://digital-photography-school.com/10-ways-to-take-stunning-portraits/" target="_blank" aria-label="creating a successful portrait (opens in a new tab)" rel="noreferrer noopener" class="ek-link">创作一幅成功的肖像</a>时，有<em>很多</em>变化的部分。我们经常谈论灯光、构图和相机装备，虽然这三件事对于创建最终图像都很重要，但它们并不是唯一起作用的变量。</p><p>捕捉一流肖像的另一个重要部分是仔细使用角度。了解并充分利用人像摄影中的角度，可以让您以最讨人喜欢的方式捕捉拍摄对象的图像（我要补充的是，这对您拍摄的每个人来说都是独一无二的！）。</p><p>现在，“角度”有两个不同的方面：</p><ol><li> <a href="https://digital-photography-school.com/using-facial-view-and-camera-angle-to-flatter-your-portrait-subject/" target="_blank" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)" rel="noreferrer noopener" class="ek-link">面部视图</a></li><li><a href="https://digital-photography-school.com/make-photos-creative-using-camera-angles/" target="_blank" aria-label="Camera angle (opens in a new tab)" rel="noreferrer noopener" class="ek-link">相机角度</a></li></ol><p>面部视图只是指一个人的脸部在照片中可见的程度。无论您是否认识“面部视图”这个术语，您都可能知道某人直视相机的照片与侧面照片之间存在视觉差异。这是两种不同的面部视图（它们位于面部视图谱的两端）。</p><p>相机角度也是一个相当简单的概念：它指的是你拿着相机的视角。在人像摄影中，这实际上取决于您是否将相机保持在拍摄对象的视线水平位置，或者高于或低于拍摄对象的视线水平位置。</p><div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter"> <span class="responsive-image wp-image-105820" style="width:750px"><span class="space" style="width:750px; padding-top:66.67%"></span><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="750" height="500" src="https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/portrait-angles1.jpg?resize=750%2C500&#038;ssl=1" alt="人像摄影中的角度" class="wp-image-105820" srcset="https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/portrait-angles1.jpg?w=750&amp;ssl=1 750w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/portrait-angles1.jpg?resize=300%2C200&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/portrait-angles1.jpg?resize=600%2C400&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/portrait-angles1.jpg?resize=90%2C60&amp;ssl=1 90w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/portrait-angles1.jpg?resize=717%2C478&amp;ssl=1 717w" sizes="(max-width: 750px) 100vw, 750px" data-recalc-dims="1" /></span></figure></div><p>这些概念本身非常简单，对吧？困难的部分是了解这些变量如何相互作用。</p><p>因此，让我们看一下使用相同的装备、拍摄对象、位置和光线的不同面部视图和摄像机角度的一些示例，同时观察不同角度如何改变每张图像的外观和感觉。 </p><h2 class="wp-block-heading" class="wp-block-heading" data-section id="camera-angles-in-portrait-photography">人像摄影中的相机角度</h2><p>为了说明不同的摄像机角度，我将向您展示具有相同全脸视图的同一主题。只有相机的视角（以及观看者的视角）会改变！ </p><h3 class="wp-block-heading" class="wp-block-heading" data-section id="the-eye-level-camera-angle">与眼睛水平的摄像机角度</h3><p>这是人像摄影中最常见的相机角度之一，您只需将相机放置在拍摄对象的眼睛水平位置，如下所示：</p><div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter"> <span class="responsive-image wp-image-105821" style="width:750px"><span class="space" style="width:750px; padding-top:66.67%"></span><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="750" height="500" src="https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/portrait-angles2.jpg?resize=750%2C500&#038;ssl=1" alt="人像摄影中的角度" class="wp-image-105821" srcset="https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/portrait-angles2.jpg?w=750&amp;ssl=1 750w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/portrait-angles2.jpg?resize=300%2C200&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/portrait-angles2.jpg?resize=600%2C400&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/portrait-angles2.jpg?resize=90%2C60&amp;ssl=1 90w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/portrait-angles2.jpg?resize=717%2C478&amp;ssl=1 717w" sizes="(max-width: 750px) 100vw, 750px" data-recalc-dims="1" /></span></figure></div><p>这种相机角度会产生平衡的肖像，并以自然比例的方式显示头部和身体（换句话说，透视失真几乎或完全不明显）。由于眼睛水平角度允许拍摄对象直接观看镜头，因此图像往往会在拍摄对象和观看者之间产生一种联系的感觉。</p><p>我还要指出的是，对于大多数拍摄对象来说，眼睛水平角度往往非常讨人喜欢。</p><h3 class="wp-block-heading" class="wp-block-heading" data-section id="the-high-camera-angle"> 高拍摄角度</h3><p>高相机角度涉及从拍摄对象的视线<em>上方</em>进行拍摄，这会产生如下所示的照片：</p><div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter"> <span class="responsive-image wp-image-105822" style="width:750px"><span class="space" style="width:750px; padding-top:66.67%"></span><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="750" height="500" src="https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/portrait-angles3.jpg?resize=750%2C500&#038;ssl=1" alt="人像摄影中的角度" class="wp-image-105822" srcset="https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/portrait-angles3.jpg?w=750&amp;ssl=1 750w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/portrait-angles3.jpg?resize=300%2C200&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/portrait-angles3.jpg?resize=600%2C400&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/portrait-angles3.jpg?resize=90%2C60&amp;ssl=1 90w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/portrait-angles3.jpg?resize=717%2C478&amp;ssl=1 717w" sizes="(max-width: 750px) 100vw, 750px" data-recalc-dims="1" /></span></figure></div><p>这样的角度，焦点集中在脸部而不是身体上，对于成年人来说，可以非常显瘦。</p><p>现在，我根本不关心让孩子看起来比实际更苗条，但在拍摄孩子时我仍然经常使用这个角度，因为我喜欢它强调孩子们的童心品质的方式。</p><p>我还发现，父母往往非常喜欢从高角度拍摄<a href="https://digital-photography-school.com/how-to-photograph-children/" target="_blank" aria-label="photographs of their children (opens in a new tab)" rel="noreferrer noopener" class="ek-link">孩子的照片</a>，我相信这是因为父母在日常生活中经常从这个角度看孩子，所以感觉非常自然和<a href="https://digital-photography-school.com/11-tips-for-better-candid-photography/" target="_blank" aria-label="candid (opens in a new tab)" rel="noreferrer noopener" class="ek-link">坦率</a>。</p><p>另一个好处是，从高角度拍摄可以轻松地在拍摄对象的眼睛中获得<a href="https://digital-photography-school.com/catchlights-in-portraiture/" target="_blank" aria-label="good catchlights (opens in a new tab)" rel="noreferrer noopener" class="ek-link">良好的聚光灯</a>，并且还可以帮助伪装不太理想的背景。</p><p>另一方面，在某些情况下，这个拍摄角度可能不利于您。它会产生明显的<a href="https://digital-photography-school.com/lens-distortion-in-photography/" target="_blank" aria-label="perspective distortion (opens in a new tab)" rel="noreferrer noopener" class="ek-link">透视变形</a>（头部与身体相比异常大），因此如果您的拍摄对象非常瘦，从上方拍摄有时会使您的拍摄对象看起来像摇头娃娃，这很少会讨人喜欢。</p><h3 class="wp-block-heading" class="wp-block-heading" data-section id="the-low-camera-angle">低摄像角度</h3><div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter"><span class="responsive-image wp-image-105824" style="width:750px"><span class="space" style="width:750px; padding-top:75.07%"></span><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="750" height="563" src="https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/portrait-angles4.jpg?resize=750%2C563&#038;ssl=1" alt="人像摄影中的角度" class="wp-image-105824" srcset="https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/portrait-angles4.jpg?w=750&amp;ssl=1 750w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/portrait-angles4.jpg?resize=300%2C225&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/portrait-angles4.jpg?resize=600%2C450&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/portrait-angles4.jpg?resize=717%2C538&amp;ssl=1 717w" sizes="(max-width: 750px) 100vw, 750px" data-recalc-dims="1" /></span></figure></div><p>从低相机角度拍摄（将相机放置在拍摄对象眼睛下方并向上倾斜）是一个非常复杂的过程。一方面，它可以使人看起来高大而权威，这对于某些商业肖像来说非常有用。另一方面，它会产生双下巴，使人看起来比实际更大，而您的客户可能不会喜欢这一点。</p><p>请注意，即使是轻微的低角度也会产生这种效果，因此，如果您拍摄的人物比您高，请记住这一点尤其重要。如果您身高 5 英尺 2 英寸，而您拍摄的人身高 6 英尺 4 英寸，则您可能需要发挥创意，以确保不会从低角度拍摄整个场景。让你的拍摄对象坐下、蹲下，或者找到一些你可以爬上去的东西，至少对于某些照片来说是这样——这确实会产生不同的效果。</p><p>我已经在刚学会走路的婴儿身上使用过几次这种相机角度，并且可以想象如果我正在拍摄政治家、足球运动员或希望拍摄的人，则可以使用更广角的镜头（以捕捉更多的身体）显得特别有力量。但总的来说，这通常不是拍摄肖像时最讨人喜欢的角度。</p><h3 class="wp-block-heading" class="wp-block-heading" data-section id="to-sum-up">总结…</h3><div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter"> <span class="responsive-image wp-image-105827" style="width:450px"><span class="space" style="width:450px; padding-top:133.33%"></span><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="450" height="600" src="https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/portrait-angles7.jpg?resize=450%2C600&#038;ssl=1" alt="人像摄影中的角度" class="wp-image-105827" srcset="https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/portrait-angles7.jpg?resize=450%2C600&amp;ssl=1 450w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/portrait-angles7.jpg?resize=225%2C300&amp;ssl=1 225w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/portrait-angles7.jpg?w=563&amp;ssl=1 563w" sizes="(max-width: 450px) 100vw, 450px" data-recalc-dims="1" /></span></figure></div><p>不要害怕尝试。尝试从两个不同的相机角度捕捉相同的图像。上图展示了同一主题从视线水平以及高相机角度呈现的效果。</p><p>如果我做了一项民意调查，我敢打赌我会发现有些人更喜欢平视拍摄，有些人更喜欢高摄像角度。这在很大程度上是一个品味和偏好的审美问题，所以我经常强调在我的肖像拍摄中包括这两种类型的角度。 </p><h2 class="wp-block-heading" class="wp-block-heading" data-section id="facial-views-in-portrait-photography">人像摄影中的面部视图</h2><p>正如我在简介中所解释的，面部视图与相机角度无关，因此在拍摄肖像时考虑<em>这两个</em>因素非常重要。</p><p>让我们快速浏览一下您可以使用的一些面部视图：</p><h3 class="wp-block-heading" class="wp-block-heading" data-section id="the-full-face-view">全脸视图</h3><p>拍摄拍摄对象的全脸意味着他们的脸应直接指向相机镜头：</p><div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter"> <span class="responsive-image wp-image-105826" style="width:750px"><span class="space" style="width:750px; padding-top:66.67%"></span><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="750" height="500" src="https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/portrait-angles6.jpg?resize=750%2C500&#038;ssl=1" alt="人像摄影中的角度" class="wp-image-105826" srcset="https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/portrait-angles6.jpg?w=750&amp;ssl=1 750w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/portrait-angles6.jpg?resize=300%2C200&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/portrait-angles6.jpg?resize=600%2C400&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/portrait-angles6.jpg?resize=90%2C60&amp;ssl=1 90w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/portrait-angles6.jpg?resize=717%2C478&amp;ssl=1 717w" sizes="(max-width: 750px) 100vw, 750px" data-recalc-dims="1" /></span></figure></div><p>通过全脸视图，您可以等量地看到双耳和脸部两侧。</p><p>全脸肖像通常传达一种自信和自信的感觉，尤其是当被拍摄者用眼睛直视相机时。这些肖像也往往感觉非常平衡，尤其是当您将拍摄对象放在画面中央时。</p><h3 class="wp-block-heading" class="wp-block-heading" data-section id="partial-views">部分观点</h3><div class="wp-block-image is-style-with-caption"><figure class="aligncenter"><span class="responsive-image wp-image-105828" style="width:750px"><span class="space" style="width:750px; padding-top:74.8%"></span><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="750" height="561" src="https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/portrait-angles8.jpg?resize=750%2C561&#038;ssl=1" alt="人像摄影中的角度" class="wp-image-105828" srcset="https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/portrait-angles8.jpg?w=750&amp;ssl=1 750w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/portrait-angles8.jpg?resize=300%2C224&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/portrait-angles8.jpg?resize=600%2C449&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/portrait-angles8.jpg?resize=717%2C536&amp;ssl=1 717w" sizes="(max-width: 750px) 100vw, 750px" data-recalc-dims="1" /></span><figcaption class="wp-element-caption">我用 3/4 面部视图拍摄了左侧图像；右侧的图像是使用侧面视图拍摄的。</figcaption></figure></div><p>其他面部视图包括 3/4 视图、2/3 视图和侧面视图。在 3/4 视图中，拍摄对象的转动刚好足以让相机不再看到他们的一只耳朵。在 2/3 视图中，对象继续转动，使得他们的鼻子即将打破后脸颊的平面。对于真实的侧面肖像，拍摄对象的脸部旋转 90 度并垂直于相机。</p><p>将拍摄对象的脸部转向 2/3 视图或 3/4 视图进行拍摄往往会传达出更随意、不那么自信的肖像。使用 3/4 面部视图拍摄且拍摄对象正好离开镜头的图像通常是最成功的偷拍图像，因为观看者仍然可以轻松看到面部表情。</p><p>同样，侧面拍摄可以让肖像感觉不摆姿势，同时又优雅端庄（特别是<a href="https://digital-photography-school.com/5-secrets-to-create-a-perfect-silhouette-portrait-outdoors/" target="_blank" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)" rel="noreferrer noopener" class="ek-link">在拍摄剪影</a>时）。</p><div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter"> <span class="responsive-image wp-image-105825" style="width:750px"><span class="space" style="width:750px; padding-top:66.67%"></span><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="750" height="500" src="https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/portrait-angles5.jpg?resize=750%2C500&#038;ssl=1" alt="人像摄影中的角度" class="wp-image-105825" srcset="https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/portrait-angles5.jpg?w=750&amp;ssl=1 750w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/portrait-angles5.jpg?resize=300%2C200&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/portrait-angles5.jpg?resize=600%2C400&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/portrait-angles5.jpg?resize=90%2C60&amp;ssl=1 90w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/portrait-angles5.jpg?resize=717%2C478&amp;ssl=1 717w" sizes="(max-width: 750px) 100vw, 750px" data-recalc-dims="1" /></span> </figure></div><h2 class="wp-block-heading" class="wp-block-heading" data-section id="enhance-your-portraits-with-angles">通过角度增强你的肖像</h2><p>真正理解角度的最好方法是找一个朋友去实验。从您能想到的每个相机角度拍摄照片，包括鸟瞰或虫眼等非传统角度。</p><p>然后拍摄每个面部视图的照片：全脸、3/4 视图、2/3 和侧面。如果您确实雄心勃勃，请尝试将面部视图和摄像机角度结合起来。问问自己：如果从与眼睛水平的角度拍摄全脸，或者从高角度拍摄全脸，肖像的感觉会发生变化吗？</p><p>很快，您将能够提前设想不同的角度，并且能够在一致的基础上获得更强大的肖像！</p><p>现在交给你：</p><p><em>您喜欢具有特定面部视图和/或拍摄角度的图像吗？您的偏好是什么？为什么？在下面的评论中分享您的想法！</em></p><div class="topics-list"><div class="wrapper"><div class="list-header"><h4 class="title-small">目录</h4><h3 class="title-pillar"><a href="https://digital-photography-school.com/10-ways-to-take-stunning-portraits/">人像摄影</a></h3></div><div class="list-wrapper"><ul class="topics-wrapper"><li class="list-item  has-children" data-list-item=""><div class="item-wrapper"><span class="list-text">一般的<span class="circle" aria-hidden="true"></span></span></div><ul class="sub-list nested-11"><li class="list-item " data-list-item="164945"><div class="item-wrapper"> <a href="https://digital-photography-school.com/15-common-portrait-mistakes/?utm_source=dPS&utm_medium=topic_cluster&utm_campaign=https%3A%2F%2Fdigital-photography-school.com%2Fportrait-angles-for-beginners-a-visual-guide%2F" class="list-text">15 个需要避免的常见肖像错误<span class="circle" aria-hidden="true"></span></a></div></li><li class="list-item " data-list-item="46813"><div class="item-wrapper"> <a href="https://digital-photography-school.com/10-ways-to-direct-a-portrait-shoot-like-a-pro/?utm_source=dPS&utm_medium=topic_cluster&utm_campaign=https%3A%2F%2Fdigital-photography-school.com%2Fportrait-angles-for-beginners-a-visual-guide%2F" class="list-text">像专业人士一样拍摄人像的 10 种方法<span class="circle" aria-hidden="true"></span></a></div></li><li clas