mp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/vert.jpg?resize=717%2C868&amp;ssl=1 717w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/vert.jpg?w=1118&amp;ssl=1 1118w" sizes="(max-width: 496px) 100vw, 496px" data-recalc-dims="1" /></span></figure></div><p>同一张照片，不同的拍摄方向。背景是否有助于讲述更多故事，或者您更喜欢只关注主题，就像我在剪裁较紧的肖像中那样？</p><p><strong>确保在您的帖子、评论或社交媒体上添加#dPSWeeklyChallenge 和 #dPSPortraitOrLandscape 主题标签。您可以在 Facebook、Instagram 或 Twitter 上标记我们！</strong></p><p><a href="https://digital-photography-school.com/weekly-challenge/"><strong>在这里找到我们之前所有的每周挑战。</strong></a></p><p>只需将您的照片上传到评论字段（在 Disqus 评论部分查找小相机图标），它们就会嵌入供我们所有人查看，或者如果您愿意，也可以将它们上传到您最喜欢的照片共享网站并离开到他们的链接。向我展示您在本周挑战中最好的照片。有时图像需要一段时间才能显示，因此请耐心等待，尽量不要将同一张图像发布两次。</p><p><strong>在 dPS Facebook 群组中分享</strong></p><p>您还可以在<a rel="nofollow noopener"  href="https://www.facebook.com/groups/digitalphotographyschoolgroup/">dPS Facebook 群组</a>中分享您的图片，因为挑战每周都会发布在那里。</p><div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"> <span class="responsive-image wp-image-261403" style="width:579px"><span class="space" style="width:579px; padding-top:103.63%"></span><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="579" height="600" src="https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/landscape-vs-portrait-1005-1.jpg?resize=579%2C600&#038;ssl=1" alt="dPS 双周摄影挑战赛 – 构图" class="wp-image-261403" srcset="https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/landscape-vs-portrait-1005-1.jpg?resize=579%2C600&amp;ssl=1 579w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/landscape-vs-portrait-1005-1.jpg?resize=289%2C300&amp;ssl=1 289w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/landscape-vs-portrait-1005-1.jpg?resize=768%2C796&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/landscape-vs-portrait-1005-1.jpg?resize=717%2C743&amp;