如何拍摄蜘蛛网：16 个专家技巧https://digital-photography-school.com/how-to-photograph-a-spiders-web/ https://digital-photography-school.com/how-to-photograph-a-spiders-web/#commentsDarren Rowse Fri, 14 Jun 2024 10:00:00 +0000 Photography Tips and TutorialsintermediateMacro Photography https://digital-photography-school.com/how-to-photograph-a-spiders-web/ <p>帖子《<a rel="nofollow" href="https://digital-photography-school.com/how-to-photograph-a-spiders-web/">如何拍摄蜘蛛网：16 个专家技巧》</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://digital-photography-school.com">数码摄影学校</a>上。它的作者是<a rel="nofollow" href="https://digital-photography-school.com/author/darren/">达伦·罗斯</a>。</p><p>如果您想拍摄美丽的蜘蛛网摄影，那么您来对地方了。这些精致、闪闪发光的结构具有微妙的复杂性，几乎让人忍不住拍照——此外，蜘蛛网可以为您的作品集增添神秘和优雅的气息。虽然捕捉令人惊叹的蜘蛛网照片可能是一个挑战，[...]</p><p>帖子《<a rel="nofollow" href="https://digital-photography-school.com/how-to-photograph-a-spiders-web/">如何拍摄蜘蛛网：16 个专家技巧》</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://digital-photography-school.com">数码摄影学校</a>上。它的作者是<a rel="nofollow" href="https://digital-photography-school.com/author/darren/">达伦·罗斯</a>。</p> ; <p>帖子《<a rel="nofollow" href="https://digital-photography-school.com/how-to-photograph-a-spiders-web/">如何拍摄蜘蛛网：16 个专家技巧》</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://digital-photography-school.com">数码摄影学校</a>上。它的作者是<a rel="nofollow" href="https://digital-photography-school.com/author/darren/">达伦·罗斯</a>。</p><div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-full"> <span class="responsive-image wp-image-261411" style="width:1200px"><span class="space" style="width:1200px; padding-top:103.67%"></span><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="1200" height="1244" src="https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/spider-web-photography-1006.jpg?resize=1200%2C1244&#038;ssl=1" alt="拍摄令人惊叹的蜘蛛网照片" class="wp-image-261411" srcset="https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/spider-web-photography-1006.jpg?w=1200&amp;ssl=1 1200w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/spider-web-photography-1006.jpg?resize=289%2C300&amp;ssl=1 289w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/spider-web-photography-1006.jpg?resize=579%2C600&amp;ssl=1 579w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/spider-web-photography-1006.jpg?resize=768%2C796&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/spider-web-photography-1006.jpg?resize=717%2C743&amp;ssl=1 717w" sizes="(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px" data-recalc-dims="1" /></span></figure></div><p>如果您想拍摄美丽的蜘蛛网摄影，那么您来对地方了。这些精致、闪闪发光的结构具有微妙的复杂性，几乎<em>让人忍不住</em>拍照——此外，蜘蛛网可以为您的作品集增添神秘和优雅的气息。</p><p>虽然拍摄令人惊叹的蜘蛛网照片可能是一项挑战，但只要掌握一些专业知识，您就可以立即开始拍摄出色的图像。这就是本文的全部内容：为您提供创建始终如一的出色结果所需的工具。</p><p>无论您是休闲智能手机摄影师还是数码单反相机爱好者，接下来的建议都适合您。我将涵盖从掌握背景散景到用镜头进行全面抽象的所有内容。</p><p>听起来不错？让我们开始吧！</p><h2 class="wp-block-heading" class="wp-block-heading" data-section id="shoot-on-a-still-day"> 1. 在无风的日子拍摄</h2><p>蜘蛛网非常轻，即使有<em>一丝</em>风，它们也会在你拍摄时来回摇摆。</p><p>这会导致三个主要问题：</p><ol><li>如果您使用较慢的<a href="https://digital-photography-school.com/shutter-speed/" target="_blank" aria-label="shutter speed (opens in a new tab)" rel="noreferrer noopener" class="ek-link">快门速度</a>（近距离拍摄时通常需要这种速度，尤其是在清晨和傍晚），移动的网会产生运动模糊。</li><li>如果您以高倍率对焦（例如，您使用<a href="https://digital-photography-school.com/choose-perfect-macro-lens/" target="_blank" aria-label="macro lens (opens in a new tab)" rel="noreferrer noopener" class="ek-link">微距镜头</a>），那么您将很难锁定焦点。</li><li>任何运动都会甩掉水分，甚至可能破坏网。</li></ol><p>因此，您必须注意<em>仅</em>在最安静的日子里进行拍摄。查看当地天气预报，目标风速为 5 英里/小时或更低。另外，在清晨寻找蜘蛛网；日出之后往往风力较小，而且光线通常是美丽的金色。 </p><h2 class="wp-block-heading" class="wp-block-heading" data-section id="focus-manually-and-use-your-highest-magnification-lens"> 2. 手动对焦（并使用最高放大倍率的镜头）</h2><div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-full"> <span class="responsive-image wp-image-130181" style="width:5472px"><span class="space" style="width:5472px; padding-top:66.67%"></span><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="5472" height="3648" src="https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/06/spiders-web-0.jpg?resize=5472%2C3648&#038;ssl=1" alt="清晨的蜘蛛网" class="wp-image-130181" srcset="https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/06/spiders-web-0.jpg?w=5472&amp;ssl=1 5472w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/06/spiders-web-0.jpg?resize=300%2C200&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/06/spiders-web-0.jpg?resize=768%2C512&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/06/spiders-web-0.jpg?resize=600%2C400&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/06/spiders-web-0.jpg?resize=90%2C60&amp;ssl=1 90w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/06/spiders-web-0.jpg?resize=717%2C478&amp;ssl=1 717w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/06/spiders-web-0.jpg?w=2000&amp;ssl=1 2000w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/06/spiders-web-0.jpg?w=3000&amp;ssl=1 3000w" sizes="(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px" data-recalc-dims="1" /></span></figure></div><p>蜘蛛网<em>非常</em>小，这意味着如果您想捕捉细节，则需要近距离对焦。</p><p>不幸的是，距离越近，相机的自动对焦系统就越差。因此，当您接近蜘蛛网时，您的镜头将开始来回搜索 - 并且可能无法完全找到焦点。</p><p>这就是<a href="https://digital-photography-school.com/dont-afraid-manual-focus/" target="_blank" aria-label="manual focus (opens in a new tab)" rel="noreferrer noopener" class="ek-link">手动对焦</a>的用武之地。它可以让您通过调整镜筒上的对焦环来获得清晰的照片。请注意，要手动对焦，您通常需要轻按镜头或相机侧面的开关（通常标有<em>AF/M</em> ）。</p><p>顺便说一句，所有镜头都具有最大放大倍率，这是靠近拍摄对象对焦时获得的细节水平。如果您想要拍摄精美的高倍率图像，您会需要选择一款能够进行高倍率对焦的镜头。最好的放大镜是微距镜头，但如果你没有，也没关系。只需检查您拥有的所有镜头的规格表，然后找出哪一个提供最高的放大倍率。</p><p>您还可以考虑购买近焦滤镜或延长管，这将提高镜头的放大能力。 </p><h2 class="wp-block-heading" class="wp-block-heading" data-section id="be-an-environmentally-friendly-photographer"> 3. 做一名环保摄影师</h2><p>请记住：哪里有一张网，哪里就有一个小（或者不是那么小！）的生物创造了它。</p><p>因此，请注意不要触摸或以其他方式干扰您遇到的网。您可能会想用手指重新定位网，但要抵制这种倾向；相反，如果您对网页的外观不满意，请尝试使用微距镜头超近距离拍摄抽象构图，或改变视角以获得不同的结果。 </p><h2 class="wp-block-heading" class="wp-block-heading" data-section id="find-a-plain-background-that-makes-the-web-stand-out"> 4. 找到一个能让网页脱颖而出的朴素背景</h2><p>初学者常常无法考虑蜘蛛网图片的背景——但背景却非常重要。</p><p>好的背景可以增强图像，而坏的背景会损害（并且通常会破坏）最终结果。</p><p>但什么样的背景才算是好的背景呢？对于蜘蛛网，我建议使用纯色背景，最好是深色背景。在合适的光线下，深色背景会突出半透明的网页，创造出华丽、引人注目的照片：</p><div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-full"> <span class="responsive-image wp-image-130183" style="width:5184px"><span class="space" style="width:5184px; padding-top:66.67%"></span><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="5184" height="3456" src="https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/06/spiders-webs-2.jpg?resize=5184%2C3456&#038;ssl=1" alt="蜘蛛网与露珠" class="wp-image-130183" srcset="https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/06/spiders-webs-2.jpg?w=5184&amp;ssl=1 5184w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/06/spiders-webs-2.jpg?resize=300%2C200&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/06/spiders-webs-2.jpg?resize=768%2C512&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/06/spiders-webs-2.jpg?resize=600%2C400&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/06/spiders-webs-2.jpg?resize=90%2C60&amp;ssl=1 90w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/06/spiders-webs-2.jpg?resize=717%2C478&amp;ssl=1 717w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/06/spiders-webs-2.jpg?w=2000&amp;ssl=1 2000w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/06/spiders-webs-2.jpg?w=3000&amp;ssl=1 3000w" sizes="(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px" data-recalc-dims="1" /></span></figure></div><p>至少，确保背景不会分散注意力。将颜色保持在最低限度，并争取较大的主题与背景分离。 </p><h2 class="wp-block-heading" class="wp-block-heading" data-section id="carefully-choose-your-aperture-and-depth-of-field"> 5. 仔细选择光圈（和景深）</h2><p>蜘蛛网摄影就是要<em>强调</em>你的主要主题——蜘蛛网——同时确保背景不显眼并且（理想情况下）互补。</p><p>强调主要主题并弱化背景的最简单方法之一是什么？扩大<a href="https://digital-photography-school.com/aperture/" target="_blank" aria-label="aperture (opens in a new tab)" rel="noreferrer noopener" class="ek-link">光圈</a>以创建美丽的背景模糊。</p><p> （请注意，本文中的蜘蛛网图片都具有平滑、模糊的背景？这是故意的！）</p><p>在高放大倍率下，只要主体与背景的分离度良好（即背景距离主体超过几英寸），您就可以在 f/1.4 到 f/5.6 之间的任何位置获得模糊的背景。</p><div class="wp-block-image is-style-with-caption"><figure class="aligncenter size-full"> <span class="responsive-image wp-image-261412" style="width:1500px"><span class="space" style="width:1500px; padding-top:78.93%"></span><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="1500" height="1184" src="https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/spider-web-photography-51.jpg?resize=1500%2C1184&#038;ssl=1" alt="如何拍摄蜘蛛网" class="wp-image-261412" srcset="https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/spider-web-photography-51.jpg?w=1500&amp;ssl=1 1500w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/spider-web-photography-51.jpg?resize=300%2C237&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/spider-web-photography-51.jpg?resize=600%2C474&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/spider-web-photography-51.jpg?resize=768%2C606&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/spider-web-photography-51.jpg?resize=717%2C566&amp;ssl=1 717w" sizes="(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px" data-recalc-dims="1" /></span><figcaption class="wp-element-caption">在高倍率下拍摄时，创建模糊背景相当容易；只需使用相当宽的光圈并确保蜘蛛网和背景之间有一点分离。</figcaption></figure></div><p>但如果您缩小以获得更环保的图像，则需要将光圈保持尽可能低（f/2.8 是一个很好的起点）。</p><p>顺便说一句，大光圈会产生<em>窄或浅的景深效果</em>。这听起来可能很复杂，但它只是指对焦镜头的数量；浅<a aria-label="depth of field (opens in a new tab)" href="https://digital-photography-school.com/understanding-depth-field-beginners/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" class="ek-link">景深</a>可以使场景的一小部分清晰对焦，而深景深可以使大部分场景（甚至整个镜头）<em>清晰</em>对焦。 </p><h2 class="wp-block-heading" class="wp-block-heading" data-section id="try-to-create-background-bokeh"> 6.尝试创建背景散景</h2><p>我在上一篇技巧中谈到了背景模糊，但我想在这里真正磨练它；具体来说，我想讨论<a href="https://digital-photography-school.com/how-to-achieve-nice-bokeh-in-plain-english/" target="_blank" aria-label="background bokeh (opens in a new tab)" rel="noreferrer noopener" class="ek-link">背景散景</a>在蜘蛛网照片中的价值。</p><p>散景是您在专业图像中经常看到的美丽而模糊的背景。它通过模糊干扰来将注意力吸引到你的主题上——在本例中是蜘蛛网。执行良好的散景效果可以让您的蜘蛛网像其他东西一样流行！</p><p>为了获得漂亮的散景效果，您需要拨入相对较宽的光圈设置。换句话说，您需要选择较宽的 f 值，通常在 f/1.8 到 f/4 范围内。 （但请注意，距离拍摄对象越近，就越容易创建奶油般的散景！因此，如果您在高放大倍率下工作，即使在 f/5.6 左右，您也可以获得强烈的背景模糊。）</p><p>使用宽镜头光圈时，景深会变窄，从而产生散景效果。</p><div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-full"> <span class="responsive-image wp-image-261417" style="width:1500px"><span class="space" style="width:1500px; padding-top:66.27%"></span><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="1500" height="994" src="https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/spider-web-photography-55.jpg?resize=1500%2C994&#038;ssl=1" alt="如何拍摄蜘蛛网" class="wp-image-261417" srcset="https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/spider-web-photography-55.jpg?w=1500&amp;ssl=1 1500w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/spider-web-photography-55.jpg?resize=300%2C200&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/spider-web-photography-55.jpg?resize=600%2C398&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/spider-web-photography-55.jpg?resize=768%2C509&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/spider-web-photography-55.jpg?resize=90%2C60&amp;ssl=1 90w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/spider-web-photography-55.jpg?resize=115%2C75&amp;ssl=1 115w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/spider-web-photography-55.jpg?resize=717%2C475&amp;ssl=1 717w" sizes="(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px" data-recalc-dims="1" /></span></figure></div><p>现在，靠近网络会增加背景模糊，但要小心。更窄的景深意味着聚焦误差的空间更小。您希望网页清晰而背景模糊，而不是相反。请毫不犹豫地进行几次测试拍摄，以确保您的焦点准确。 </p><h2 class="wp-block-heading" class="wp-block-heading" data-section id="shoot-from-a-head-on-angle"> 7.从正面角度拍摄</h2><p>从各个角度拍摄蜘蛛网可以给您带来有趣的结果（正如我希望本文中的图像有效地展示的那样！）。但是，当您刚开始时，请尝试将自己直接放在网络前面并直接射击。</p><p>这将使您能够保持整个网络的焦点，因为从镜头到拍摄对象的所有部分的距离将相似，从而防止浅景深效果（如上所述）模糊部分网络。</p><div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-full"> <span class="responsive-image wp-image-261414" style="width:1500px"><span class="space" style="width:1500px; padding-top:66.67%"></span><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="1500" height="1000" src="https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/spider-web-photography-52.jpg?resize=1500%2C1000&#038;ssl=1" alt="如何拍摄蜘蛛网" class="wp-image-261414" srcset="https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/spider-web-photography-52.jpg?w=1500&amp;ssl=1 1500w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/spider-web-photography-52.jpg?resize=300%2C200&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/spider-web-photography-52.jpg?resize=600%2C400&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/spider-web-photography-52.jpg?resize=768%2C512&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/spider-web-photography-52.jpg?resize=90%2C60&amp;ssl=1 90w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/spider-web-photography-52.jpg?resize=717%2C478&amp;ssl=1 717w" sizes="(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px" data-recalc-dims="1" /></span></figure></div><p>当然，您并不<em>总是</em>需要关注整个网络。您可能还喜欢从不同角度进行一些浅景深拍摄，以实现有趣的抽象效果。 </p><h2 class="wp-block-heading" class="wp-block-heading" data-section id="dont-forget-a-tripod-or-shoot-with-a-fast-shutter-speed"> 8.不要忘记三脚架（或使用较快的快门速度拍摄）</h2><p>在高倍率下，相机抖动会增加，这可能会导致照片模糊。</p><p>所以你有两个选择：</p><ol><li>您可以将三脚架带入现场，这样即使在低快门速度下也能保持相机稳定。这确实有几个缺点——首先，坚固的三脚架可能很昂贵，而且它们可能很笨重，而且在慢快门速度下，你需要一个真正静止的拍摄对象。</li><li>您可以手持拍摄并使用较快的快门速度。在这里，您需要将速度保持在 1/125 秒左右（并且可能高于 1/160 秒或 1/200 秒，具体取决于放大级别和手的稳定性）。</li></ol><p>哪种方法最好？这实际上取决于您的喜好和拍摄风格。一些摄影师喜欢三脚架拍摄的缓慢、从容的特性，而另一些摄影师则喜欢手持的灵活性。但是，如果您打算在弱光下拍摄，则可能需要采用三脚架路线，除非您的相机能够在高<a href="https://digital-photography-school.com/iso-settings/" target="_blank" aria-label="ISOs (opens in a new tab)" rel="noreferrer noopener" class="ek-link">ISO</a>下实现低噪点。</p><h2 class="wp-block-heading" class="wp-block-heading" data-section id="look-for-webs-with-dew"> 9.寻找有露水的网</h2><p>许多经典的蜘蛛网照片都包含露水或雨滴，如下所示：</p><div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-full"> <span class="responsive-image wp-image-130185" style="width:5472px"><span class="space" style="width:5472px; padding-top:66.67%"></span><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="5472" height="3648" src="https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/06/spiders-webs-4.jpg?resize=5472%2C3648&#038;ssl=1" alt="蜘蛛网与水滴" class="wp-image-130185" srcset="https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/06/spiders-webs-4.jpg?w=5472&amp;ssl=1 5472w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/06/spiders-webs-4.jpg?resize=300%2C200&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/06/spiders-webs-4.jpg?resize=768%2C512&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/06/spiders-webs-4.jpg?resize=600%2C400&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/06/spiders-webs-4.jpg?resize=90%2C60&amp;ssl=1 90w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/06/spiders-webs-4.jpg?resize=717%2C478&amp;ssl=1 717w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/06/spiders-webs-4.jpg?w=2000&amp;ssl=1 2000w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/06/spiders-webs-4.jpg?w=3000&amp;ssl=1 3000w" sizes="(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px" data-recalc-dims="1" /></span></figure></div><p>正如您所看到的，露水看起来很漂亮，而且它在失焦区域产生了有趣的散景效果。</p><p>我上面提到，一天中结露的最佳时间是早晨，不过您也可以在暴风雨后冒险出去（当然，假设没有风！）。</p><h2 class="wp-block-heading" class="wp-block-heading" data-section id="shoot-into-the-sun"> 10.对着太阳拍摄</h2><p>许多严肃的微距摄影师喜欢拍摄逆光（即在阳光下拍摄）的蜘蛛网。结果可能是壮观的——戏剧性的、富有个性的——尽管注意你的方法很重要，因为背光可能很难有效处理。</p><p>时机非常重要。尝试在清晨或傍晚拍摄蜘蛛网图像。那时太阳在天空中很低，光线更加柔和，角度也很有趣。</p><p>然后就是要考虑定位。你会想要找到一个蜘蛛网，你可以从一个好的角度拍摄，阳光（大致）从后面照射。这就是如何获得美丽的背光效果，太阳将网线转变为发光的光丝，如下所示：</p><div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-full"> <span class="responsive-image wp-image-261415" style="width:1500px"><span class="space" style="width:1500px; padding-top:66.67%"></span><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="1500" height="1000" src="https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/spider-web-photography-53.jpg?resize=1500%2C1000&#038;ssl=1" alt="如何拍摄蜘蛛网" class="wp-image-261415" srcset="https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/spider-web-photography-53.jpg?w=1500&amp;ssl=1 1500w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/spider-web-photography-53.jpg?resize=300%2C200&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/spider-web-photography-53.jpg?resize=600%2C400&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/spider-web-photography-53.jpg?resize=768%2C512&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/spider-web-photography-53.jpg?resize=90%2C60&amp;ssl=1 90w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/spider-web-photography-53.jpg?resize=717%2C478&amp;ssl=1 717w" sizes="(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px" data-recalc-dims="1" /></span></figure></div><p>当然，安全第一。切勿通过镜头直视太阳，也不要让阳光直接照射相机太长时间。一个技巧是将太阳放置在取景框之外。这样，您就可以捕获沐浴在阳光下的网络，而不必担心您的眼睛或设备！</p><p>最后，不要害怕图像曝光不足。即使背景变暗，曝光不足也将确保您捕捉到网络本身的大量细节。 （此外，深色背景上发光的网的组合看起来令人惊叹！）</p><h2 class="wp-block-heading" class="wp-block-heading" data-section id="fill-the-frame"> 11.填充框架</h2><div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-full"><span class="responsive-image wp-image-261416" style="width:1500px"><span class="space" style="width:1500px; padding-top:66.27%"></span><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="1500" height="994" src="https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/spider-web-photography-50.jpg?resize=1500%2C994&#038;ssl=1" alt="如何拍摄蜘蛛网" class="wp-image-261416" srcset="https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/spider-web-photography-50.jpg?w=1500&amp;ssl=1 1500w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/spider-web-photography-50.jpg?resize=300%2C200&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/spider-web-photography-50.jpg?resize=600%2C398&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/spider-web-photography-50.jpg?resize=768%2C509&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/spider-web-photography-50.jpg?resize=90%2C60&amp;ssl=1 90w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/spider-web-photography-50.jpg?resize=115%2C75&amp;ssl=1 115w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/spider-web-photography-50.jpg?resize=717%2C475&amp;ssl=1 717w" sizes="(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px" data-recalc-dims="1" /></span></figure></div><p>这是一条简单的构图建议：</p><p>如果您想创建原始的蜘蛛网图像，请不要从太远的位置拍摄，以免蜘蛛网仅覆盖画面的一部分。相反，尽可能靠近网络——无论是物理方式还是通过镜头的变焦机制。</p><p>如果您拥有微距镜头，请务必使用它；它会让您更轻松地填充框架！</p><p>当然，您可以捕捉没有框架填充网络的令人惊叹的图像。但通过填充框架，您可以强调主要主题，此外您还可以突出显示抽象图案，甚至捕捉转向美术领域的图像。</p><p>另外，花时间尝试不同的角度（并测试不同的光圈值，以获得抽象的景深效果！）。</p><h2 class="wp-block-heading" class="wp-block-heading" data-section id="go-abstract"> 12. 抽象化</h2><p>如果您想捕捉更具<em>创意的</em>蜘蛛网图像，请记住，蜘蛛网并不总是看起来像照片中的蜘蛛网。它可以是一件抽象的艺术作品。</p><p>为了实现这一目标，您通常需要在超高放大倍率下工作，这就是微距镜头发挥作用的地方。放大可让您专注于单股或一小股股线。曾经的网将变成令人着迷的图案，甚至可能是一条横穿你的框架的线。</p><p>正确对焦至关重要。为了让一根线真正脱颖而出，需要精确地聚焦。当你钉住它时，那根线会变得锋利，使网络的其余部分看起来像一个柔软、朦胧的背景。</p><p>最后，记住使用较快的快门速度。在如此高的放大倍率下，即使是最轻微的相机抖动也会使图像模糊。并捕捉大量镜头，以最大限度地提高您获得至少一张您喜欢的照片的机会！ </p><h2 class="wp-block-heading" class="wp-block-heading" data-section id="photograph-the-spider-web-from-both-sides"> 13.从两侧拍摄蜘蛛网</h2><p>有时，蜘蛛网的一侧看起来非常暗淡无生气，而另一侧看起来<em>很华丽</em>——要么是因为光线以正确的方式照射在蜘蛛网上，要么是因为背景看起来要好得多。</p><p>例如，下图以清晨的露珠为背景，背景是美丽的初升太阳。从网络的另一端这是不可能的！</p><div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-full"> <span class="responsive-image wp-image-130186" style="width:4200px"><span class="space" style="width:4200px; padding-top:78.57%"></span><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="4200" height="3300" src="https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/06/spiders-webs-3.jpg?resize=4200%2C3300&#038;ssl=1" alt="蜘蛛网露" class="wp-image-130186" srcset="https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/06/spiders-webs-3.jpg?w=4200&amp;ssl=1 4200w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/06/spiders-webs-3.jpg?resize=300%2C236&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/06/spiders-webs-3.jpg?resize=768%2C603&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/06/spiders-webs-3.jpg?resize=600%2C471&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/06/spiders-webs-3.jpg?resize=717%2C563&amp;ssl=1 717w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/06/spiders-webs-3.jpg?w=2000&amp;ssl=1 2000w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/06/spiders-webs-3.jpg?w=3000&amp;ssl=1 3000w" sizes="(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px" data-recalc-dims="1" /></span></figure></div><p>事实上，当你找到一张好的蜘蛛网时，我建议<em>在</em>拍摄前检查蜘蛛网的两面。另外，不要害怕趴在网上，即使这意味着躺在湿草或泥里。您将获得更亲密的视角，而且低视角通常可以提供最好的背景。 </p><h2 class="wp-block-heading" class="wp-block-heading" data-section id="photograph-with-and-without-spiders"> 14. 有蜘蛛和没有蜘蛛的照片</h2><p>蜘蛛网可以讲述两个不同的故事，具体取决于蜘蛛是否存在。一个空的网络会让人感到空虚，甚至神秘。另一方面，一只自豪地埋在网中的蜘蛛可以让我们欣赏到自然世界的美景。我鼓励您拍摄两者的照片！</p><p>当你发现一张蜘蛛网里有常驻蜘蛛时，你就有了选择。尝试不同的角度和距离。拍摄一些蜘蛛占据中心舞台的镜头，以及一些蜘蛛只是网络设计的一小部分的镜头（请参阅下面我的最后提示！）。</p><p>尝试一下你的相机设置。根据您的构图，您可能需要改变焦点或曝光以突出蜘蛛作为焦点。聚焦良好的蜘蛛可以为您的图像提供全新的深度和细节水平。</p><p>如果你发现一个空网，这也是一个机会。尝试从强调其结构或与光相互作用的方式的角度捕捉它。您可能会发现，没有蜘蛛会给您的照片增添一种喜怒无常或神秘的感觉。</p><p>无论您选择哪种方法，请务必进行大量拍摄。您可以稍后决定哪些最能捕捉您想要的情绪或构图。</p><h2 class="wp-block-heading" class="wp-block-heading" data-section id="experiment-with-flash"> 15. 尝试闪光灯</h2><p>这是倒数第二个蜘蛛网摄影技巧：</p><p>将闪光灯带入现场并使用它拍摄有趣的图像。</p><p>就我个人而言，我发现使用自然光拍摄效果最好。但有时通过闪光灯添加人造光可以很好地照亮网络并产生一些很好的聚光灯。当光线较暗时，这尤其有效；闪光灯将使网络保持清晰（不需要高 ISO！）。</p><p>如果您确实需要闪光灯，请考虑使用<a href="https://digital-photography-school.com/photography-ring-light/" target="_blank" aria-label="ring flash (opens in a new tab)" rel="noreferrer noopener" class="ek-link">环形闪光灯</a>（它安装在镜头前部并均匀地照亮拍摄对象）。您还可以选择使用离机闪光灯，您可以用一只手握住闪光灯，同时用另一只手拍摄（或者将相机放置在三脚架上时握住闪光灯）。</p><p>底线：享受闪光灯的乐趣，不要害怕尝试！</p><h2 class="wp-block-heading" class="wp-block-heading" data-section id="include-the-environment">16. 包括环境</h2><div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-full"><span class="responsive-image wp-image-261413" style="width:1500px"><span class="space" style="width:1500px; padding-top:66.4%"></span><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="1500" height="996" src="https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/spider-web-photography-54.jpg?resize=1500%2C996&#038;ssl=1" alt="如何拍摄蜘蛛网" class="wp-image-261413" srcset="https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/spider-web-photography-54.jpg?w=1500&amp;ssl=1 1500w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/spider-web-photography-54.jpg?resize=300%2C200&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/spider-web-photography-54.jpg?resize=600%2C398&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/spider-web-photography-54.jpg?resize=768%2C510&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/spider-web-photography-54.jpg?resize=90%2C60&amp;ssl=1 90w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/spider-web-photography-54.jpg?resize=115%2C75&amp;ssl=1 115w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/spider-web-photography-54.jpg?resize=717%2C476&amp;ssl=1 717w" sizes="(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px" data-recalc-dims="1" /></span></figure></div><p>不要误会我的意思：正如我上面强调的，用蜘蛛网填充你的框架通常是一个很棒的主意。它强调网络的复杂性，将聚光灯放在您想要的地方。但是上下文呢？</p><p>网络上有一个完整的世界，有时展示该环境可以为您的照片增添额外的层次。生锈的栅栏柱之间串起的蜘蛛网或跨越两朵野花之间的间隙可以为您的图像增添一层诗意。</p><p>因此，如果环境有趣，请稍微改变一下。后退几步或使用更广角的镜头来捕捉更多的环境。</p><p>注意：要包含网络及其周围环境，您需要使用更窄的光圈，特别是当网络和背景之间有很大距离时。这样，网络及其周围环境都会变得清晰。</p><p>并始终注意你的构图。包含更多元素意味着更多分散注意力的机会。留意框架的角落和边缘。确保所有内容都添加到图像中，而不是将焦点从网络上移开。 </p><h2 class="wp-block-heading" class="wp-block-heading" data-section id="spider-web-photography-final-words">蜘蛛网摄影：最后的话</h2><p>希望您现在已经准备好拍摄一些属于自己的美丽的蜘蛛网照片了。从背景散景到抽象线条，创意的可能性是无穷无尽的——虽然很容易陷入技术细节中，但一旦你开始尝试并享受乐趣，魔法就会真正发生。</p><p>你还在等什么？拿起相机，出发吧。找到那些大多数人都不会再看一眼的隐藏网络。将它们变成您的下一个杰作！</p><p>现在交给你：</p><p><em>您最喜欢以下哪些蜘蛛网摄影技巧？你打算很快出去射蜘蛛吗？在下面的评论中分享您的想法！</em></p><p>帖子《<a rel="nofollow" href="https://digital-photography-school.com/how-to-photograph-a-spiders-web/">如何拍摄蜘蛛网：16 个专家技巧》</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://digital-photography-school.com">数码摄影学校</a>上。它的作者是<a rel="nofollow" href="https://digital-photography-school.com/author/darren/">达伦·罗斯</a>。</p> ; https://digital-photography-school.com/how-to-photograph-a-spiders-web/feed/ 161
您应该以肖像还是风景方向拍摄？ https://digital-photography-school.com/portrait-or-landscape-orientation/ https://digital-photography-school.com/portrait-or-landscape-orientation/#commentsMegan Kennedy Thu, 13 Jun 2024 10:00:00 +0000 Photography Tips and Tutorialsbeginnerphotography fundamentals https://digital-photography-school.com/?p=177006 <p>帖子 <a rel="nofollow" href="https://digital-photography-school.com/portrait-or-landscape-orientation/">你应该以肖像还是风景方向拍摄？</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://digital-photography-school.com">数码摄影学校</a>。它的作者是<a rel="nofollow" href="https://digital-photography-school.com/author/megan-kennedy/">梅根·肯尼迪</a>。</p><p>标准相机传感器是矩形的，这种配置允许横向（水平）和纵向（垂直）方向。当人们第一次拿起专用相机时，他们最初的冲动是以横向拍摄大多数主题（例如风景、城市景观和建筑），而主要使用纵向[…]</p><p>帖子 <a rel="nofollow" href="https://digital-photography-school.com/portrait-or-landscape-orientation/">你应该以肖像还是风景方向拍摄？</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://digital-photography-school.com">数码摄影学校</a>。它的作者是<a rel="nofollow" href="https://digital-photography-school.com/author/megan-kennedy/">梅根·肯尼迪</a>。</p> ; <p>帖子 <a rel="nofollow" href="https://digital-photography-school.com/portrait-or-landscape-orientation/">你应该以肖像还是风景方向拍摄？</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://digital-photography-school.com">数码摄影学校</a>。它的作者是<a rel="nofollow" href="https://digital-photography-school.com/author/megan-kennedy/">梅根·肯尼迪</a>。</p><div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-full"> <span class="responsive-image wp-image-261394" style="width:1200px"><span class="space" style="width:1200px; padding-top:103.67%"></span><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="1200" height="1244" src="https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/landscape-vs-portrait-1005.jpg?resize=1200%2C1244&#038;ssl=1" alt="您应该使用哪种照片方向？" class="wp-image-261394" srcset="https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/landscape-vs-portrait-1005.jpg?w=1200&amp;ssl=1 1200w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/landscape-vs-portrait-1005.jpg?resize=289%2C300&amp;ssl=1 289w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/landscape-vs-portrait-1005.jpg?resize=579%2C600&amp;ssl=1 579w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/landscape-vs-portrait-1005.jpg?resize=768%2C796&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/landscape-vs-portrait-1005.jpg?resize=717%2C743&amp;ssl=1 717w" sizes="(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px" data-recalc-dims="1" /></span></figure></div><p>标准相机传感器是矩形的，这种配置允许横向（水平）和纵向（垂直）方向。当人们第一次拿起专用相机时，他们的第一冲动是拍摄大多数拍摄对象的横向（例如风景、城市景观和建筑），而纵向主要用于拍摄人物肖像。</p><p>原因并不难理解：大多数相机<em>默认</em>都是横向设计的。拍摄纵向照片需要将相机翻转过来，这需要深思熟虑的决策（而且通常会很不舒服！）。因此，除非图像是传统的肖像，否则大多数初学者都会选择风景路线。</p><p>但随着摄影师的进步，经常会出现一个问题：你真的应该在风景和其他风景主题上使用横向方向吗？你真的应该一直以肖像方向拍摄肖像吗？那么那些不符合风景但也不是肖像的主题呢？什么方向最有效？</p><p>如果您自己问这些问题，那么我认为您的思路是正确的 - 而且我认为我可以帮助您更好地理解纵向和横向方向之间的差异，以及它们如何影响您的图像。下面，我分享了使用这些不同摄影格式的最佳建议，以便您在关键时刻做出正确的决定！</p><p>让我们开始吧。 </p><h2 class="wp-block-heading" class="wp-block-heading" data-section id="portrait-vs-landscape-orientation-basics">纵向与横向方向基础知识</h2><div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter"><span class="responsive-image wp-image-177263" style="width:1500px"><span class="space" style="width:1500px; padding-top:59.2%"></span><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="1500" height="888" src="https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/portrait_or_landscape.jpg?resize=1500%2C888&#038;ssl=1" alt="纵向和横向示例" class="wp-image-177263" srcset="https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/portrait_or_landscape.jpg?w=1500&amp;ssl=1 1500w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/portrait_or_landscape.jpg?resize=300%2C178&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/portrait_or_landscape.jpg?resize=768%2C455&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/portrait_or_landscape.jpg?resize=600%2C355&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/portrait_or_landscape.jpg?resize=717%2C424&amp;ssl=1 717w" sizes="(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px" data-recalc-dims="1" /></span></figure></div><p>如果您只是对使用纵向和横向方向的实用建议感兴趣，请随意跳到下一部分 - 但对于那些想要了解这些视觉格式背后的历史以及画家和摄影师如何使用的人来说过去使用过它们，继续阅读！</p><h3 class="wp-block-heading" class="wp-block-heading" data-section id="landscape-orientation"> 横向</h3><p>“风景”和“肖像”的名称可能源于很久以前艺术中使用的画布的方向。水平矩形的尺寸最能适应风景画家所描绘的广阔景色。这为该格式赢得了称号。</p><p>然而，风景方向不仅限于风景画，也不仅限于风景照片。是的， <a href="https://www.vangoghgallery.com/painting/starry-night.html" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopenernoopener noreferrer" class="ek-link">文森特·梵高</a>、 <a href="https://www.metmuseum.org/art/collection/search/45434" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopenernoopener noreferrer" class="ek-link">葛饰北斋</a>和<a href="https://www.claudemonetgallery.org/Antibes-Seen-From-The-Salis-Gardens2.html" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopenernoopener noreferrer" class="ek-link">莫奈</a>的风景画杰作都是以风景画形式创作的。但像<a href="https://www.uffizi.it/en/artworks/birth-of-venus" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopenernoopener noreferrer" class="ek-link">桑德罗·波提切利</a>和<a href="https://www.wassilykandinsky.net/work-36.php" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopenernoopener noreferrer" class="ek-link">瓦西里·康定斯基</a>这样的艺术家利用风景方向创作了非风景艺术。</p><p>在摄影方面， <a href="http://lanting.com/" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopenernoopener noreferrer" class="ek-link">弗兰斯·兰廷 (Frans Lanting)、</a> <a href="http://www.andreasgursky.com/en/works/2017/tokyo" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopenernoopener noreferrer" class="ek-link">安德烈亚斯·古尔斯基 (Andreas Gursky</a> ) 和<a href="https://gagosian.com/artists/gregory-crewdson/" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopenernoopener noreferrer" class="ek-link">格雷戈里·克鲁德森 (Gregory Crewdson)</a>等摄影师都以风景为主题，但他们的许多主题<em>都不</em>是风景。 </p><div class="wp-block-image wp-image-177201 size-full is-style-with-caption"><figure class="aligncenter"> <span class="responsive-image wp-image-177201" style="width:1500px"><span class="space" style="width:1500px; padding-top:66.67%"></span><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="1500" height="1000" src="https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/portrait_or_landscape_leaf_landscape.jpg?resize=1500%2C1000&#038;ssl=1" alt="水平方向叶" class="wp-image-177201" srcset="https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/portrait_or_landscape_leaf_landscape.jpg?w=1500&amp;ssl=1 1500w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/portrait_or_landscape_leaf_landscape.jpg?resize=300%2C200&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/portrait_or_landscape_leaf_landscape.jpg?resize=768%2C512&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/portrait_or_landscape_leaf_landscape.jpg?resize=600%2C400&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/portrait_or_landscape_leaf_landscape.jpg?resize=90%2C60&amp;ssl=1 90w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/portrait_or_landscape_leaf_landscape.jpg?resize=717%2C478&amp;ssl=1 717w" sizes="(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px" data-recalc-dims="1" /></span><figcaption class="wp-element-caption">我的树叶图像与传统的风景拍摄相去甚远，但我选择了水平格式来创造一种更轻松的观看方式。 </figcaption></figure></div><h3 class="wp-block-heading" class="wp-block-heading" data-section id="portrait-orientation">纵向</h3><p>照片（或画布）的高度大于宽度的照片（或画布）以肖像格式进行取景。</p><p>列奥纳多·达·芬奇的<a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Mona_Lisa#/media/File:Mona_Lisa,_by_Leonardo_da_Vinci,_from_C2RMF_retouched.jpg" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopenernoopener noreferrer" class="ek-link"><em>《蒙娜丽莎》</em></a>和约翰内斯·维米尔的<a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Girl_with_a_Pearl_Earring#/media/File:Meisje_met_de_parel.jpg" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopenernoopener noreferrer" class="ek-link"><em>《戴珍珠耳环的女孩》</em></a>都是以传统格式描绘的肖像画的著名例子。多萝西娅·兰格 (Dorothea Lange) 的<a href="https://www.moma.org/learn/moma_learning/dorothea-lange-migrant-mother-nipomo-california-1936/" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopenernoopener noreferrer" class="ek-link"><em>《移民母亲》</em></a>和史蒂夫·麦凯里 (Steve McCurry) 的<a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Afghan_Girl#/media/File:Sharbat_Gula.jpg" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopenernoopener noreferrer" class="ek-link"><em>《阿富汗女孩》</em></a>都是以肖像格式拍摄的肖像摄影的著名例子。</p><p>但肖像方向不仅仅用于描绘人物的艺术。 <a href="https://www.nationalgallery.org.uk/paintings/rachel-ruysch-flowers-in-a-glass-vase-with-a-tulip" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopenernoopener noreferrer" class="ek-link">雷切尔·鲁伊施 (Rachel Ruysch)</a>和<a href="https://www.claudemonetgallery.org/The-Water-Lily-Pond-Aka-Japanese-Bridge.html" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopenernoopener noreferrer" class="ek-link">克劳德·莫奈 (Claude Monet)</a>等画家以肖像画形式创作，同时也适应非人类题材。</p><p>摄影师<a href="https://www.tate.org.uk/art/artists/edward-weston-2720" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopenernoopener noreferrer" class="ek-link">爱德华·亨利·韦斯顿 (Edward Henry Weston)</a>使用肖像格式为他对有机材料的研究赋予了正式的品质，而<a href="http://www.artnet.com/artists/bernd-and-hilla-becher/" target="_blank" aria-label="the Bechers (opens in a new tab)" rel="nofollow noopenernoreferrer noopener" class="ek-link">贝歇夫妇</a>则拍摄了数百张城市地标的肖像照片。</p><p>也可以以横向格式拍摄肖像； <a href="https://www.icp.org/browse/archive/constituents/robert-frank?all/all/all/all/0" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopenernoopener noreferrer" class="ek-link">罗伯特·弗兰克（Robert Frank）</a>和<a href="http://www.artnet.com/artists/annie-leibovitz/" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopenernoopener noreferrer">安妮·莱博维茨（Annie Lebovitz）</a>等摄影师就以这种方式拍摄肖像。 </p><div class="wp-block-image wp-image-177202 size-full is-style-with-caption"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"> <span class="responsive-image wp-image-177202" style="width:400px"><span class="space" style="width:400px; padding-top:150%"></span><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="400" height="600" src="https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/portrait_or_landscape_leaf.jpg?resize=400%2C600&#038;ssl=1" alt="垂直叶摘要" class="wp-image-177202" srcset="https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/portrait_or_landscape_leaf.jpg?resize=400%2C600&amp;ssl=1 400w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/portrait_or_landscape_leaf.jpg?resize=200%2C300&amp;ssl=1 200w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/portrait_or_landscape_leaf.jpg?resize=768%2C1152&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/portrait_or_landscape_leaf.jpg?resize=717%2C1076&amp;ssl=1 717w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/portrait_or_landscape_leaf.jpg?w=1000&amp;ssl=1 1000w" sizes="(max-width: 400px) 100vw, 400px" data-recalc-dims="1" /></span><figcaption class="wp-element-caption">这是上面显示的同一片叶子，这次是纵向拍摄的。纵向方向赋予图像更正式的品质。 </figcaption></figure></div><h2 class="wp-block-heading" class="wp-block-heading" data-section id="should-you-use-portrait-or-landscape-orientation">您应该使用纵向还是横向？</h2><p>现在是时候解决一个大问题了：拍照时应该使用什么方向？什么时候肖像是更好的选择？什么时候应该坚持风景？</p><p>以下是选择框架方向时要考虑的四个关键事项：</p><h3 class="wp-block-heading" class="wp-block-heading" data-section id="fitting-the-subject">适合主题</h3><p>选择纵向或横向方向的决定因素之一是拍摄对象本身的尺寸。</p><p>就拍摄人脸和身体而言，肖像格式可能是理想的选择。人体的垂直特性非常适合纵向，因为它<em>适合</em>。</p><p> <a aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)" href="https://digital-photography-school.com/photographing-buildings-composition-tips/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" class="ek-link">高层建筑、</a> <a aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)" href="https://digital-photography-school.com/8-creative-ways-to-photograph-trees/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" class="ek-link">树木</a>和<a aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)" href="https://digital-photography-school.com/6-tips-photograph-waterfalls/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" class="ek-link">瀑布</a>等垂直主题有时也需要纵向拍摄才能完整拍摄。</p><div class="wp-block-image is-style-with-caption"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"> <span class="responsive-image wp-image-177203" style="width:400px"><span class="space" style="width:400px; padding-top:150%"></span><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="400" height="600" src="https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/portrait_or_landscape_lily.jpg?resize=400%2C600&#038;ssl=1" alt="垂直方向花" class="wp-image-177203" srcset="https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/portrait_or_landscape_lily.jpg?resize=400%2C600&amp;ssl=1 400w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/portrait_or_landscape_lily.jpg?resize=200%2C300&amp;ssl=1 200w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/portrait_or_landscape_lily.jpg?resize=768%2C1152&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/portrait_or_landscape_lily.jpg?resize=717%2C1076&amp;ssl=1 717w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/portrait_or_landscape_lily.jpg?w=1000&amp;ssl=1 1000w" sizes="(max-width: 400px) 100vw, 400px" data-recalc-dims="1" /></span><figcaption class="wp-element-caption">这种植物的垂直度使其非常适合拍摄肖像格式的照片。</figcaption></figure></div><p>另一方面，由水平元素组成的主题（例如<a href="https://digital-photography-school.com/tips-for-aviation-photography-with-canon-ef-24-105-f-4l-lens/">飞机</a>和<a href="https://digital-photography-school.com/10-tips-photographing-wide-angle-landscapes/">风景</a>）更适合横向。由于横向格式的长度大于高度，因此您可以使用横向框架来框架这些更水平的元素，而无需沿侧面剪掉不必要的部分。 </p><div class="wp-block-image wp-image-177195 size-full is-style-with-caption"><figure class="aligncenter"> <span class="responsive-image wp-image-177195" style="width:1500px"><span class="space" style="width:1500px; padding-top:66.67%"></span><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="1500" height="1000" src="https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/portrait_or_landscape_aircraft.jpg?resize=1500%2C1000&#038;ssl=1" alt="水平或垂直水平飞机" class="wp-image-177195" srcset="https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/portrait_or_landscape_aircraft.jpg?w=1500&amp;ssl=1 1500w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/portrait_or_landscape_aircraft.jpg?resize=300%2C200&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/portrait_or_landscape_aircraft.jpg?resize=768%2C512&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/portrait_or_landscape_aircraft.jpg?resize=600%2C400&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/portrait_or_landscape_aircraft.jpg?resize=90%2C60&amp;ssl=1 90w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/portrait_or_landscape_aircraft.jpg?resize=717%2C478&amp;ssl=1 717w" sizes="(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px" data-recalc-dims="1" /></span><figcaption class="wp-element-caption">由于飞机的尺寸，航空摄影通常以横向进行。</figcaption></figure></div><p>横向还可以为将附加元素合并到照片中提供更多空间。这在<a href="https://digital-photography-school.com/environmental-portraits/">环境肖像等摄影类型中特别有用，</a>其中照片的背景与主题一样重要。</p><h3 class="wp-block-heading" class="wp-block-heading" data-section id="emphasis">强调</h3><p>图像的方向对视觉强调有很大贡献。</p><p>肖像方向夸大了照片中拍摄对象的垂直延伸。它还讲述了我们与高大的主题的联系，强调独立感、惊奇感、现代感，甚至优越感或不安感。</p><p>相比之下，景观方向特别强调空间，体现轻松和沉浸感。</p><p>在下面的简单示例中，请注意从纵向到横向的变化如何导致完全不同的重点：</p><div class="wp-block-image is-style-with-caption"><figure class="aligncenter"> <span class="responsive-image wp-image-177342" style="width:1500px"><span class="space" style="width:1500px; padding-top:55.73%"></span><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="1500" height="836" src="https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/portrait_or_landscape_diagram_flower.jpg?resize=1500%2C836&#038;ssl=1" alt="花朵剪影示例" class="wp-image-177342" srcset="https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/portrait_or_landscape_diagram_flower.jpg?w=1500&amp;ssl=1 1500w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/portrait_or_landscape_diagram_flower.jpg?resize=300%2C167&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/portrait_or_landscape_diagram_flower.jpg?resize=768%2C428&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/portrait_or_landscape_diagram_flower.jpg?resize=600%2C334&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/portrait_or_landscape_diagram_flower.jpg?resize=160%2C88&amp;ssl=1 160w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/portrait_or_landscape_diagram_flower.jpg?resize=717%2C400&amp;ssl=1 717w" sizes="(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px" data-recalc-dims="1" /></span><figcaption class="wp-element-caption">肖像还是风景？这两张花卉剪影图像各有优点，但尽管主题相同，结果却<em>截然不同</em>！</figcaption></figure></div><p>肖像示例强调了<a href="https://digital-photography-school.com/beginners-guide-photographing-flowers/" target="_blank" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)" rel="noreferrer noopener" class="ek-link">花</a>的活力、正直品质。景观方向创造了更轻松的视角。</p><h3 class="wp-block-heading" class="wp-block-heading" data-section id="removing-distractions"> 消除干扰</h3><p>每个摄影情况都是不同的，有时潜在图像中的某个元素并不理想。</p><p>如果画面中存在您希望忽略的元素，切换相机方向可能有助于获得更精美的图像。一般来说，最好在外出拍摄时执行此操作，但您也可以在回家后使用裁剪工具重新调整图像的方向。</p><p>使用纵向<a aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)" href="https://digital-photography-school.com/using-cropping-to-improve-photographs/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" class="ek-link">裁剪</a>掉多余的信息将简化图像并最大限度地减少干扰。另一方面，从纵向切换到横向会降低图像高度，从而优先考虑照片中的水平流动。</p><div class="wp-block-image is-style-with-caption"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"> <span class="responsive-image wp-image-177197" style="width:438px"><span class="space" style="width:438px; padding-top:136.99%"></span><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="438" height="600" src="https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/portrait_or_landscape_abstract_crop.jpg?resize=438%2C600&#038;ssl=1" alt="水的抽象水平" class="wp-image-177197" srcset="https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/portrait_or_landscape_abstract_crop.jpg?resize=438%2C600&amp;ssl=1 438w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/portrait_or_landscape_abstract_crop.jpg?resize=219%2C300&amp;ssl=1 219w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/portrait_or_landscape_abstract_crop.jpg?resize=768%2C1051&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/portrait_or_landscape_abstract_crop.jpg?resize=717%2C981&amp;ssl=1 717w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/portrait_or_landscape_abstract_crop.jpg?w=1096&amp;ssl=1 1096w" sizes="(max-width: 438px) 100vw, 438px" data-recalc-dims="1" /></span><figcaption class="wp-element-caption">如果您注意到框架边缘有干扰，从水平方向快速调整为垂直方向可以解决该问题。 </figcaption></figure></div><h3 class="wp-block-heading" class="wp-block-heading" data-section id="formality-vs-relaxation">正式与放松</h3><p>由于横向方向已经常以某些方式使用，并且由于纵向方向已经常以<em>其他</em>方式使用，因此这些方向现在在大多数观看者的心中具有特定的关联。</p><p>肖像方向与历史<a href="https://digital-photography-school.com/tips-for-photographing-costume-portraits/">肖像画</a>的形式有关。它还与直立有关，直立与清醒、社交能力和精力有关。</p><p>另一方面，风景格式可以给照片带来更轻松、有机的印象。因此，水平方向与躺着相关，为图像带来更宁静的品质。</p><p>作为一名摄影师，您可以利用这些关联来创建具有不同效果的图像。想要拍摄更正式的照片吗？尝试纵向。想要创造更轻松的拍摄效果？横向可能是更好的选择。</p><div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter"> <span class="responsive-image wp-image-177198" style="width:1500px"><span class="space" style="width:1500px; padding-top:66.67%"></span><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="1500" height="1000" src="https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/portrait_or_landscape_rope.jpg?resize=1500%2C1000&#038;ssl=1" alt="编织垫" class="wp-image-177198" srcset="https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/portrait_or_landscape_rope.jpg?w=1500&amp;ssl=1 1500w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/portrait_or_landscape_rope.jpg?resize=300%2C200&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/portrait_or_landscape_rope.jpg?resize=768%2C512&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/portrait_or_landscape_rope.jpg?resize=600%2C400&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/portrait_or_landscape_rope.jpg?resize=90%2C60&amp;ssl=1 90w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/portrait_or_landscape_rope.jpg?resize=717%2C478&amp;ssl=1 717w" sizes="(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px" data-recalc-dims="1" /></span> </figure></div><h2 class="wp-block-heading" class="wp-block-heading" data-section id="when-in-doubt-try-them-both">如有疑问，请尝试两者！</h2><p>在纵向或横向之间进行选择并不容易。有很多方面需要考虑，图像的方向在很大程度上取决于具体情况。</p><p>但是，如果您了解不同方向的优点和缺点，您将能够很好地决定使用哪个方向！</p><p>当您无法确定纵向或横向哪个最好时，不要害怕尝试两者，然后在计算机屏幕上并排评估两个图像。</p><p>您不仅可以确保最终拍摄出一张好照片，还可以在此过程中学到一些有关照片方向的知识！</p><p>现在交给你：</p><p><em>您倾向于纵向还是横向？为什么？在下面的评论中分享您的想法！</em></p><div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter"> <span class="responsive-image wp-image-178466" style="width:1000px"><span class="space" style="width:1000px; padding-top:150%"></span><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="1000" height="1500" src="https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/dps-portrait-or-landscape-orientation-pinterest.jpg?resize=1000%2C1500&#038;ssl=1" alt="纵向或横向" class="wp-image-178466" srcset="https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/dps-portrait-or-landscape-orientation-pinterest.jpg?w=1000&amp;ssl=1 1000w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/dps-portrait-or-landscape-orientation-pinterest.jpg?resize=200%2C300&amp;ssl=1 200w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/dps-portrait-or-landscape-orientation-pinterest.jpg?resize=768%2C1152&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/dps-portrait-or-landscape-orientation-pinterest.jpg?resize=400%2C600&amp;ssl=1 400w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/dps-portrait-or-landscape-orientation-pinterest.jpg?resize=717%2C1076&amp;ssl=1 717w" sizes="(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px" data-recalc-dims="1" /></span></figure></div><p>帖子 <a rel="nofollow" href="https://digital-photography-school.com/portrait-or-landscape-orientation/">你应该以肖像还是风景方向拍摄？</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://digital-photography-school.com">数码摄影学校</a>。它的作者是<a rel="nofollow" href="https://digital-photography-school.com/author/megan-kennedy/">梅根·肯尼迪</a>。</p> ; https://digital-photography-school.com/portrait-or-landscape-orientation/feed/ 19 号
如何在 Photoshop 中创建蓝晒效果（分步） https://digital-photography-school.com/digital-cyanotype-using-photoshop/ https://digital-photography-school.com/digital-cyanotype-using-photoshop/#commentsAna Mireles Wed, 12 Jun 2024 10:00:00 +0000 Post Production TipsintermediatePhotoshop https://digital-photography-school.com/?p=159565 <p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://digital-photography-school.com/digital-cyanotype-using-photoshop/">如何在 Photoshop 中创建蓝晒效果（一步一步）</a>一文首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://digital-photography-school.com">Digital Photography School</a>上。它的作者是<a rel="nofollow" href="https://digital-photography-school.com/author/ana-mireles/">安娜·米雷莱斯</a>。</p><p>早在摄影的早期，蓝晒工艺是一种流行的方法，可以创造出具有吸引人、美丽的青色色调的图像。今天，您仍然可以制作蓝晒照片 - 事实上，美术摄影师中无相机蓝晒照片的制作工艺已经重新流行 - 但它需要暗室化学品。 （事实上​​，我们有一个全面的指南 [...]</p><p>这篇文章 <a rel="nofollow" href="https://digital-photography-school.com/digital-cyanotype-using-photoshop/">如何在 Photoshop 中创建蓝晒效果（一步一步）</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://digital-photography-school.com">Digital Photography School</a>上。它的作者是<a rel="nofollow" href="https://digital-photography-school.com/author/ana-mireles/">安娜·米雷莱斯</a>。</p> ; <p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://digital-photography-school.com/digital-cyanotype-using-photoshop/">如何在 Photoshop 中创建蓝晒效果（一步一步）</a>一文首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://digital-photography-school.com">Digital Photography School</a>上。它的作者是<a rel="nofollow" href="https://digital-photography-school.com/author/ana-mireles/">安娜·米雷莱斯</a>。</p><div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-full"> <span class="responsive-image wp-image-261378" style="width:1200px"><span class="space" style="width:1200px; padding-top:103.67%"></span><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="1200" height="1244" src="https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/cyanotype-effect-photoshop-1005.jpg?resize=1200%2C1244&#038;ssl=1" alt="使用 Photoshop 创建美丽的蓝晒版" class="wp-image-261378" srcset="https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/cyanotype-effect-photoshop-1005.jpg?w=1200&amp;ssl=1 1200w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/cyanotype-effect-photoshop-1005.jpg?resize=289%2C300&amp;ssl=1 289w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/cyanotype-effect-photoshop-1005.jpg?resize=579%2C600&amp;ssl=1 579w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/cyanotype-effect-photoshop-1005.jpg?resize=768%2C796&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/cyanotype-effect-photoshop-1005.jpg?resize=717%2C743&amp;ssl=1 717w" sizes="(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px" data-recalc-dims="1" /></span></figure></div><p>早在摄影的早期，蓝晒工艺是一种流行的方法，可以创造出具有吸引人、美丽的青色色调的图像。今天，您仍然可以制作蓝晒照片 - 事实上，美术摄影师中无相机蓝晒照片的制作工艺已经重新流行 - 但它需要暗室化学品。 （事实上​​，我们<a href="https://digital-photography-school.com/cyanotype-photography/" target="_blank" aria-label="comprehensive guide to creating physical cyanotypes right here (opens in a new tab)" rel="noreferrer noopener" class="ek-link">在这里有创建物理蓝晒的综合指南</a>！）</p><p>幸运的是，如果您对创建蓝晒效果感兴趣，则不必返回暗室或成为化学家并在此过程中浪费大量材料。您可以使用 Photoshop 创建<em>数字</em>蓝晒版，这就是我今天将向您展示的内容。</p><p>注意：由于摄影师通过将光敏乳剂涂在他们想要打印的纸张（或表面）上来实现蓝晒，因此您首先需要的是模仿这种效果的背景。如果您觉得自己很狡猾，可以购买画笔和一些蓝色颜料并实际创建背景。然后扫描它并使其尺寸和分辨率最适合您要使用的图像。</p><p>也就是说，您可以以数字方式创建背景。因为我向您承诺了数字蓝晒技术，所以我将在我的教程中包括背景创建过程！</p><p>这就是你要做的： </p><h2 class="wp-block-heading" class="wp-block-heading" data-section id="step-create-your-cyanotype-background">第 1 步：创建蓝晒背景</h2><p>您首先需要打开 Photoshop。使用空白的白色画布创建一个新文件。</p><p>继续选择屏幕左侧的<a href="https://digital-photography-school.com/5-things-to-know-about-photoshop-brushes/" target="_blank" aria-label="Brush tool (opens in a new tab)" rel="noreferrer noopener" class="ek-link"><strong>画笔</strong>工具</a>，然后选择画笔的大小和类型。从<strong>选项栏中</strong>选择画笔功能；我建议选择一把宽尖的画笔，比如一把扇子，这样效果就可以模仿油漆的笔触，而不是钢笔或记号笔。</p><p>画笔大小取决于文档的大小，但您需要保持相对较大以创建“刷涂”效果：</p><div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter"> <span class="responsive-image wp-image-159566" style="width:1500px"><span class="space" style="width:1500px; padding-top:54.8%"></span><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="1500" height="822" src="https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/Create-Digital-Cyanotype-Photoshop-Tutorial-Brush.jpg?resize=1500%2C822&#038;ssl=1" alt="如何使用 Photoshop 创建蓝晒版" class="wp-image-159566" srcset="https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/Create-Digital-Cyanotype-Photoshop-Tutorial-Brush.jpg?w=1500&amp;ssl=1 1500w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/Create-Digital-Cyanotype-Photoshop-Tutorial-Brush.jpg?resize=300%2C164&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/Create-Digital-Cyanotype-Photoshop-Tutorial-Brush.jpg?resize=768%2C421&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/Create-Digital-Cyanotype-Photoshop-Tutorial-Brush.jpg?resize=600%2C329&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/Create-Digital-Cyanotype-Photoshop-Tutorial-Brush.jpg?resize=620%2C340&amp;ssl=1 620w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/Create-Digital-Cyanotype-Photoshop-Tutorial-Brush.jpg?resize=160%2C88&amp;ssl=1 160w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/Create-Digital-Cyanotype-Photoshop-Tutorial-Brush.jpg?resize=717%2C393&amp;ssl=1 717w" sizes="(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px" data-recalc-dims="1" /></span></figure></div><p>在画笔颜色方面，使用黑色，因为稍后会应用蓝色调。</p><p>然后继续用画笔覆盖大部分画布。目标不是把整个东西涂成黑色，而是模拟一张涂有光敏乳液的纸，如下所示：</p><div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter"> <span class="responsive-image wp-image-159567" style="width:1500px"><span class="space" style="width:1500px; padding-top:54.6%"></span><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="1500" height="819" src="https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/Create-Digital-Cyanotype-Photoshop-Tutorial-Brushstroke-Background.jpg?resize=1500%2C819&#038;ssl=1" alt="如何使用 Photoshop 创建蓝晒版" class="wp-image-159567" srcset="https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/Create-Digital-Cyanotype-Photoshop-Tutorial-Brushstroke-Background.jpg?w=1500&amp;ssl=1 1500w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/Create-Digital-Cyanotype-Photoshop-Tutorial-Brushstroke-Background.jpg?resize=300%2C164&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/Create-Digital-Cyanotype-Photoshop-Tutorial-Brushstroke-Background.jpg?resize=768%2C419&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/Create-Digital-Cyanotype-Photoshop-Tutorial-Brushstroke-Background.jpg?resize=600%2C328&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/Create-Digital-Cyanotype-Photoshop-Tutorial-Brushstroke-Background.jpg?resize=620%2C340&amp;ssl=1 620w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/Create-Digital-Cyanotype-Photoshop-Tutorial-Brushstroke-Background.jpg?resize=160%2C88&amp;ssl=1 160w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/Create-Digital-Cyanotype-Photoshop-Tutorial-Brushstroke-Background.jpg?resize=717%2C391&amp;ssl=1 717w" sizes="(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px" data-recalc-dims="1" /></span></figure></div><p>笔触不均匀就可以了。请记住，最初的方法使用手工技术，因此不均匀的笔触会产生漂亮独特的外观。</p><h2 class="wp-block-heading" class="wp-block-heading" data-section id="step-add-your-image">第 2 步：添加您的图片</h2><p>现在是时候引入您想要进行蓝晒处理的图像了。根据我的经验，任何黑色或深色背景的照片都能与蓝晒背景完美融合。但是，可以使用任何图像。 （如果您不确定选择哪个图像，请记住这是一个相当快的过程，因此您可以随时尝试多张图像！）</p><p>将图像作为新的 Photoshop 文档打开并降低其饱和度。为此，请在主菜单中选择<strong>“图像”>;“调整”>;“色相/饱和度”</strong> 。然后将<strong>饱和度</strong>滑块一直向下移动到左侧：</p><div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter"> <span class="responsive-image wp-image-159570" style="width:1500px"><span class="space" style="width:1500px; padding-top:55.2%"></span><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="1500" height="828" src="https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/Create-Digital-Cyanotype-Photoshop-Tutorial-Hue-Saturation.jpg?resize=1500%2C828&#038;ssl=1" alt="如何使用 Photoshop 创建蓝晒版" class="wp-image-159570" srcset="https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/Create-Digital-Cyanotype-Photoshop-Tutorial-Hue-Saturation.jpg?w=1500&amp;ssl=1 1500w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/Create-Digital-Cyanotype-Photoshop-Tutorial-Hue-Saturation.jpg?resize=300%2C166&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/Create-Digital-Cyanotype-Photoshop-Tutorial-Hue-Saturation.jpg?resize=768%2C424&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/Create-Digital-Cyanotype-Photoshop-Tutorial-Hue-Saturation.jpg?resize=600%2C331&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/Create-Digital-Cyanotype-Photoshop-Tutorial-Hue-Saturation.jpg?resize=160%2C88&amp;ssl=1 160w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/Create-Digital-Cyanotype-Photoshop-Tutorial-Hue-Saturation.jpg?resize=717%2C396&amp;ssl=1 717w" sizes="(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px" data-recalc-dims="1" /></span></figure></div><p>现在您已经有了单色图像，继续将其拖动到您创建笔触背景的画布中。它将作为新图层粘贴到该文档中。</p><p>重新定位它，使其恰好适合背景的“绘制”部分。如果需要调整照片大小，请按<strong>Ctrl/Cmd</strong> + <strong>T</strong>并拖动角，直到看起来合适为止。单击复选标记进行应用。</p><p>您现在应该有一个看起来像这样的图像：</p><div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter"> <span class="responsive-image wp-image-159573" style="width:1500px"><span class="space" style="width:1500px; padding-top:55.2%"></span><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="1500" height="828" src="https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/Create-Digital-Cyanotype-Photoshop-Tutorial-Layers.jpg?resize=1500%2C828&#038;ssl=1" alt="如何使用 Photoshop 创建蓝晒版" class="wp-image-159573" srcset="https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/Create-Digital-Cyanotype-Photoshop-Tutorial-Layers.jpg?w=1500&amp;ssl=1 1500w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/Create-Digital-Cyanotype-Photoshop-Tutorial-Layers.jpg?resize=300%2C166&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/Create-Digital-Cyanotype-Photoshop-Tutorial-Layers.jpg?resize=768%2C424&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/Create-Digital-Cyanotype-Photoshop-Tutorial-Layers.jpg?resize=600%2C331&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/Create-Digital-Cyanotype-Photoshop-Tutorial-Layers.jpg?resize=160%2C88&amp;ssl=1 160w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/Create-Digital-Cyanotype-Photoshop-Tutorial-Layers.jpg?resize=717%2C396&amp;ssl=1 717w" sizes="(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px" data-recalc-dims="1" /></span> </figure></div><h2 class="wp-block-heading" class="wp-block-heading" data-section id="step-lighten-the-background">第三步：淡化背景</h2><p>此时，我们将减轻笔触，以便与图像更好地融合。</p><p>确保选择了笔触图层而<em>不是</em>图像图层。然后单击<a href="https://digital-photography-school.com/photoshop-layers-for-beginners/" target="_blank" aria-label="Adjustment Layer icon (opens in a new tab)" rel="noreferrer noopener" class="ek-link">调整图层图标</a>并选择<strong><a href="https://digital-photography-school.com/use-levels-tool-photoshop/" target="_blank" aria-label="Levels (opens in a new tab)" rel="noreferrer noopener" class="ek-link">级别</a></strong>：</p><div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter"> <span class="responsive-image wp-image-159574" style="width:1500px"><span class="space" style="width:1500px; padding-top:55%"></span><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="1500" height="825" src="https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/Create-Digital-Cyanotype-Photoshop-Tutorial-Levels.jpg?resize=1500%2C825&#038;ssl=1" alt="如何使用 Photoshop 创建蓝晒版" class="wp-image-159574" srcset="https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/Create-Digital-Cyanotype-Photoshop-Tutorial-Levels.jpg?w=1500&amp;ssl=1 1500w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/Create-Digital-Cyanotype-Photoshop-Tutorial-Levels.jpg?resize=300%2C165&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/Create-Digital-Cyanotype-Photoshop-Tutorial-Levels.jpg?resize=768%2C422&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/Create-Digital-Cyanotype-Photoshop-Tutorial-Levels.jpg?resize=600%2C330&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/Create-Digital-Cyanotype-Photoshop-Tutorial-Levels.jpg?resize=620%2C340&amp;ssl=1 620w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/Create-Digital-Cyanotype-Photoshop-Tutorial-Levels.jpg?resize=160%2C88&amp;ssl=1 160w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/Create-Digital-Cyanotype-Photoshop-Tutorial-Levels.jpg?resize=717%2C394&amp;ssl=1 717w" sizes="(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px" data-recalc-dims="1" /></span></figure></div><p>这将创建一个位于图像层和“画布”背景层之间的图层，这意味着它只会影响笔触，而不会影响照片。</p><p>您可以通过色阶调整做<em>很多事情</em>，但正如我所说，我们的目标是减轻笔触背景。抓住中间色调滑块并将其稍微向下拖动（请参阅上面的屏幕截图以获取指导！）。然后抓住黑色滑块并将其轻轻向上移动，使黑色变成深灰色。 </p><h2 class="wp-block-heading" class="wp-block-heading" data-section id="step-create-the-blue-effect">第四步：创建蓝色效果</h2><p>蓝晒版应该看起来是蓝色的，但我们目前正在处理灰色画布上的黑白图像。</p><p>所以这就是我们需要做的：</p><p>首先，确保选择顶层（即包含图像的图层）。单击调整图层图标，然后添加<strong>色彩平衡</strong>图层：</p><div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter"> <span class="responsive-image wp-image-159568" style="width:1500px"><span class="space" style="width:1500px; padding-top:55%"></span><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="1500" height="825" src="https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/Create-Digital-Cyanotype-Photoshop-Tutorial-Color-Balance.jpg?resize=1500%2C825&#038;ssl=1" alt="如何使用 Photoshop 创建蓝晒版" class="wp-image-159568" srcset="https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/Create-Digital-Cyanotype-Photoshop-Tutorial-Color-Balance.jpg?w=1500&amp;ssl=1 1500w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/Create-Digital-Cyanotype-Photoshop-Tutorial-Color-Balance.jpg?resize=300%2C165&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/Create-Digital-Cyanotype-Photoshop-Tutorial-Color-Balance.jpg?resize=768%2C422&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/Create-Digital-Cyanotype-Photoshop-Tutorial-Color-Balance.jpg?resize=600%2C330&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/Create-Digital-Cyanotype-Photoshop-Tutorial-Color-Balance.jpg?resize=620%2C340&amp;ssl=1 620w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/Create-Digital-Cyanotype-Photoshop-Tutorial-Color-Balance.jpg?resize=160%2C88&amp;ssl=1 160w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/Create-Digital-Cyanotype-Photoshop-Tutorial-Color-Balance.jpg?resize=717%2C394&amp;ssl=1 717w" sizes="(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px" data-recalc-dims="1" /></span></figure></div><p>通过调整滑块，您可以创建漂亮的蓝色调。请随意尝试，但作为起点，请尝试我的设置：青色 -62、洋红色 0 和蓝色 +95。</p><p>一旦您对图像的颜色感到满意，您可以继续下一步，或者您可以选择通过添加另一个调整图层来降低颜色的强度。</p><p> （记住始终保持选择顶部图层，以便新的调整图层影响所有图层！）</p><p>具体来说，您可以添加<strong>色相/饱和度</strong>图层，然后将<strong>饱和度</strong>滑块向左移动一点：</p><div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-full"> <span class="responsive-image wp-image-159576" style="width:1500px"><span class="space" style="width:1500px; padding-top:55.2%"></span><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="1500" height="828" src="https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/Create-Digital-Cyanotype-Photoshop-Tutorial-Cyan-Tone.jpg?resize=1500%2C828&#038;ssl=1" alt="如何使用 Photoshop 创建蓝晒版" class="wp-image-159576" srcset="https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/Create-Digital-Cyanotype-Photoshop-Tutorial-Cyan-Tone.jpg?w=1500&amp;ssl=1 1500w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/Create-Digital-Cyanotype-Photoshop-Tutorial-Cyan-Tone.jpg?resize=300%2C166&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/Create-Digital-Cyanotype-Photoshop-Tutorial-Cyan-Tone.jpg?resize=768%2C424&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/Create-Digital-Cyanotype-Photoshop-Tutorial-Cyan-Tone.jpg?resize=600%2C331&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/Create-Digital-Cyanotype-Photoshop-Tutorial-Cyan-Tone.jpg?resize=160%2C88&amp;ssl=1 160w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/Create-Digital-Cyanotype-Photoshop-Tutorial-Cyan-Tone.jpg?resize=717%2C396&amp;ssl=1 717w" sizes="(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px" data-recalc-dims="1" /></span></figure></div><p>这会巧妙地降低图像的饱和度并降低​​蓝色的强度。只是要小心不要添加太多的去饱和度；否则，您的图像将不再类似于蓝晒版。 </p><h2 class="wp-block-heading" class="wp-block-heading" data-section id="step-blend-the-image-and-the-background">第5步：混合图像和背景</h2><p>如果您仍然可以在笔触背景上看到图像的边框，则平衡不太正确。我们希望确保图像和背景无缝地融合在一起，就像真正的蓝晒版一样。</p><p>幸运的是，这个问题很容易解决。您只需要调整<a href="https://digital-photography-school.com/first-3-photoshop-blend-modes-need-understand/" target="_blank" aria-label="layer blend mode (opens in a new tab)" rel="noreferrer noopener" class="ek-link">图层混合模式</a>即可！只需选择图像（不是背景）图层，然后打开混合模式菜单。我建议选择<strong>“变亮”</strong>或<strong><a href="https://digital-photography-school.com/screen-blend-mode/" target="_blank" aria-label="Screen (opens in a new tab)" rel="noreferrer noopener" class="ek-link">“滤色”</a></strong>以获得最佳效果：</p><div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter"> <span class="responsive-image wp-image-159572" style="width:1500px"><span class="space" style="width:1500px; padding-top:55.2%"></span><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="1500" height="828" src="https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/Create-Digital-Cyanotype-Photoshop-Tutorial-Layer-Blending-Mode.jpg?resize=1500%2C828&#038;ssl=1" alt="如何使用 Photoshop 创建蓝晒版" class="wp-image-159572" srcset="https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/Create-Digital-Cyanotype-Photoshop-Tutorial-Layer-Blending-Mode.jpg?w=1500&amp;ssl=1 1500w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/Create-Digital-Cyanotype-Photoshop-Tutorial-Layer-Blending-Mode.jpg?resize=300%2C166&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/Create-Digital-Cyanotype-Photoshop-Tutorial-Layer-Blending-Mode.jpg?resize=768%2C424&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/Create-Digital-Cyanotype-Photoshop-Tutorial-Layer-Blending-Mode.jpg?resize=600%2C331&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/Create-Digital-Cyanotype-Photoshop-Tutorial-Layer-Blending-Mode.jpg?resize=160%2C88&amp;ssl=1 160w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/Create-Digital-Cyanotype-Photoshop-Tutorial-Layer-Blending-Mode.jpg?resize=717%2C396&amp;ssl=1 717w" sizes="(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px" data-recalc-dims="1" /></span></figure></div><p>这应该可以解决大多数混合问题。但是，在我的示例图像中，放大时仍然可以看到边框：</p><div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter"> <span class="responsive-image wp-image-159569" style="width:1500px"><span class="space" style="width:1500px; padding-top:55.13%"></span><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="1500" height="827" src="https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/Create-Digital-Cyanotype-Photoshop-Tutorial-Fine-Tunning.jpg?resize=1500%2C827&#038;ssl=1" alt="如何使用 Photoshop 创建蓝晒版" class="wp-image-159569" srcset="https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/Create-Digital-Cyanotype-Photoshop-Tutorial-Fine-Tunning.jpg?w=1500&amp;ssl=1 1500w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/Create-Digital-Cyanotype-Photoshop-Tutorial-Fine-Tunning.jpg?resize=300%2C165&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/Create-Digital-Cyanotype-Photoshop-Tutorial-Fine-Tunning.jpg?resize=768%2C423&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/Create-Digital-Cyanotype-Photoshop-Tutorial-Fine-Tunning.jpg?resize=600%2C331&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/Create-Digital-Cyanotype-Photoshop-Tutorial-Fine-Tunning.jpg?resize=160%2C88&amp;ssl=1 160w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/Create-Digital-Cyanotype-Photoshop-Tutorial-Fine-Tunning.jpg?resize=717%2C395&amp;ssl=1 717w" sizes="(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px" data-recalc-dims="1" /></span></figure></div><p>如果您遇到这种情况，请从左侧的工具面板中选择<a aria-label="Eraser tool (opens in a new tab)" href="https://digital-photography-school.com/photoshop-eraser-tool/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" class="ek-link"><strong>橡皮擦</strong>工具</a>。选择具有柔和边框的画笔，并将不透明度降低至 30% 左右。小心地刷过可见的边框边缘，以创建更平滑的过渡。 </p><h2 class="wp-block-heading" class="wp-block-heading" data-section id="share-your-finished-cyanotype">分享你完成的蓝晒版！</h2><p>嗯，这基本上就是您需要做的全部事情。此时，您应该拥有非常漂亮的数字蓝晒版！这是我的：</p><div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-full"> <span class="responsive-image wp-image-159575" style="width:1500px"><span class="space" style="width:1500px; padding-top:66.67%"></span><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="1500" height="1000" src="https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/Digital-Cyanotype-Photoshop-Final.jpg?resize=1500%2C1000&#038;ssl=1" alt="如何使用 Photoshop 创建蓝晒版" class="wp-image-159575" srcset="https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/Digital-Cyanotype-Photoshop-Final.jpg?w=1500&amp;ssl=1 1500w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/Digital-Cyanotype-Photoshop-Final.jpg?resize=300%2C200&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/Digital-Cyanotype-Photoshop-Final.jpg?resize=768%2C512&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/Digital-Cyanotype-Photoshop-Final.jpg?resize=600%2C400&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/Digital-Cyanotype-Photoshop-Final.jpg?resize=90%2C60&amp;ssl=1 90w, https://i0.wp.com/digital-photography-school.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/Digital-Cyanotype-Photoshop-Final.jpg?resize=717%2C478&amp;ssl=1 717w" sizes="(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px" data-recalc-dims="1" /></span></figure></div><p>如果您喜欢这种效果，我鼓励您在几张不同的照片上尝试一下。然后导出您最喜欢的并在下面的评论中分享！</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://digital-photography-school.com/digital-cyanotype-using-photoshop/">如何在 Photoshop 中创建蓝晒效果（一步一步）</a>一文首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://digital-photography-school.com">Digital Photography School</a>上。它的作者是<a rel="nofollow" href="https://digital-photography-school.com/author/ana-mireles/">安娜·米雷莱斯</a>。</p> ; https://digital-photography-school.com/digital-cyanotype-using-photoshop/feed/ 3
